{"id": "V11.23", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V11.23", "date": "2021-11-17", "champions": [{"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Complete visual update across all skins.", "New splash artwork for  Resistance Caitlyn,  Sheriff Caitlyn,  Safari Caitlyn,  Arctic Warfare Caitlyn, and  Officer Caitlyn.", "Adjusted splash artwork for  Original Caitlyn,  Headhunter Caitlyn,  Lunar Wraith Caitlyn,  Pool Party Caitlyn,  Arcade Caitlyn, and  Arcade Caitlyn Prestige Edition.", "New lore.", "New voice-over.", "Added ejected bullet when reloading her rifle."]}, {"about": "Headshot", "lines": ["Removed: Gaining an Empowered Headshot no longer allows Caitlyn to attack the trapped target ignoring an ongoing attack cooldown.", "Undocumented/New: Because they are proper attacks now, Headshot attacks against trapped enemies also generate a stack towards  Headshot now.", "\"Passive Ready\" SFX adjusted for more of a Hextech feel. Added SFX that plays when Headshot is ready for use."]}, {"about": "Piltover Peacemaker", "lines": ["New meshes and particles made to look more Hextech. Initial on-hit SFX are now more impactful than subsequent hits."]}, {"about": "Yordle Snap Trap", "lines": ["Added indicator on traps and their activation VFXs. Trap SFXs adjusted to match new animation timing."]}, {"about": "90 Caliber Net", "lines": ["New range indicator. On-hit SFX are now more impactful."]}, {"about": "Ace in the Hole", "lines": ["New laser and Hextech imagery. On-cast SFX are now more impactful and have additional Hextech elements."]}]}, {"name": "Fiddlesticks", "changes": [{"about": "A Harmless Scarecrow", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Placing a  Scarecrow Effigy while channeling  Crowstorm no longer overrides the ultimate's SFX."]}]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Base voice lines have been remastered to sound clearer, cleaner, and smoother."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Deat