us movement speed AP ratio increased to 12% per 100 AP from 5% per 100 AP.", "Base damage increased to 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 / 95 from 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90.", "Cooldown increased to 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4 seconds from 4 at all ranks.", "Mana cost increased to 65 from 45."]}, {"about": "Watch Out! Eep!", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 / 150 from 70 / 85 / 100 / 115 / 130.", "AP ratio increased to 35% AP from 30% AP."]}, {"about": "Swirlseed", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 18 seconds from 12.", "Base damage increased to 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 / 170 from 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 / 150.", "AP ratio increased to 45% AP from 40% AP.", "Slow changed to 40% at all ranks from 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45%."]}, {"about": "Lilting Lullaby", "lines": ["Sleep duration reduced to 1.5 / 2 / 2.5 seconds from 2 / 2.5 / 3.", "AP ratio increased to 40% AP from 30% AP.", "Initial slow reduced to 10% from 25%.", "Removed: Slow no longer increases up to 50% over the duration."]}]}, {"name": "Lucian", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated visual effects."]}]}, {"name": "Malzahar", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 510 from 537."]}, {"about": "Call of the Void", "lines": ["AP ratio reduced to 55% AP from 65% AP."]}]}, {"name": "Nocturne", "changes": [{"about": "Umbra Blades", "lines": ["New Effect: Damage and healing are now reduced by 50% against minions."]}]}, {"name": "Olaf", "changes": [{"about": "Ragnarok", "lines": ["Undocumented/Bug fix: Can once again remove the  grounded and  silence debuffs from the  Cassiopeia's  Miasma,  Singed's  Mega Adhesive and  Soraka's  Equinox fields."]}]}, {"name": "Rek'Sai", "changes": [{"about": "Queen's Wrath", "lines": ["Base damage per attack increased to 21 / 27 / 33 / 39 / 45 from 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40.", "Maximum base damage increased to 63 / 81 / 99 / 117 / 135 from 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120."]}, {"about": "Prey Seeker", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 from 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "PROJECT: Renekton", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed VFX bugs."]}]}, {"name": "Rumble", "changes": [{"about": "Electro Harpoon", "lines": ["Undocumented/Bug Fix: Will now cast immediately no matter how far away the cursor is, instead of causing Rumble to walk closer to his cursor if cast further than 10000 units away."]}]}, {"name": "Seraphine", "changes": [{"about": "High Note", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65% AP from 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% AP.", "Maximum AP ratio increased to 67.5 / 75 / 82.5 / 90 / 97.5% AP from 60 / 67.5 / 75 / 82.5 / 90% AP."]}]}, {"name": "Shaco", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 560 from 587.", "Base movement speed reduced to 345 from 350."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "Mega Adhesive", "lines": ["Undocumented/Bug fix: Grounded debuff can once again be cleansed by  Olaf's  Ragnarok."]}]}, {"name": "Sion", "changes": [{"about": "Glory in Death", "lines": ["Bug Fix:  Sterak's Gage's Lifeline no longer refreshes its readiness upon death, which caused it to always trigger again during Glory in Death even if on cooldown."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "Equinox", "lines": ["Undocumented/Bug fix: Silence debuff can once again be cleansed by  Olaf's  Ragnarok."]}]}, {"name": "Sylas", "changes": [{"about": "Hijack", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Hijacking  Devour now properly allows Sylas to apply stacks of  An Acquired Taste on his basic attacks against enemy champions."]}]}, {"name": "Tahm Kench", "changes": [{"about": "An Acquired Taste", "lines": ["New Effect: Now has a base damage of 12 - 60 (based on level).", "Health ratio reduced to 2.5% bonus health from 2.5% maximum health.", "Previously granted 14.25 - 54.63 (based on level) damage from base health."]}, {"about": "Tongue Lash", "lines": ["New Effect: Now applies  An Acquired Taste's damage.", "New Effect: Now has a base heal of 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35.", "Heal health ratio reduced to 4 / 4.5 / 5 / 5.5 / 6% missing health from 6 / 7 / 8 / 9 / 10%."]}, {"about": "Abyssal Dive", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where its cooldown refund would not scale with ability haste.", "Cooldown refund increased to 40% from 30%.", "Mana cost refund increased to 40% from 30%."]}, {"about": "Devour", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he could Devour an enemy without full stacks of An Acquired Taste if he queued the spell before the stacks fell off.", "Base shield increased to 400 / 500 / 600 from 300 / 450 / 600.", "Ally self slow reduced to 30 / 20 / 10% from 40 / 25 / 10%."]}]}, {"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Undocumented/Bug Fix: First move voice line now always triggers.", "Undocumented/Bug Fix: Generic item purchase lines have been restored.", "Undocumented/Bug Fix: Missing item specific voice interactions have been repurposed."]}, {"about": "Starlight's Touch", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 from 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90."]}, {"about": "Dazzle", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 40 from 60."]}, {"about": "Cosmic Radiance", "lines": ["Undocumented/Bug Fix:  Voice lines have been made more frequent to trigger."]}]}, {"name": "Xin Zhao", "changes": [{"about": "Wind Becomes Lightning", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds from 12 / 10.5 / 9 / 7.5 / 6."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": [{"about": "Sweeping Blade", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer occasionally fails to plays its proper animation and instead use his moving animation."]}]}, {"name": "Zed", "changes": [{"about": "PROJECT: Zed Prestige Edition", "lines": ["Suit colors changed to be more grey than brown.", "Blade colors changed to be more gold.", " Shadow Slash visual effects now have grind particles."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base mana reduced to 420 from 480."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated visual effects.", "Now matches his aesthetics from Legends of Runeterra.", "All skins cleaned up to match the new effects on the base skin."]}, {"about": "Time Bomb", "lines": ["New VFX; AoE stun effects are now easier to identify."]}, {"about": "Rewind", "lines": ["New cast effect."]}, {"about": "Time Warp", "lines": ["Cleaned up; textures adjusted to match overall changes."]}, {"about": "Chronoshift", "lines": ["Modernized to match overall changes."]}, {"about": "Shurima Desert Zilean", "lines": [" Time Bomb", "Now has a subtle sand effect."]}, {"about": "Blood Moon Zilean and  Sugar Rush Zilean", "lines": [" Chronoshift", "Modernized revive effect to match base changes."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "Mega Adhesive", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Targets are once again rooted if  Flung into Mega Adhesive."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "Mega Adhesive", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Slow no longer sometimes lingers longer than intended."]}]}]}
{"id": "V11.13", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V11.13", "date": "2021-06-23", "champions": [{"name": "Aphelios", "changes": [{"about": "The Hitman and the Seer", "lines": ["Bonus attack damage increased to 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 from 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 20 / 24.", "Lethality increased to 4.5 / 9 / 13.5 / 18 / 22.5 / 27 from 3.5 / 7 / 10.5 / 14 / 17.5 / 21."]}, {"about": "Moonlight Vigil", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he would heal from spells instead of basic attacks when using it with  Severum."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Miasma", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Grounded debuff is now non-dispellable.", "This prevents the debuff from being briefly removed by  cleanses even while the player remains in the AoE.", "Because of this,  Olaf's  Ragnarok fails to dispell and become immune to the effect for the remaining duration unless he leaves and reenters it.(bug)"]}]}, {"name": "Dr. Mundo", "changes": [{"about": "Goes Where He Pleases", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Now prevents  Mordekaiser's  Realm of Death from bringing Dr. Mundo to the Death Realm; no longer prevents the initial slow being applied."]}, {"about": "Blunt Force Trauma", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Now more fluidly turns before the attack animation."]}, {"about": "Corporate Mundo,  El Macho Mundo,  Executioner Mundo,  Mr. Mundoverse,  Mundo Mundo, and  TPA Mundo", "lines": [" Infected Bonesaw", "Bug Fix: Is now more visible when used in brushes."]}]}, {"name": "Gnar", "changes": [{"about": "Rage Gene", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where  Mega Gnar's base attack damage was inconsistent with its tooltip."]}]}, {"name": "Jinx", "changes": [{"about": "Star Guardian Jinx", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Individual item purchase voice lines have been restored.", " Statikk Shiv's purchase lines now play for buying  Stormrazor."]}]}, {"name": "Kayn", "changes": [{"about": "Blade's Reach", "lines": ["Bug Fix: VFX is now revealed when cast within terrain towards enemy champions."]}]}, {"name": "Lee Sin", "changes": [{"about": "Tempest", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 100 / 130 / 160 / 190 / 220 from 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 / 260."]}]}, {"name": "Neeko", "changes": [{"about": "Inherent Glamour", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where, when disguised, her purple bar displayed the selected ally's health instead of her current health."]}]}, {"name": "Olaf", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health growth increased to 100 from 93.", "Base mana regeneration increased to 7.5 from 7.47.", "Mana regeneration growth increased to 0.6 from 0.58."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": [{"about": "Powerball", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where the SFX volume was affected by his VO."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "Valor", "lines": ["Base shield reduced to 85 / 115 / 145 / 175 / 205 from 95 / 125 / 155 / 185 / 215."]}]}, {"name": "Rumble", "changes": [{"about": "Scrap Shield", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 7 / 6.75 / 6.5 / 6.25 / 6 seconds from 6 at all ranks.", "Bonus movement speed reduced to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% from 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35%.", "Danger Zone bonus movement speed reduced to 15 / 22.5 / 30 / 37.5 / 45% from 22.5 / 30 / 37.5 / 45 / 52.5%."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "Mega Adhesive", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Grounded debuff is now non-dispellable.", "This prevents the debuff from being briefly removed by  cleanses even while the player remains in the AoE.", "Because of this,  Olaf's  Ragnarok fails to dispell and become immune to the effect for the remaining duration unless he leaves and reenters it.(bug)"]}]}, {"name": "Sion", "changes": [{"about": "Glory in Death", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where the respawned Sion could be knocked back to his previous location by certain abilities, if  Glory in Death lasted longer than his death timer's duration.", " Dr. Mundo's  Blunt Force Trauma no longer pulls a vanished Sion from his respawn location.", " Urgot's  Disdain no longer pulls respawned Sion if he is more than 2000 units away.", " Zac's  Stretching Strikes still has this issue."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "Equinox", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Silence debuff is now non-dispellable.", "This prevents the debuff from being briefly removed by  cleanses even while the player remains in the AoE.", "Because of this,  Olaf's  Ragnarok fails to dispell and become immune to the effect for the remaining duration unless he leaves and reenters it.(bug)"]}]}, {"name": "Tahm Kench", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 570 from 600.", "Health growth reduced to 95 from 100.", "Mana growth increased to 50 from 40.", "Base armor reduced to 42 from 47."]}, {"about": "An Acquired Taste", "lines": ["Health ratio reduced to 2.5% maximum health from 4%."]}, {"about": "Tongue Lash", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 7 / 6.5 / 6 / 5.5 / 5 seconds from 5 at all ranks.", "Mana cost reduced to 50 / 46 / 42 / 38 / 34 from 50 at all ranks.", "Undocumented: Range reduced to  900 from 930.", "Slow changed to 40% at all ranks from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70%.", "Slow duration reduced to 2 seconds from 3.", "Stun duration reduced to 1.5 seconds from 2.", "New Effect: Now applies a stack of  An Acquired Taste against champions.", "Does not apply  An Acquired Taste's damage.", "Hitting champions with 3 stacks still consumes all their stacks to stun them.", "New Effect: Range and missile speed now scales up with his size.", "New Effect: Now heals for 6 / 7 / 8 / 9 / 10% missing health upon hitting enemy champions.", "New Effect: Can now  Devour enemy champions with three stacks of  An Acquired Taste if Tongue Lash hits them.", "Removed: Can no longer activate  Devour to eat minions or jungle monsters."]}, {"about": "Abyssal Dive (W)", "lines": ["Swapped with  Devour.", "Renamed to Abyssal Dive from Abyssal Voyage.", "Active: Tahm Kench  channels for 1.35 seconds, and upon completion  blinks to the target location after a 0.15-second delay. Upon arrival, he deals 100 / 135 / 170 / 205 / 240 (+100% AP) magic damage to nearby enemies and  knocks them up and  stuns them for 1 second. Hitting at least 1 enemy champion refunds 30% of the cooldown and mana cost.", "Enemies can see the indicator of this ability after he has channeled for 0.75 seconds.", "Allies may travel with Tahm if they are  Devoured, but can still exit early at any time.", "Tahm Kench is  unable to act for 0.65 seconds after the end of the channel.", "Cooldown: 21 / 20 / 19 / 18 / 17 seconds.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120.", "Cast Range: 1000 / 1050 / 1100 / 1150 / 1200."]}, {"about": "Thick Skin", "lines": ["Grey health timer increased to 4 seconds from 2.5.", "Shield duration increased to 2.5 seconds from 2.", "New Effect: Grey health is now capped at 300% maximum health.", "Healing changed to 10% maximum health per 0.264 seconds from 12 - 209 (based on level) per 0.8 seconds."]}, {"about": "Devour (R)", "lines": ["Swapped with  Abyssal Voyage.", "Active: Tahm Kench swallows the target  champion for up to 3 seconds, rendering them  vanished and  unable to act, as well as granting them  displacement immunity for the duration. Devour can be recast after 1 second, and does so automatically at the end of the duration.", "Devour will not automatically recast while Tahm Kench is performing  Abyssal Dive, and will instead do so after he has finished.", "If the target is an ally, they are granted a 300 / 450 / 600 (+100% AP)  shield for 2.5 seconds, refreshing after being spat out.", "Allies can exit at will by inputting a movement command, unless they're  immobilized or the recast is on cooldown.", "Tahm Kench is unable to cast movement spells and is  slowed by 40 / 25 / 10% while an ally is swallowed, but may still cast  Abyssal Dive.", "Allies can see if this spell is ready next to his health bar.", "If the target is an enemy, they are  suppressed for the duration and dealt 100 / 250 / 400 (+15% (+5% per 100 AP) of the target's maximum health) magic damage after the displacement ends.", "Devour can only be cast on enemies with 3 stacks of  An Acquired Taste, consuming the stacks in the process.", "Tahm Kench is  grounded and  slowed by 40% while an enemy is swallowed.", "Recast: Tahm Kench  spits the target out in the target direction.", "Cooldown: 120 / 100 / 80 seconds.", "Mana Cost: 100."]}]}, {"name": "Viego", "changes": [{"about": "Sovereign's Domination", "lines": ["Undocumented: Can now use  Ornn's  Living Forge's quick shop menu to forge items for his temporary inventory and waste his gold.(bug)"]}, {"about": "Blade of the Ruined King", "lines": ["Healing against minions reduced to 50% from 100%."]}, {"about": "Harrowed Path", "lines": ["Bonus movement speed increased to 25 / 27.5 / 30 / 32.5 / 35% from 20 / 22.5 / 25 / 27.5 / 30%.", "Initial missile range (for wall collision) increased to 775 from 700.", "Wall-spread missile speed increased to 1200 from 1000.", "Undocumented: Wall spread distance cap (each direction) increased to 8000 from 6000.", "Due to a bug, the changes to the wall-spread speed and distance were only applied to the counter-clockwise missile."]}]}, {"name": "Xayah", "changes": [{"about": "Double Daggers", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150 from 45 / 65 / 85 / 105 / 125."]}]}, {"name": "Sylas", "changes": [{"about": "Hijack", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer keeps  Rek'Sai's  Void Rush for one additional cast.", "Bug Fix: Hijacking  Jayce's ultimate while he is in Cannon Form once again gives Sylas  Transform Mercury Cannon, instead of  Transform Mercury Hammer, which would not give Sylas access to Jayce's melee abilities when cast, either."]}]}, {"name": "Dr. Mundo", "changes": [{"about": "Heart Zapper", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Once again heals back Dr. Mundo's grey health for hitting a champion."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Realm Warp", "lines": ["Bug Fix:  Channel is once again interrupted by activating  Zhonya's Hourglass or  Stopwatch.", "Channel is now also interrupted by an allied  Bard's  Tempered Fate.(bug)Ryze"]}]}]}
{"id": "V11.12", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V11.12", "date": "2021-06-09", "champions": [{"name": "Aphelios", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base magic resistance increased to 30 from 26.", "Attack damage growth increased to 3 from 2.4."]}, {"about": "Severum", "lines": ["Healing from basic attacks reduced to 3% - 10% (based on level) from 3% - 20% (based on level).", "Healing from spells increased to 9% - 30% (based on level) from 3% - 20% (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Onslaught", "lines": ["Attack speed ratio reduced to 2 per 100% bonus attack speed from 3.", "Base damage increased to 10 - 40 (based on level) from 10 - 30 (based on level).", "Bonus AD ratio changed to 20% - 35% (based on level) bonus AD from 21% - 30% (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Crescendum", "lines": ["Bonus damage reduced to 0% - 160% (based on number of Chakrams) AD from 0% - 164% (based on number of Chakrams) AD."]}, {"about": "Sentry", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 31 - 100 (based on level) from 25 - 85 (based on level).", "Bonus AD ratio increased to 40% - 60% (based on level) bonus AD) from 35% - 50% (based on level)."]}]}, {"name": "Dr. Mundo", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Complete visual upgrade across all skins.", "New splash artwork for  Original Dr. Mundo,  Toxic Dr. Mundo,  Corporate Mundo,  Mundo Mundo,  Executioner Mundo, and  Rageborn Mundo.", "Adjusted splash artwork for  TPA Mundo,  Pool Party Mundo,  El Macho Mundo, and  Frozen Prince Mundo.", "New lore.", "New voice-over.", "Stats", "Attack damage growth increased to 4.2 from 3.", "Base attack speed reduced to 0.67 from 0.721.", "Attack speed growth increased to 3.3% from 2.8%.", "Base armor reduced to 32 from 36."]}, {"about": "Goes Where He Pleases (Innate)", "lines": ["New Effect: Now periodically causes him to ignore the next  immobilizing effect.", "Preventing an effect makes him lose 7% of his current health and launches a canister that lands 525 units in the general direction of its source, remaining on the ground for 7 seconds. Dr. Mundo can pick it up to heal himself for 8% of his maximum health and reduce the cooldown of this effect by 15 seconds.", "Enemy champions can destroy the canister by walking over it before Dr. Mundo reaches it.", "Goes Where He Pleases' cooldown resets upon respawning.", "Cooldown: 45 - 15 (based on level) seconds.", "Health regeneration reduced to 2% maximum health from 2.5%."]}, {"about": "Infected Bonesaw (Q)", "lines": ["Health cost reduced to 50 at all ranks from 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90.", "Minimum damage increased to 80 / 135 / 190 / 245 / 300 from 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280.", "Maximum damage to monsters changed to 150 / 225 / 300 / 375 / 450 from 100 / 200 / 300 / 400 / 500.", "Removed: No longer restores health equal to the full health cost if Infected Bonesaw kills a non-champion.", "Removed: Damage is no longer capped at 100 / 200 / 300 / 400 / 500 against minions."]}, {"about": "Heart Zapper (W)", "lines": ["No longer a toggle spell.", "Removed: No longer grants 30% tenacity while toggled on.", "New Active: Dr. Mundo charges up a defibrillator for 4 seconds, dealing a total of 80 / 140 / 200 / 260 / 320 magic damage over the duration, with each tick occuring every 0.25 seconds, to nearby enemies and storing 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45% of the post-mitigation damage he takes. Heart Zapper can be recast after 1 second for the duration, and does so automatically at the end of the duration.", "New Recast: Dr. Mundo detonates the defibrillator, dealing 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 (+7% bonus health) magic damage to nearby enemies and  healing himself for 100% of all the damage stored if at least one enemy is hit, reduced to 50% if no  champion is hit.", "Health cost changed to 5% current health on-cast from 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 health per second while toggled on.", "Cooldown increased to 17 / 16.5 / 16 / 15.5 / 15 seconds from 4 seconds at all ranks."]}, {"about": "Blunt Force Trauma (E)", "lines