s at least  1, the first enemy  champion hit, including  dead ones, takes an insulting 1  true damage but also receives  1 from Samira.", "If cast while a  corpse of an enemy champion is within range, Samira will turn to face towards the closest one.", "This spell counts as an ability for  Daredevil Impulse.", "Target Range:  950.", "Width:  120.", "Width: 1400."]}]}, {"name": "Senna", "changes": [{"about": "Absolution", "lines": ["Mist Wraith spawn rate on minion and lesser monster kills reduced to 4.166% from 8.33%."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "Fleet of Foot", "lines": ["Bonus movement speed increased to 35 - 55 (based on level) from 30 - 50 (based on level)."]}]}, {"name": "Sylas", "changes": [{"about": "Hijack", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 100 / 70 / 40 seconds from 100 / 80 / 60."]}]}, {"name": "Syndra", "changes": [{"about": "Pool Party Syndra", "lines": [" Force of Will", "Bug Fix: Range indicator is no longer missing."]}]}, {"name": "Twisted Fate", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Basemovement speed reduced to 330 from 335."]}]}, {"name": "Udyr", "changes": [{"about": "Phoenix Stance", "lines": ["Cone base damage increased to 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 / 310 from 50 / 95 / 140 / 185 / 230 / 275.", "AP ratio increased to 70% AP from 60% AP."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Final Hour", "lines": ["Bonus attack damage increased to 35 / 50 / 65 from 25 / 40 / 55."]}]}, {"name": "Yone", "changes": [{"about": "Fate Sealed", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Allied party indicator no longer displays green when on cooldown."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "Riposte", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Reverting a bugfix from V10.18 that attempted to fix a bug where Fiora would trigger her enemy's Vitals through a Spell Shield. The bugfix introduced a new bug that would negatively impact Fiora's play in Worlds, so while this bug will be fixed in the future, any changes to her this patch will be reverted."]}]}, {"name": "Rek'Sai", "changes"