bug where he would not deal damage to all enemies with a stolen  Karthus'  Requiem."]}]}, {"name": "Syndra", "changes": [{"about": "Scatter the Weak", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14 seconds from 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12."]}]}, {"name": "Talon", "changes": [{"about": "Noxian Diplomacy", "lines": ["Mana cost increased to 40 from 30.", "Heal reduced to 10 - 70 (based on level) from 20 - 71 (based on level)."]}]}, {"name": "Tristana", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack speed increased to 0.679 to 0.656.", "Attack speed ratio increased to 0.679 to 0.656."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health increased to 612 from 582.", "Health growth increased to 86 from 84."]}]}, {"name": "Varus", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health increased to 530 from 500.", "Health growth increased to 91 from 89."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Tumble", "lines": ["AD ratio increased to 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80% AD from 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70% AD."]}]}, {"name": "Volibear", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Title changed to the Relentless Storm from the Thunder's Roar.", "Complete visual upgrade across all skins.", "New skin:  The Thousand-Pierced Bear.", "New splash artwork for  Original Volibear,  Thunder Lord Volibear,  Northern Storm Volibear, and  Runeguard Volibear.", "Adjusted splash artwork for  Captain Volibear and  El Rayo Volibear.", "New lore.", "New voice-over."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 580 from 584.48.", "Health growth reduced to 85 from 86.", "Base mana increased to 350 from 270.4.", "Mana growth increased to 40 from 30.", "Base armor reduced to 31 from 35.", "Base magic resistance reduced to 32 from 32.1.", "Base health regeneration increased to 9 from 8.", "Health regeneration growth increased to 0.75 from 0.65.", "Base mana regeneration reduced to 6.25 from 8.092.", "Mana regeneration growth reduced to 0.5 from 0.65.", "Base attack damage reduced to 60 from 68.", "Attack damage growth reduced to 3 from 3.3.", "Base attack speed increased to 0.66 from 0.658.", "Attack speed ratio increased to 0.7 from 0.658.", "Attack speed growth reduced to 2% from 2.67%.", "Base attack range increased to 150 from 125.", "Base movement speed reduced to 340 from 345."]}, {"about": "The Relentless Storm (Innate)", "lines": ["Innate: Volibear gains 1 stack of The Relentless Storm whenever he damages an enemy with  basic attacks on-hit and abilities, up to a maximum of 5. The Relentless Storm lasts for 6 seconds, refreshing whenever Volibear gains a stack. At maximum stacks, he gains Lightning Claws.", "The Relentless Storm: Volibear gains 5% bonus attack speed per stack, up to 25% bonus attack speed.", "Lightning Claws: Volibear's claws ignite with lightning, causing his basic attacks on-hit to deal 11 - 60 (based on level) (+40% AP) bonus magic damage to the target and the closest  visible enemy within 450 units of the target, chaining up to 4 subsequent targets.", "Effect Radius: 450."]}, {"about": "Thundering Smash (Q)", "lines": ["Active: Volibear drops on all fours, becoming  ghosted and gaining 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% bonus movement speed for 4 seconds, doubled when moving towards  visible enemy  champions.", "While active, Volibear's next basic attack within the duration  pounces on the target, deals 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 (+120% bonus AD) bonus physical damage, and  stuns the target for 1 second.", "If Volibear becomes  immobilized while Thundering Smash is active, the effect ends prematurely and the cooldown is reset.", "Thundering Smash  resets Volibear's basic attack timer, benefits from life steal and is affected by  critical strike modifiers.", "Mana Cost: 50.", "Cooldown: 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 seconds."]}, {"about": "Frenzied Maul (W)", "lines": ["Active: Volibear strikes the target enemy, dealing 10 / 35 / 60 / 85 / 110 (+100% AD) (+6% of his bonus health) physical damage, applying  on-hit effects, and Wounding them for 8 seconds.", "If Frenzied Maul targets a Wounded enemy, Volibear bites the target, dealing  50% increased damage and  healing himself for 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 (+8 / 10 / 12 / 14 / 16% of his missing health). The heal is halved against  minions.", "Frenzied Maul also benefits from life steal.", "Mana Cost: 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50.", "Cooldown: 5 seconds.", "Target Range:  325 / 350.", "Cast Time: 0.25 seconds."]}, {"about": "Sky Splitter (E)", "lines": ["Active: Volibear summons a lightning bolt to strike at the target location after a 2-second delay. Enemies can see the cast location indicator after a 1-second delay. If Volibear is within the lightning strike, he  shields himself for 15% of his maximum health (+80% AP) for 3 seconds.", "The lightning bolt deals 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+80% AP) (+7 / 8.5 / 10 / 11.5 / 13% of target's maximum health) magic damage to all enemies struck, capped at 100 / 200 / 300 / 400 / 500 against non-champions,  slowing them by 40% for 2 seconds, and grants  sight of the area for X seconds.", "Mana Cost: 60.", "Cooldown: 15 seconds.", "Target Range: 1200.", "Effect Radius:  325 / 425."]}, {"about": "Stormbringer (R)", "lines": ["Active: Volibear gains Stormbringer for 12 seconds and  leaps to the target location with  immunity to crowd control as well as granting  sight of the area in a 500 radius during it. If  Thundering Smash is active when Stormbringer is cast, its duration is refreshed.", "Stormbringer: Volibear becomes  ghosted and gains 200 / 400 / 600 bonus health, 50 bonus attack range, 25 increased range on  Frenzied Maul, and 25% increased size.", "Volibear impacts after a 1-second delay,  slowing all enemies in an area by 50%, decaying over 1 second. Enemies in the epicenter are also dealt 250 / 475 / 700 (+250% bonus AD) (+125% AP) physical damage.", "Volibear also disables enemy  turrets in an area for 2 / 4 / 6 seconds, dealing them the same physical damage.", "Stormbringer will cast at 