{"id": "V10.7", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V10.7", "date": "2020-04-01", "champions": [{"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Perfect Execution", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 100 / 80 / 60 seconds from 120 / 90 / 60."]}]}, {"name": "Corki", "changes": [{"about": "Special Delivery", "lines": ["Minimum DoT duration increased to 2 seconds from 1.5."]}]}, {"name": "Draven", "changes": [{"about": "Blood Rush", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer cancels basic attack animation."]}]}, {"name": "Fiddlesticks", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Title changed to the Ancient Fear from the Harbinger of Doom.", "Complete visual upgrade across all skins.", "New artwork for  Original Fiddlesticks,  Spectral Fiddlesticks,  Union Jack Fiddlesticks,  Bandito Fiddlesticks,  Pumpkinhead Fiddlesticks,  Fiddle Me Timbers,  Surprise Party Fiddlesticks and  Dark Candy Fiddlesticks.", "Tweaked artwork for  Risen Fiddlesticks and  Praetorian Fiddlesticks.", "New voice over and separate voice overs for Praetorian and Surprise Party.", "New lore."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 55.36 from 48.36.", "Base armor increased to 34 from 30.", "Base health increased to 580.4 from 524.4.", "Health growth increased to 92 from 80."]}, {"about": "A Harmless Scarecrow (Innate)", "lines": ["Innate - Scarecrow Effigy: Fiddlesticks starts each game with an exclusive  Scarecrow Effigy, which permanently occupies his trinket slot.", " Scarecrow Effigy: Consume a charge to place a visible  Effigy at the target location (X range), which reveals the surrounding area. The effigy visually appears exactly as  Fiddlesticks does to enemies. Enemy  champions that approach an effigy will activate it, causing the effigy to fake a random action, after which the effigy will deal 1 damage to itself. Stores one charge every 115 - 30 (based on level) seconds, up to 2 maximum charges.", "Innate - A Harmless Scarecrow: Starting from level 6, placing an  effigy grants  obscured vision of the revealed area as well as  reveal and  disable enemy  wards near it for 6 seconds."]}, {"about": "Terrify (Q)", "lines": ["Active: Passive: All enemy units are afflicted with Dread when Fiddlesticks is out of combat for 2.5 seconds and is unseen by enemy champions. Fiddlestick's next damaging ability against an enemy affected by Dread will  fear them for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds. This effect can trigger against multiple enemies for area of effect abilities.", "Active: Fiddlesticks shrieks at the target enemy, which, after a 0.4 seconds delay, deal 6 / 7 / 8 / 9 / 10% (+2% per 100 AP) of target's current health magic damage and  fears them for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds,  slowing them by 90% . Terrify has a minimum damage threshold of 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120, and is capped at 400 against monsters.", "Enemies can only be  feared by Terrify once every few seconds. If the target of Terrify's active has recently been feared, Terrify's damage and minimum damage threshold are doubled.", "Mana Cost: 65.", "Cooldown: 15 / 14.5 / 14 / 13.5 / 13 seconds.", "On-Target Cooldown: 15 / 14.5 / 14 / 13.5 / 13 seconds.", "Target Range: 575.", "Cast Time: 0.4 seconds."]}, {"about": "Bountiful Harvest (W)", "lines": ["Active: Fiddlesticks  tethers itself to all nearby enemies and  channels for up to 2 seconds. While channeling, tethered enemies are  revealed as it siphons their souls, dealing magic damage to them every 0.25 seconds, with the last tick dealing 12.5 / 20 / 27.5 / 35 / 42.5 (+8.25% AP) (+12 / 13 / 14 / 15 / 16% of target's missing health) magic damage. Deals a total of 100 / 160 / 220 / 280 / 340 (+70% AP) (+12 / 13 / 14 / 15 / 16% of target's missing health) magic damage. Total damage is reduced to 40% against minions.", "Fiddlesticks  heals itself for 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% of the pre-mitigation damage dealt, reduced to 15% against  minions.", "If all targets break their tethers by moving out of range, the ability ends immediately. If the ability is fully channeled or all targets are slain, 60% of the remaining cooldown is refunded.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80.", "Cooldown: 9 / 8.5 / 8 / 7.5 / 7 seconds.", "Effect Radius: 575.", "Tether Radius: 850.", "Cast Time: 0.1 seconds."]}, {"about": "Reap (E)", "lines": ["Active: Fiddlesticks swings with its scythe in a crescent-shaped area on the target location, dealing 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 / 190 (+50% AP) magic damage and  slowing enemies hit by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% for 1.25 seconds.", "Enemies hit in the center of the area are also  silenced for 1.25 seconds.", "Mana Cost: 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60.", "Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 seconds.", "Target Range: 850."]}, {"about": "Crowstorm (R)", "lines": ["Active: After  channeling for 1.5 seconds, Fiddlesticks  blinks to the target location with a murder of crows flying wildly around it for 5 seconds, dealing magic damage to nearby enemies every 0.25 seconds. Deals a maximum of 625 / 1125 / 1625 (+225% AP) magic damage.", "Mana Cost: 100.", "Cooldown: 140 / 110 / 80 seconds.", "Target Range: 800.", "Effect Radius: 600."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "Hero's Entrance", "lines": ["New Effect: On cast, now grants  Shield of Durand's passive magic damage shield to all allied champions in the area he casted it at for 5 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Perseverance", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 8 seconds from 7."]}, {"about": "Decisive Strike", "lines": ["Bonus movement speed duration changed to 1 / 1.65 / 2.3 / 2.95 / 3.6 seconds from 1.5 / 2 / 2.5 / 3 / 3.5."]}]}, {"name": "Ivern", "changes": [{"about": "Triggerseed", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 / 170 from 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140."]}, {"about": "Daisy!", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 140 / 130 / 120 seconds from 160 / 140 / 120."]}]}, {"name": "Kai'Sa", "changes": [{"about": "Supercharge", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 seconds from 16 / 15.5 / 15 