0% of Comet Spear's cooldown.", "If Pantheon is interrupted during the charge, or the charge completes without reactivation, Comet Spear is cancelled and the ability is put on full cooldown but refunds half the mana cost. Comet Spear's total damage is reduced by 10% against  minions and by 15% against  monsters.", " Mortal Will: Deals an additional 20 - 240 (based on level) (+100% bonus AD) bonus physical damage, affected by the previous damage reductions, to all enemies hit and  slows them by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% for 2.5 seconds.", "Mana Cost: 40.", "Cooldown: 10 / 9.5 / 9 / 8.5 / 8 seconds.", "Target Range: 575 / 1200 (based on channel time).", "Width: 120.", "Speed: 1500."]}, {"about": "Shield Vault (W)", "lines": ["Active: Pantheon  dashes to the target enemy unit, dealing them 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 (+100% AP) physical damage and  stunning them for 1 second.", " Mortal Will: Pantheon's next basic attack within 4 seconds strikes his target 3 times, dealing 50% AD physical damage per hit, up to 150% AD. Each hit applies on-hit effects.", "The ability can be dodged if the target moves 800 units away.", "Mana Cost: 55.", "Cooldown: 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 seconds.", "Target Range: 600."]}, {"about": "Aegis Assault (E)", "lines": ["Active: Pantheon braces his shield for 1.5 seconds in the target direction while striking in a cone, during which he is slowed for between 0% - 50% based on his movement direction relative to the shield's facing direction. Aegis Assault cannot be interrupted by crowd control.", "For the duration, Pantheon is  invulnerable against damage dealt by enemies in the target direction, and deals [up to 100% AD physical damage over the duration][8.3% AD physical damage every 0.125 seconds] to all enemies struck, reduced by 50% against  minions, and by 33.3% against  non-epic monsters.", "At the end of the duration or upon reactivation after 0.3 seconds, Pantheon slams with his shield after a 0.25 second delay, dealing 55 / 105 / 155 / 205 / 255 (+150% bonus AD) physical damage.", " Mortal Will: Aegis Assault's duration is increased to 2.5 seconds, dealing [up to 166.6% AD physical damage over the duration][13.8% AD physical damage every 0.125 seconds].", "Mana Cost: 80.", "Cooldown: 22 / 20.5 / 19 / 17.5 / 16 seconds.", "Target Range: 400."]}, {"about": "Grand Starfall (R)", "lines": ["Active: Pantheon  channels for 2 seconds to leap high into the air, then marks and reveals his destination before crashing down along the target area 2.4 seconds later. He remains  vanished until the landing is complete.", "The landing deals 300 / 500 / 700 (+100% AP) magic damage, decreased by up to 50% at the edges of the area.", "Grand Starfall instantly readies  Mortal Will.", "Grand Starfall's cooldown is reduced to 30 seconds if the channel is interrupted or canceled.", "Mana Cost: 100.", "Cooldown: 180 / 165 / 150 seconds.", "Target Range: 5500 / 2000.", "Effect Radius: 450.", "Inner Radius: 125."]}]}, {"name": "Poppy", "changes": [{"about": "Heroic Charge", "lines": ["Bug Fix:  Phase Rush and  Electrocute activates properly when she casts Heroic Charge in specific combos."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "Broken Wings", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 12 seconds at all ranks from 12 / 11.5 / 11 / 10.5 / 10."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "Fury of the North", "lines": ["Bonus armor changed to 10 (+35% bonus armor) from 20 (+25% bonus armor).", "Bonus magic resistance changed to 10 (+35% bonus magic resistance) from 20 (+25% bonus magic resistance)."]}, {"about": "Arctic Assault", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 seconds from 17 / 15.5 / 14 / 12.5 / 11."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Twilight Assault", "lines": ["Increased health ratio increased to 5 / 5.5 / 6 / 6.5 / 7% of his target's maximum health from 4 / 4.5 / 5 / 5.5 / 6%."]}, {"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160 from 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150