ock (Innate)", "lines": ["Innate: Yuumi periodically empowers her next basic attack against an enemy champion to restore 30 - 160 (based on level) mana and grant her a 50 - 330 (based on level) (+40% AP) shield that lasts until it is broken.", "While  Attached, the shield transfers to her Anchor.", "Static Cooldown: 20 - 8 (based on level) seconds."]}, {"about": "Prowling Projectile (Q)", "lines": ["Active: Yuumi fires an errant missile that deals 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 (+30% AP) magic damage to the first enemy hit.", "If the missile is in flight for 1 second, it instead deals 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 / 260 (+60% AP) magic damage and  slows by 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80%, decaying over 1 / 1.1 / 1.2 / 1.3 / 1.4 / 1.5 seconds, to enemy  champions struck.", "While  Attached, Yuumi directs the trajectory of the missile instead for up to 3 seconds before fizzling.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 / 85.", "Cooldown: 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 seconds."]}, {"about": "You and Me! (W)", "lines": ["Passive: Yuumi and her Anchor gain bonus attack damage or ability power (Adaptive) equal to a percentage of the other's highest stat (bonus AD = 3 / 5.4 / 7.8 / 10.2 / 12.6%, bonus AP = 5 / 9 / 13 / 17 / 21%). Additionally, Yuumi starts with a point in You and Me! and  Prowling Projectile instead has 6 ranks.", "Active: Yuumi  dashes to an allied champion and attaches to them. While Attached, Yuumi is  untargetable except from  turrets and follows her Anchor's movement, losing the ability to attack but retaining the ability to cast (except movement spells).", "Active - Change of Plan: Yuumi can switch her Anchor at no cooldown, and will detach automatically if her Anchor dies. If re-activated without a valid target, Yuumi will detach from her Anchor and dash up to 250 units in the target direction.", "Static Cooldown: 10 / 5 / 0 (based on level) seconds."]}, {"about": "Zoomies (E)", "lines": ["Passive: Yuumi periodically stores a Zoomies charge, up to 2 stored at once.", "Active: Yuumi  heals herself for 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 (+10% AP), with the base amount increased by 0% - 100% (based on target's missing health) and the scaling amount increased by 0% - 300% (based on target's missing health), up to 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 (+40% AP), and gains 25% (+10% per 100 AP) bonus movement speed decaying over 2 seconds.", "While  Attached, her partner is targeted by the ability instead.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100.", "Cooldown: 0.5 seconds.", "Recharge: 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14 seconds."]}, {"about": "Final Chapter (R)", "lines": ["Active: Yuumi  recoils X units in the opposite direction, after which Book launches 7 waves over 3.5 seconds, each dealing 60 / 100 / 140 (+20% AP) magic damage. Enemy  champions hit take only 40% damage from subsequent waves, and when struck with three waves, they are  rooted for 1.75 seconds.", "Yuumi can move and cast both  You and Me! and  Zoomies during Final Chapter.", "Mana Cost: 100.", "Cooldown: 130 / 120 / 110 / 100 / 90 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "Garden of Thorns", "lines": ["Damage from basic attacks that doesn't trigger on-hit effects (ex.  Corki's  Hextech Munitions,  Miss Fortune's  Love Tap, etc.) no longer deals a separate instance of damage to her plants."]}]}, {"name": "Yuumi", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base mana regeneration increased to 10 from 7.5."]}, {"about": "Bop 'n' Block", "lines": ["Mana restored increased to 40 - 160 (based on level) from 30 - 160 (based on level).", "Base shield strength increased to 80 - 360 (based on level) from 50 - 330 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Prowling Projectile", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 / 165 from 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140.", "AP ratio increased to 45% AP from 30% AP.", "Empowered base damage increased to 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 / 285 from 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 / 260.", "Slow strength increased to 40 / 48 / 56 / 64 / 72 / 80% from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60