yle ascends into a new form, gaining additional bonuses.", "Aflame - Level 6: While Exalted, Kayle's basic attacks additionally launch a wave of fire in the target's direction, dealing 10 - 30 (based on  Starfire Spellblade's Rank) (+10% AD) (+20% AP) magic damage to enemies hit.", "Arisen - Level 11: Kayle becomes a  ranged champion with 550 attack range. Additionally, Zealous's bonus attack speed is increased to 10% bonus attack speed, for a maximum of 50% bonus attack speed.", "Transcendent - Level 16: Kayle permanently has full Zealous stacks and is permanently Exalted. Additionally, Aflame's fiery waves now deal true damage."]}, {"about": "Radiant Blast (Q)", "lines": ["Active: Kayle plants a portal at her initial location that faces the target direction. After a 0.5-second delay, a celestial sword launches forward from the portal.", "The sword explodes into a cross upon collision with an enemy, dealing 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+60% bonus AD) (+50% AP) magic damage and  slowing targets struck by 26 / 32 / 38 / 44 / 50%, while reducing their armor and magic resistance by 20% for 3 seconds.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80.", "Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds."]}, {"about": "Celestial Blessing (W)", "lines": ["Active: Kayle and target allied champion are  healed for 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+30% AP) health and gain 26 / 32 / 38 / 44 / 50% (+10% per 100 AP) bonus movement speed for 2 seconds.", "If cast without a valid target, or self-cast, Celestial Blessing will automatically target the most wounded ally in range.", "Target Range: 900.", "Mana Cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90.", "Cooldown: 15 seconds."]}, {"about": "Starfire Spellblade (E)", "lines": ["Passive: Kayle's basic attacks deal 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 (+10% AD) (+20% AP) bonus magic damage. Additionally,  Aflame's base damage is increased.", "Active: Kayle's next basic attack within 6 seconds deals 10 / 12.5 / 15 / 17.5 / 20% of target's missing health bonus magic damage. While  Aflame, it also damages enemies surrounding the target.", "Prior to becoming  Arisen, Starfire Spellblade also causes Kayle to become a  ranged champion with 550 attack range on the empowered attack.", "Mana Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70.", "Cooldown: 8 seconds."]}, {"about": "Divine Judgment (R)", "lines": ["Active: Kayle conjures swords around the target allied champion or herself over 1.5 seconds, after which she brings them crashing to the ground, dealing magic damage to all enemies in the area.", "Divine Judgment also grants the target  invulnerability for 2 / 2.5 / 3 seconds.", "Target Range: 900.", "Mana Cost: 100.", "Cooldown: 160 / 120 / 80 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Lucian", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Clearer hit audio on basic attacks."]}, {"about": "Lightslinger", "lines": ["Clearer hit audio."]}, {"about": "Ardent Blaze", "lines": ["All skins except  High Noon Lucian have cast audio shimmerier, deep tones on travel audio reduced, and target hit sound added.  Heartseeker Lucian on-hit sound is unchanged."]}, {"about": "Relentless Pursuit", "lines": ["Dash audio brightened."]}, {"about": "The Culling", "lines": ["Clearer hit audio."]}, {"about": "Striker Lucian", "lines": ["Clearer hit audio on basic attacks.", " Lightslinger", "Clearer hit audio.", " Relentless Pursuit", "Dash audio brightened.", " The Culling", "Clearer hit audio."]}]}, {"name": "Lux", "changes": [{"about": "Lunar Empress Lux", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Textures no longer becomes corrupted upon death."]}]}, {"name": "Morgana", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Title changed to the Fallen from Fallen Angel.", "Complete visual upgrade across all skins.", "New artwork for  Original Morgana,  Blackthorn Morgana,  Exiled Morgana,  Blade Mistress Morgana, and  Sinful Succulence Morgana.", "Tweaked artwork for  Ghost Bride Morgana,  Lunar Wraith Morgana,  Bewitching Morgana, and  Victorious Morgana.", "New voice over.", "New lore."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 56 from 55.46.", "Base armor reduced to 25 from 25.384.", "Base health increased to 560 from 559.48.", "Base mana reduced to 340 from 340.8.", "Base movement speed reduced to 330 from 335."]}, {"about": "Tormented Shadow", "lines": ["Renamed to Tormented Shadow from Tormented Soil.", "Minimum base damage reduced to 12 / 24 / 36 / 48 / 60 from 16 / 32 / 48 / 64 / 80.", "Minimum AP ratio reduced to 16% AP from 22% AP.", "Bonus damage increased to 0% - 170% (based on target's missing health) from 0% - 50% (based on target's missing health).", "Maximum base damage increased to 32.4 / 64.8 / 97.2 / 129.6 / 162 from 24 / 48 / 72 / 96 / 120.", "Maximum AP ratio increased to 43% AP from 33% AP."]}, {"about": "Soul Shackles", "lines": ["New Effect: Now grants 5 / 30 / 55% bonus movement speed towards enemies that are shackled.", "New ability icon."]}]}, {"name": "Neeko", "changes": [{"about": "Tangle-Barbs", "lines": ["Removed: Champion hit condition removed.", "Enemies hit to empower missile reduced to 1 from 2.", "Root duration increased to 0.7 / 0.9 / 1.1 / 1.3 / 1.5 seconds from 0.5 at all ranks.", "The first unit hit is rooted for 0.7 / 0.9 / 1.1 / 1.3 / 1.5 seconds, while all the others are rooted for 1.8 / 2.1 / 2.4 / 2.7 / 3 seconds.", "Bug Fix: No longer disarms enemies."]}]}, {"name": "Nunu & Willump", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 570 from 590."]}, {"about": "Consume", "lines": ["Base non-champion healing reduced to 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 / 215 from 75 / 120 / 165 / 210 / 255."]}]}, {"name": "Rakan", "changes": [{"about": "Grand Entrance", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 70 / 120 / 170 / 220 / 270 from 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250.", "Dash speed increased to 1500 from 1400 (+ 0 / 45 / 80 (based on type of boots))."]}]}, {"name": "Rengar", "changes": [{"about": "Thrill of the Hunt", "lines": ["Bug Fix: True sight indicator from the ability is no longer misplaced on  Star Guardian Ezreal."]}]}, {"name": "Skarner", "changes"