no longer reduced by 25%.", "Crowd control duration against secondary targets increased to 0.75 seconds from 0.25.", "Knock aside distance against secondary targets increased to 350 units from 250."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "Eulogy of the Isles", "lines": ["Maiden of the Mist base damage reduced to 0 / 10 / 40 from 10 / 20 / 40.", "Bonus damage against Maiden of the Mist's target reduced to 3 / 6 / 9% of target's maximum health from 5 / 7.5 / 10%."]}]}, {"name": "Neeko", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack speed growth reduced to 1.5% from 3.5%.", "Attack damage growth reduced to 2 from 3."]}, {"about": "Shapesplitter", "lines": ["Base passive damage reduced to 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 from 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170."]}]}]}
