n increased to 3 seconds from 2.", "Bonus movement speed duration increased to 3 seconds from 2.", "New Effect: The clone now travels in the target direction until it runs into terrain, rather than pathing to the target location.", "Bug Fix: On-hit damage now works on turrets again."]}, {"about": "Pop Blossom", "lines": ["Removed: No longer slows by 40% as she leaps into the air.", "Leap duration reduced to 0.6 seconds from 0.75.", "Bug Fix: Tooltip now correctly shows the AP ratio."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": [{"about": "Prowl", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Basic attack no longer cancels if a Hunt activates mid-attack animation."]}]}, {"name": "Ornn", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health increased to 590 from 565.64.", "Base armor increased to 36 from 33.04."]}]}, {"name": "Rakan", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Recommended items updated."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base armor reduced to 29 from 33."]}, {"about": "Grand Entrance", "lines": ["Dash speed changed to 1400 (+ 0 / 45 / 80 (based on type of boots)) from 2050 (+30% movement speed).", "Delay on arrival before impact reduced to 0.35 seconds from 0.5."]}, {"about": "The Quickness", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug that caused it to sometimes not affect his basic attack target."]}]}, {"name": "Rek'Sai", "changes": [{"about": "Queen's Wrath", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Attacks now interact properly with  Hail of Blades."]}]}, {"name": "Shyvana", "changes": [{"about": "Fury of the Dragonborn", "lines": ["Bonus physical and magical damage to  dragons and  Vilemaw increased to 20% from 10%."]}, {"about": "Flame Breath", "lines": ["Bonus damage against marked enemies increased to 3.25% of target's maximum health from 2.5%."]}]}, {"name": "Sylas", "changes": [{"about": "Petricite Burst (Innate)", "lines": ["Innate: After casting a spell, Sylas' next basic attack is modified to whirl his chains around him, dealing 5 - 48 (based on level) (+100% AD) (+20% AP) magic damage to the target and 