rs an arc, together forming a full circle of cover around him. Each shotgun has one shell and an individual reload timer of 30 / 25 / 20 / 15 / 10 (based on level) seconds.", "The next basic attack in the direction of a loaded shotgun causes it to fire, dealing 40 - 100 (based on level)% AD (+4.5 / 5.25 / 6 / 7 / 8 (based on level)% of target's maximum health) physical damage to all enemies hit within, up to 25 - 365 (based on level) against monsters.", "Echoing Flames deals 10% reduced damage to enemies recently damaged in the last 5 seconds, stacking up to 3 times."]}, {"about": "Corrosive Charge - Q spell", "lines": ["Active: Urgot launches a canister at the target location that explodes after a brief delay, dealing 25 / 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 (+70% AD) physical damage and  slowing all enemies hit by 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65% for 1 second.", "Mana Cost: 55", "Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds"]}, {"about": "Purge - W spell", "lines": ["Passive: Urgot's other abilities apply Purge to enemy champions for a few seconds.", "Active: Urgot shields himself for 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+30% bonus health) and autonomously attacks the nearest enemy for the next 4 seconds, without interrupting his movement, prioritizing enemy champions marked for Purging.", "Urgot attacks with 3.0 attack speed but deals 12 (+20 / 24 / 28 / 32 / 36% AD) physical damage, with only 33.3% on-hit damage and cannot  critically strike. Attacks deal a minimum of 50 damage against minions.", "While active, Urgot also gains 40% slow resistance and  ghost versus non-champions but attacking reduces his base movement speed by 125 for 1 second.", "Mana Cost: 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65", "Cooldown: 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 seconds"]}, {"about": "Disdain - E spell", "lines": ["Active: After a brief delay, Urgot dashes in the target direction, dealing 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 (+50% AD) physical damage to all enemies in the way and  knocking them aside.", "Urgot comes to a stop upon colliding with an enemy champion,  stunning them for 0.75 seconds and  flinging them over himself.", "Mana Cost: 50", "Cooldown: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 seconds"]}, {"about": "Fear Beyond Death - R spell", "lines": ["First Cast: Urgot fires a chem-drill forward that impales the first enemy champion struck, dealing physical damage, leashing them for 3 seconds and  slowing them by 0% - 75% (based on target's missing health).", "If the target is below 25% of their maximum health, Fear Beyond Death can be re-activated, and automatically does so after 3 seconds if the target is within the threshold.", "Second Cast: Urgot begins channeling as he launches chains at the target,  suppressing them on impact and reeling them in over X seconds, during which they are untargetable by other effects.", "The channel can only be interrupted by Urgot's death. If the channel is successful, the target is executed and surrounding enemies are  terrified for 1.5 seconds.", "Mana Cost: 100", "Cooldown: 120 / 95 / 70 seconds"]}]}, {"name": "Xerath", "changes": [{"about": "Eye of Destruction", "lines": ["Slow increased to 25% from 10%."]}, {"about": "Rite of the Arcane", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 200 / 240 / 280 from 200 / 230 / 260."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Stretching Strikes", "lines": ["Current health cost increased to 8% current health from 4% current health.", "Cooldown increased to 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 seconds from 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8."]}, {"about": "Unstable Matter", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 15 / 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 from 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90."]}, {"about": "Elastic Slingshot", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he could channel Elastic Slingshot while under hard crowd control effects if he used it right before they were applied."]}, {"about": "Special Weapon Zac", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Recall's audio has been restored."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Satchel Charge", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 24 / 21 / 18 / 15 / 12 seconds from 26 / 24 / 22 / 20 / 18."