aking collision more consistent.", "Bug Fix: Rammus can now interact with Plants during Powerball"]}, {"about": "Defensive Ball Curl", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 6 seconds from 14.", "Bonus armor changed to 20 (+50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70% armor) from 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120.", "Bonus magic resistance changed to 20 (+50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70% magic resistance) from 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120.", "New Effect: Now slows Rammus by 60% during the effect.", "New Effect: Can be toggled off early.", "Damage when attacked changed to  Spiked Shell's damage from 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 (+10% armor)."]}, {"about": "Frenzying Taunt", "lines": ["Renamed Frenzying Taunt from Puncturing Taunt.", "Removed: Reduces the target's armor by 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25.", "New Effect: Grants 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% bonus attack speed for the duration of the taunt.", "New Effect: Attack speed bonus constantly refreshes while any of Rammus' other spells are active."]}, {"about": "Tremors", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 40 / 80 / 120 from 65 / 130 / 195.", "AP ratio reduced to 20% AP from 30% AP.", "New Effect: Slow enemies it damage by 8 / 10 / 12% for 1.5 seconds, stacking up to 8 times, up to a maximum of 64 / 80 / 96%.", "New Effect: Deals double damage to structures.", "Damage against structure per second increased to 80 / 160 / 240 (+40% AP) from 65 / 130 / 195 (+30% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "Ruthless Predator", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Ruthless Predator's lockout time was shorter than intended (0.525 seconds instead of 0.75).", "Bug Fix: Fury-empowered casts no longer generate Fury.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where, when casting Ruthless Predator and queueing either  Cull the Meek or  Dice while at 100 Fury, the queued ability would sometimes not be empowered or consume Fury."]}, {"about": "Slice and Dice", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Slice and Dice's ranges were shorter than intended (400 instead of 450).", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Slice and Dice's dash speeds were slower than intended (650 instead of 750)."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect:  Runic Blade's buff duration,  Broken Wings' recast window, and  Blade of the Exile's buff duration are now tracked as timers overlaid above their ability icons, rather than via buff bar icons."]}, {"about": "Runic Blade", "lines": ["New Effect: Stacks are now tracked below her health bar and are only visible to Riven."]}, {"about": "Broken Wings", "lines": ["The timing around when Riven becomes able to animation cancel Q casts, as well as how long she has to animation cancel, have both been made more consistent.", "New Effect: Can no longer joke, taunt, or laugh during Broken Wings's animations.", "New Effect: Can more reliably target units on high-latency environments.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where the knockback on Broken Wings's third cast ended sooner than intended if it interrupted a different displacement effect or if the target collided with terrain."]}, {"about": "Valor", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where spell queueing sometimes didn't properly work when casting Valor during  Broken Wings' animation."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "SKT T1 Ryze", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Broccoli is now properly centered during his recall animation."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "Fury of the North", "lines": ["Frost Armor bonus resistances reduced to 20 / 60 / 100 (based on level) from 100 at all levels."]}, {"about": "Arctic Assault", "lines": ["Shifted slightly to address instances where Sejuani collided with targets behind her."]}, {"about": "Winter's Wrath", "lines": ["New Effect: Cooldown starts once both swings are complete instead of on-cast.", "Cooldown reduced to 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 seconds from 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6."]}]}, {"name": "Udyr", "changes": [{"about": "Tiger Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 45 - 28 (based on level) from 50 - 33 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Turtle Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 45 - 28 (based on level) from 50 - 33 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Bear Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 45 - 28 (based on level) from 50 - 33 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Phoenix Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 45 - 28 (based on level) from 50 - 33 (based on level)."]}]}, {"name": "Vi", "changes": [{"about": "Assault and Battery", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Will no longer carry her into the enemy fountain if her target  Recalls during the travel time."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": [{"about": "Wind Wall", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Enemies no longer lose spell shields when walking through the very edge of Wind Wall."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "Shepherd of Souls", "lines": ["New Effect: Mist Walkers no longer perish when they move too far away from Yorick or the  Maiden."]}, {"about": "Last Rites", "lines": ["New Effect: If it kills a unit when Yorick has max graves, the furthest grave will now be replaced rather than no grave being spawned."]}, {"about": "Eulogy of the Isles", "lines": ["New Effect: The Maiden's stats now increase when Yorick puts another skill point into Eulogy of the Isles, rather than remaining unchanged until Yorick summons her again."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Stretching Strikes", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 from 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130.", "New Effect: Damage now scales with 2.5% of Zac's maximum health.", "Second hit bonus attack range increased to 125 from 100.", "New Effect: Second part of the spell now always spawns a second blob if it hits a unique unit.", "Collision AoE size increased to 300 from 200.", "Bug Fix: If the second hit would kill a minion or monster, the target will now wait to die until after Zac has slammed it into Stretching Strikes' first target.", "New Effect: If the first target is standing on top of other enemies, the second hit will now reliably choose a different target than the first.", "New Effect: Can now cast  Unstable Matter and queue up  Elastic Slingshot during Stretching Strikes' second attack and while slamming two targets together."]}, {"about": "Elastic Slingshot", "lines": ["New Effect: Knockup duration now scales from 0.5 to 1 second base upon how long Zac charges before release."]}, {"about": "Let's Bounce!", "lines": ["Time to full charge time increased to 1.1 seconds from 1."]}]}, {"name": "Kled", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he wasn't gaining his flat bonus movement speed towards enemies while dismounted.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he wasn't moving the expected distance during his dismount."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": [{"about": "Sapling Toss", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug allowing it to be casted globally."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Let's Bounce!", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a visual bug where if he died while charging Let's Bounce!, his ult kidnap animation would play on top of him for the rest of the game."]}]}, {"name": "Ahri", "changes": [{"about": "Charm", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a few bugs with it interacting oddly with other effects."]}]}, {"name": "Rakan", "changes": [{"about": "The Quickness", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a few bugs with it interacting oddly with other effects."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Stretching Strikes", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 from 40 / 80 / 60 / 100 / 120."]}]}]}
{"id": "V7.9", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V7.9", "date": "2017-05-03", "champions": [{"name": "Amumu", "changes": [{"about": "Curse of the Sad Mummy", "lines": ["Bug Fix: VFX no longer appear in the wrong place if he flashes during its cast time.", "Bug Fix: VFX no longer stay on the map forever if he dies while casting it."]}]}, {"name": "Cho'Gath", "changes": [{"about": "Vorpal Spikes", "lines": ["Undocumented: Tooltip now mentions spikes apply spell effects."]}]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "Seastone Trident", "lines": ["New Effect: Damage-over-time ticks, including the initial application, no longer count as spell hits (matching similar persistent effects like  Teemo's  Toxic Shot)."]}]}, {"name": "Graves", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Removed: Queue multiple spells during his basic attack animation."]}]}, {"name": "Kalista", "changes": [{"about": "Sentinel", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug preventing  Rakan from reliably proccing soul-mark damage if he attacked too quickly after the mark was applied."]}]}, {"name": "Karma", "changes": [{"about": "Conqueror Karma", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed channeling animation (ex. when capturing  Skarner's  Crystal Spires)."]}]}, {"name": "Kayle", "changes": [{"about": "Righteous Fury", "lines": ["Undocumented: Tooltip now mentions active apply spell effects."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash artwork for  Charred,  Totemic and  Festive."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 540 from 572.2.", "Health growth increased to 95 from 90.", "Health regeneration reduced to 5 from 7.", "Base armor increased to 30 from 28.72."]}, {"about": "Sap Magic", "lines": ["Rework: Maokai gathers magical energy from the nature around him. Every few seconds, his next attack uses that energy to heal him for 10 - 130 (based on level) (+4.5 - 10.5 (based on level)% maximum health). Each time Maokai casts a spell or if struck by an enemy's spell, Sap Magic's cooldown is reduced by 4 seconds. Will not trigger if above 95% health.", "Static Cooldown: 30 / 25 / 20 (based on level) seconds"]}, {"about": "Bramble Smash", "lines": ["Renamed Bramble Smash from Arcane Smash.", "Cast time reduced to 0.35 seconds from 0.383.", "New Effect: Closer targets are knocked back slightly more.", "Slow increased to 99% at all ranks from 20 / 27 / 34 / 41 / 48%.", "Slow duration reduced to 0.25 seconds from 1.5."]}, {"about": "Twisted Advance", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 from 75.", "Damage changed to 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150 (+40% AP) from  9 / 10 / 11 / 12 / 13% (+3% per 100 AP) of target's maximum health.", "Root duration reduced to 1 / 1.1 / 1.2 / 1.3 / 1.4 seconds from 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2."]}, {"about": "Sapling Toss", "lines": ["New Effect: New ability icon.", "Mana cost reduced to 60 at all ranks from 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100.", "Cooldown reduced to 11 seconds from 12.", "Sapling duration reduced to 30 seconds at all ranks from 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60.", "Base damage reduced to 45 / 70 / 95 / 120 / 145 from 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240.", "Removed: Damage scaling with 60% AP.", "New Effect: Damage now scales with 6 / 6.5 / 7 / 7.5 / 8% (+2% per 100 AP) of target's maximum health.", "Slow reduced to 35% from 50%.", "Slow duration increased to 2 seconds from 1.", "New Effect: Sapling duration is increased to 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 seconds when placed in brush.", "New Effect: Sapling placed in brush deals double damage over 2 seconds to all enemies hit.", "New Effect: Damage is capped at 300 against non-champions, and 600 when placed in brush."]}, {"about": "Nature's Grasp", "lines": ["Rework: Maokai summons a colossal wall of brambles and thorns that slowly advances forwards, dealing 150 / 225 / 300 (+75% AP)  magic damage and rooting any enemies struck for 0.6 - 2.4 (based on distance traveled) seconds.", "Mana Cost: 100", "Cooldown: 120 / 110 / 100 seconds", "Range: 2500"]}]}, {"name": "Master Yi", "changes": [{"about": "Cosmic Blade Master Yi", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a Mac bug causing  Meditate and  Highlander visual effects to flicker rapidly in some situations."]}]}, {"name": "Rakan", "changes": [{"about": "Cosmic Dawn Rakan", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer leaves behind a purple ghost of himself after  Recalling.", "Bug Fix: No longer turns himself purple when his  Recall is cancelled.", "Bug Fix: Fixed  Recall and death audio."]}, {"about": "Gleaming Quill", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug that could cause it to cost no mana in certain situations."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["No longer ignores inputs during his ability's cast times. Once an ability has completed, he'll move on to the next queued action.", "Various buffs and timers tracked in the buff bar (ex. remaining time to cast  Dice) are now tracked on their respective ability icons instead."]}, {"about": "Reign of Anger", "lines": ["Bug Fix: First attack when (re)entering combat now properly grants the full 5 Fury."]}, {"about": "Cull the Meek", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Range now properly scales with all size-modifying effects, not just  Dominus.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where it wasn't hitting invisible units.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he could basic attack at the same time as Cull the Meek's damage was dealt."]}, {"about": "Slice and Dice", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a timing issue that could inconsistently cause Slice and Dice to not hit enemies Renekton passes through."]}, {"about": "Dominus", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer deals an extra tick of damage on-cast."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Spell Flux", "lines": ["New Effect: If target dies while the projectile is traveling, Spell Flux will still spread to nearby enemies."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Title changed to Fury of the North from The Winter's Wrath.", "New splash artwork for  Darkrider,  Sabretusk and  Traditional."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regeneration reduced to 8.5 from 8.675.", "Base mana regeneration reduced to 7 from 7.205.", "Mana regeneration increased to 0.7 from 0.45.", "Base armor reduced to 27 from 29.54.", "Armor growth increased to 4 from 3.", "Base attack range increased to 150 from 125.", "Base attack damage reduced to 56 from 57.544.", "Attack damage growth reduced to 3 from 3.3.", "Base attack speed reduced to 0.625 from 0.67.", "Attack speed growth increased to 3% from 1.45%."]}, {"about": "Fury of the North", "lines": ["Renamed Fury of the North from Frost Armor.", "Frost Armor: Sejuani receives Frost Armor if she hasn't taken damage in the last 9 seconds, lingering for 1 / 2 / 3 (based on level) seconds after taking damage from enemy champions. Frost Armor engulfs  Bristle in True Ice, becoming immune to  slows and gains 100 (+100% total armor) bonus armor and 100 (+100% total magic resistance) bonus magic resistance.", "Icebreaker: Enemies  stunned by Sejuani are frozen. Sejuani's next basic attack or ability against them deals 10 / 15 / 20 (based on level)% of their maximum health as bonus magic damage, or 400 against minions and monsters."]}, {"about": "Arctic Assault", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 from 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100.", "Cooldown reduced to 13 / 12.5 / 12 / 11.5 / 11 seconds from 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11.", "Base damage reduced to 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 from 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260.", "Knockup duration reduced to 0.5 seconds from 0.75.", "Removed: No longer knocks up enemies around the first target hit."]}, {"about": "Winter's Wrath", "lines": ["Renamed Winter's Wrath from Flail of the Northern Winds.", "New Effect: New ability icon.", "Mana cost increased to 60 at all ranks from 40 / 35 / 30 / 25 / 20.", "Cooldown reduced to 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 seconds from 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7.", "Damage type changed to physical from magic.", "Rework: After a 0.25-seconds delay, Sejuani swings her flail in a cone in the target direction, dealing 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 (+1.5% maximum health) physical damage to all enemies hit and  knocking back minions and monsters. She then lashes out with her flail after 0.75 seconds in a straight line in the same direction, dealing 40 / 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 (+4.5% maximum health) additional physical damage and briefly  slowing to all enemies hit. Sejuani can move freely during Winter's Wrath. Both swings will strike in the cast direction, but their hitboxes follow Sejuani's movement."]}, {"about": "Permafrost", "lines": ["New Effect: New ability icon.", "Mana cost reduced to 20 from 55.", "Cooldown reduced to 1.5 seconds at all ranks from 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6.", "New Effect: Winter's Wrath, Sejuani's and nearby  melee allied champions' basic attacks now apply Frost to enemy champions and large monsters.", "New Effect: Require 4 stacks of Frost to activate.", "Base damage reduced to 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 from 80 / 105 / 130 / 155 / 180.", "AP ratio reduced to 30% AP from 50% AP.", "New Effect: Now has a per-target cooldown of 10 / 9 / 8 (based on level) seconds.", "Removed: Slowing for 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70% for 1.5 seconds.", "New Effect: Activating Permafrost now stuns them for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds."]}, {"about": "Glacial Prison", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 120 / 100 / 80 seconds from 130 / 115 / 100.", "Rework: Sejuani throws a True Ice bola in a line, dealing 100 / 125 / 150 (+40% AP) magic damage and  stunning for 1 second the first enemy champion that collides with. The bola's base damage increases the further it travels, up to 150 / 187.5 / 225. If the bola travels before exploding it stuns enemies hit for 2 seconds. The bola shatters upon collision or reaching maximum range, creating a storm for 2 seconds,  slowing other enemies by 30%. At the end of the duration the storm shatters the ground, deals 150 / 250 / 350 (+80% AP) magic damage and  slowing by 80% for 3 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Shaco", "changes": [{"about": "Hallucinate", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Clone no longer crashes the game if it dies in the fountain on ARAM."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Twilight Assault", "lines": ["Removed: Empowered attacks counting as spell hits."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "Poison Trail", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Damage now increases as soon as he puts another skill point in it, rather than waiting until he toggles it off and on again."]}]}, {"name": "Udyr", "changes": [{"about": "Tiger Stance", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Damage over time no longer melts wards."]}]}, {"name": "Volibear", "changes": [{"about": "Frenzy", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Attack speed bonus now increases as soon as he puts another skill point into it, rather than waiting until the buff falls off and is reapplied."]}]}, {"name": "Xayah", "changes": [{"about": "Cosmic Dusk Xayah", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Splash art has been flipped in Xayah's AIR client champion info page so she's not covered up by the interface."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Zac's voice now changes in pitch and speed based on his current size.", "Many of Zac's idle, movement, and emote animations have also been updated."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 60 from 59.67.", "Base armor increased to 24 from 23.88.", "Base health increased to 615 from 614.6.", "Base health regeneration increased to 8 from 7.92.", "Health regeneration growth reduced to 0.5 from 0.55."]}, {"about": "Cell Division", "lines": ["New Effect: New ability icon."]}, {"about": "Stretching Strikes", "lines": ["Renamed Stretching Strikes from Stretching Strike.", "New Effect: New ability icon.", "Cooldown increased to 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds from 9 / 8.5 / 8 / 7.5 / 7.", "Rework: Zac's arm stretches and grabs the first enemy it hits, dealing 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 (+30% AP) magic damage and slowing them by 60% for 0.25 seconds. Zac's next basic attack has 100 bonus attack range and is replaced with a long range smack that repeats the initial magic damage and slow effect. If Zac grabs a different enemy with each attack he'll throw them towards each other, dealing 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 (+30% AP) magic damage in an area if they collide."]}, {"about": "Unstable Matter", "lines": ["New Effect: New ability icon."]}, {"about": "Elastic Slingshot", "lines": ["New Effect: New ability icon.", "Channel duration to reach maximum range reduced to 0.9 / 1 / 1.1 / 1.2 / 1.3 seconds from 0.9 / 1.05 / 1.2 / 1.35 / 1.5.", "Base damage reduced to 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 from 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280.", "Knockup duration reduced to 0.5 seconds from 1."]}, {"about": "Let's Bounce!", "lines": ["New Effect: New ability icon.", "Rework:", "First cast: Zac squishes himself down, making him immune to Crowd Control for up to 2.5 seconds. Any enemies standing on top of him are slowed by 30 / 40 / 50%.", "Second cast: Charging for at least 1 second before recasting causes Zac to scoop up enemies on top of him, carrying them towards the target location. While flying through the air Zac is unstoppable. Upon landing nearby enemies take 150 / 250 / 350 (+70% AP) magic damage and are slowed by 25% for 0.5 seconds. Reactivating before Zac charges up knocks back nearby enemies instead."]}]}, {"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack animations have received non-gameplay impacting adjustments."]}]}, {"name": "Janna", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack animations have received non-gameplay impacting adjustments.", "New Effect: Basic attack visual and sound effects have been adjusted."]}, {"about": "Eye of the Storm", "lines": ["New Effect: Janna now uses crit animation while under the effect of Eye of the Storm."]}]}, {"name": "Morgana", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack animations have received non-gameplay impacting adjustments."]}]}, {"name": "Nami", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack animations have received non-gameplay impacting adjustments.", "New Effect: Basic attack visual and sound effects have been adjusted."]}, {"about": "Tidecaller's Blessing", "lines": ["New Effect: Nami now uses crit animation while under the effect of Tidecaller's Blessing."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 560 from 600."]}, {"about": "Winter's Wrath", "lines": ["Mana cost increased to 80 from 60.", "First hit base damage reduced to 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 from 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50.", "Second hit base damage reduced to 30 / 65 / 100 / 135 / 170 from 40 / 75 / 110 / 145 / 180."]}]}, {"name": "Sona", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack animations have received non-gameplay impacting adjustments."]}, {"about": "Power Chord", "lines": ["New Effect: Sona now uses crit animation while under the effect of Power Chord."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack animations have received non-gameplay impacting adjustments."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Stretching Strikes", "lines": ["Slow duration increased to 0.5 seconds from 0.25."]}, {"about": "Elastic Slingshot", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280 from 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Arise!", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug that could cause Sand Soldier attacks to sometimes not deal damage."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "Fury of the North", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug causing it not to break from instances of damage that were entirely absorbed by a shield.", "Cooldown increased to 15 / 12 / 9 (based on level) seconds from 9 at all levels."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "Venom Cask", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Once again properly adds a stack of  Deadly Venom as the cask explodes."]}]}, {"name": "Warwick", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a crash 