calling, the other may move nearby and activate their own recall to join them. Both reach base at the time of which the initiator's recall ends.", "Static Cooldown: 40 - 16 (based on level) seconds"]}, {"about": "Gleaming Quill", "lines": ["Active: Rakan slings an enchanted feather forward, dealing 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 (+50% AP) magic damage to the first enemy hit. If that enemy was a champion or epic monster, a small circular area is marked around Rakan. After a short period of time or if an ally champion comes into contact with the marked area, Rakan heals himself and surrounding allies by 23 - 150 (based on level) (+70% AP).", "Mana Cost: 60", "Cooldown: 12 / 10.5 / 9 / 7.5 / 6 seconds"]}, {"about": "Grand Entrance", "lines": ["Active: Rakan dashes forward, landing stylishly at his destination. After a dramatic pause, he leaps into the air, dealing 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 (+50% AP) magic damage and  knocking up surrounding enemies for 1 second.", "Mana Cost: 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90", "Cooldown: 18 / 16.5 / 15 / 13.5 / 12 seconds"]}, {"about": "Battle Dance", "lines": ["Active: Rakan leaps to an ally champion, shielding them for 50 / 85 / 120 / 155 / 190 (+80% AP) for 3 seconds. Battle Dance can be re-cast for 5 seconds at no cost. When re-cast, Rakan may select the same target again.  If  Xayah is the target, Battle Dance is able to be cast from an increased range.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100", "Cooldown: 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 seconds"]}, {"about": "The Quickness", "lines": ["Active: Rakan enchants his coat with a captivating sheen for the next 4 seconds, dealing 100 / 200 / 300 (+50% AP) magic damage and  charming each enemy he touches for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 seconds. Enemies can only be affected once. Rakan benefits from 50% bonus movement speed for the duration, which is briefly increased to 200% upon first damaging an enemy champion before decaying back down to 50%.", "Mana Cost: 100", "Cooldown: 120 / 110 / 100 seconds seconds"]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Overload", "lines": ["New Effect: Cooldown reset now occurs when  Rune Prison or  Spell Flux are cast, rather than when they hit their targets."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Twilight Assault", "lines": ["Removed: Empowered attack dealing 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 bonus magic damage to non-champions.", "New Effect: Empowered attack now deal an additional 15 - 40 (based on level) magic damage.", "New Effect: Empowered attack against monsters deals double damage, 30 - 80 (based on level) magic damage, but is still capped."]}, {"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Energy cost reduced to 150 from 180.", "Width increased to 120 from 100."]}, {"about": "Stand United", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 200 / 180 / 160 seconds from 180 / 150 / 120.", "Base shield value reduced to 175 / 350 / 525 from 250 / 550 / 850.", "New Effect: Shield now increases by 1% for every 1% of target's missing health, up to  280 / 560 / 840 total shield at 40% health."]}]}, {"name": "Udyr", "changes": [{"about": "Tiger Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 50 - 33 (based on level) from 47 / 44 / 41 / 38 / 35.", "Removed: Basic attacks dealing 15% AD bonus physical damage.", "New Effect: Persistent effect now also happen on every third attack after the first.", "Base damage over time reduced to 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 from 30 / 80 / 130 / 180 / 230.", "New Effect: New applications of the damage over time effect on a target already affected now deals remaining damage instantly."]}, {"about": "Turtle Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 50 - 33 (based on level) from 47 / 44 / 41 / 38 / 35.", "Removed: Granting 10 / 12 / 14 / 16 / 18% life steal.", "New Effect: First attack and every third attack after heals for 2.5% of maximum health, increased by 1% for every 1% of Udyr's missing health, up to 5% of maximum health"]}, {"about": "Bear Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 50 - 33 (based on level) from 47 / 44 / 41 / 38 / 35."]}, {"about": "Phoenix Stance", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 50 - 33 (based on level) from 47 / 44 / 41 / 38 / 35."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Dragonslayer Vayne Green Chroma", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Made easier to see on Summoner's Rift."]}]}, {"name": "Xayah", "changes": [{"about": "Clean Cuts", "lines": ["Innate: After casting an ability, Xayah's next 3 basic attacks strike all enemies along their path, dealing 100% damage to her main target and 50% pass-through damage to other enemies.  At her maximum attack range, a Feather will be left in the ground for 6 seconds. Xayah can store up to 5 empowered attacks.", "Lover's Leap: If either Xayah or  Rakan is  recalling, the other may move nearby and activate their own recall to join them. Both reach base at the time of which the initiator's recall ends."]}, {"about": "Double Daggers", "lines": ["Active: After a brief wind-up, Xayah hurls two feather-blades in quick succession in the target direction, and leaving 2 Feathers on the ground at maximum range. The feather-blades deal 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 (+50% bonus AD) physical damage to all enemies they pass through, reduced to 50% against units beyond the first.", "Mana Cost: 50", "Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 seconds"]}, {"about": "Deadly Plumage", "lines": ["Active: Xayah surrounds herself with a storm of feathers-blades for 4 seconds, granting her 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% bonus attack speed, 20% increased damage on her attacks, and 30% bonus movement speed for 1.5 seconds whenever she attacks a champion. If  Rakan is nearby, he will also gain Deadly Plumage, in turn increasing the bonus damage on each of them to 40%.", "Mana Cost: 60 / 55 / 50 / 45 / 40", "Cooldown: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 seconds"]}, {"about": "Bladecaller", "lines": ["Active: Xayah recalls all her Feathers, dealing 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 (+60% bonus AD) physical damage to enemies they strike on their way toward her, increasing by 0.5% for every 1% of Xayah's Critical Strike Chance. Minions take 50% damage. Each Feather to strike a target deals 10% less damage than the last, with a minimum of 10% damage. Enemies struck by at least 3 Feathers are  rooted for 1 second.", "Mana Cost: 40", "Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds"]}, {"about": "Featherstorm", "lines": ["Active: Xayah leaps into the air, becoming briefly untargetable but still able to move. After a short delay, she unleashes a volley of feather-blades forward in a cone, dealing 100 / 150 / 200 (+100% bonus AD) physical damage to all enemies struck and leaving a line of 5 Feathers at the end of Featherstorm's maximum range.", "Mana Cost: 80 / 90 / 100", "Cooldown: 140 / 130 / 120 seconds"]}]}, {"name": "Xin Zhao", "changes": [{"about": "Dragonslayer Xin Zhao", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he and his chromas were using the classic skin's SFX."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": [{"about": "High Noon Yasuo", "lines": [" Way of the Wanderer", "Bug Fix: Chromas no longer use the base skin particles."]}]}]}
{"id": "V7.7", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V7.7", "date": "2017-04-05", "champions": [{"name": "Alistar", "changes": [{"about": "Triumphant Roar", "lines": ["New Effect: Now heals all neaby allied champions instead of only one."]}, {"about": "Trample", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 12 / 11.5 / 11 / 10.5 / 10 seconds from 16 / 15.5 / 15 / 14.5 / 14.", "On-hit damage at 5 Trample stacks increased to 55 - 310 (based on level) from 50 - 220 (based on level).", "Bug Fix: Minions affected by Trample now display the proper visual effects."]}]}, {"name": "Amumu", "changes": [{"about": "Cursed Touch", "lines": ["Removed: Basic attacks reduces target's magic resistance by 15 / 20 / 25 (based on level) for 3 seconds.", "New Effect: Basic attacks apply Curse on target for 3 seconds. Cursed target receive 15% bonus true damage from all incoming magic damage."]}, {"about": "Despair", "lines": ["Base damage per second increased to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 from 8 / 12 / 16 / 20 / 24.", "New Effect: Damage now applies every half second instead of every second.", "New Effect: Now refreshes Curse on targets."]}, {"about": "Curse of the Sad Mummy", "lines": ["New Effect: Now applies Curse on targets."]}]}, {"name": "Bard", "changes": [{"about": "Traveler's Call", "lines": ["Meep base damage is now 30 (+15 every 5 Chimes) from 30 - 460 (based on Chimes) (+20 every 5 thereafter).", "Meep slow changed to 25 - 75 (based on Chimes)% from 25 - 80 (based on Chimes)%.", "Meep AoE unlock requirement reduced to 15 Chimes from 25 Chimes.", "Meep AoE increased radius requirement reduced to 35 Chimes from 65 Chimes.", "Meep recharge time reduced to 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 (based on Chimes) from 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 (based on Chimes).", "Meep stock limit increased to 1 - 9 (based on Chimes) from 1 / 2 / 3 / 4 (based on Chimes)."]}]}, {"name": "Braum", "changes": [{"about": "Dragonslayer Braum and  El Tigre Braum", "lines": [" Winter's Bite", "Bug Fix: Restored missing particles when killing an enemy with Winter's Bite."]}]}, {"name": "Camille", "changes": [{"about": "Tactical Sweep", "lines": ["Removed: Outer half healing against minions and monsters. Now only heals against enemy champions."]}, {"about": "The Hextech Ultimatum", "lines": ["Duration reduced to 2.5 / 3.25 / 4 seconds from 4 at all ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Cho'Gath", "changes": [{"about": "Feast", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Kill indicator now properly takes ability power into consideration."]}]}, {"name": "Darius", "changes": [{"about": "Dunkmaster Darius", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where moving the camera away from him as he was recalling would desync the sound of it."]}]}, {"name": "Elise", "changes": [{"about": "Spider Form", "lines": ["Bug Fix: If she casts Spider Form at the same time  Thresh's  Death Sentence connects, she no longer cleanses the effect."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Pulsefire Ezreal", "lines": [" Mystic Shot", "Bug Fix: If he uses Mystic Shot while affected by the aura buff of  Sona's  Hymn of Valor, he now properly uses his own VFX rather than  Sona's."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "Headmistress Fiora", "lines": [" Bladework", "Bug Fix: First hit particles no longer exceed the ruler's length."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "Colossal Smash", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 12 - 80 (based on level) from 15 - 100 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Winds of War", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 75% AP from 60% AP.", "Tornado target maximum health ratio reduced to 6% target's maximum health from 9% target's maximum health."]}, {"about": "Hero's Entrance", "lines": ["Bug Fix: If Galio disconnected while flying up during Hero's Entrance, he no longer loses the ability to attack units and structures after reconnecting."]}]}, {"name": "Gnar", "changes": [{"about": "Dino Gnar and  Gentleman Gnar", "lines": [" Boulder Toss", "Bug Fix: Mega Gnar's boulder replacements no longer visually disappear earlier than intended."]}]}, {"n