de away during her death animation for her base and a few of her skins."]}]}, {"name": "Lucian", "changes": [{"about": "The Culling", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where he was able to basic attack during The Culling if he fired an energized attack immediately before casting The Culling."]}]}, {"name": "Lulu", "changes": [{"about": "Whimsy", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bunch of cases where the polymorph effect wasn't properly canceling or interrupting certain effects and abilities."]}]}, {"name": "Lux", "changes": [{"about": "Final Spark", "lines": ["New Effect: If Final Spark kills an enemy champion, 10 / 30 / 50% of its cooldown is refunded."]}]}, {"name": "Malzahar", "changes": [{"about": "Void Swarm", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Lifesteal no longer applies when hitting voidlings."]}]}, {"name": "Miss Fortune", "changes": [{"about": "Arcade Miss Fortune", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where she was playing the wrong critical strike hit sound-effect."]}]}, {"name": "Nautilus", "changes": [{"about": "Depth Charge", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where it would properly consume spell shields of champions in their path, but displace them anyway."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": [{"about": "Bushwhack", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Lifesteal no longer applies when hitting traps."]}]}, {"name": "Nunu & Willump", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 575 from 598.28.", "Base health regeneneration reduced to 7 from 8.39."]}, {"about": "Visionary", "lines": ["New Effect: Having 5 Visionary stacks enhances the effect of his next ability:", " Consume: +160 true damage, +50 base healing.", " Blood Boil: +1% movement speed, +5% attack speed.", " Ice Blast: +40 base damage, +5% movement speed slow.", " Absolute Zero: +250 maximum base damage."]}, {"about": "Consume", "lines": ["Base damage changed to 340 / 500 / 660 / 820 / 980 / 1140 from 400 / 550 / 700 / 850 / 1000.", "Heal changed to 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 / 300 from 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250."]}]}, 