out": "Noxious Trap", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Lifesteal no longer applies when hitting traps."]}]}, {"name": "Vi", "changes": [{"about": "Assault and Battery", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where it would properly consume spell shields of champions in their path, but displace them anyway."]}]}, {"name": "Volibear", "changes": [{"about": "Thunder Claws", "lines": ["Maximum number of bounces increased to 8 from 4.", "New Effect: There's now a small delay between bounces.", "New Effect: Is now better at searching for additional targets before ending the chain early."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "Dark Procession", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Lifesteal no longer applies when hitting the wall."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Cell Division", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a rare bug where it could sometimes cause him to instantly revive (and potentially revive a second time if he's killed again before his bloblets recombined)."]}, {"about": "Elastic Slingshot", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where  Flashing right after casting it would change his position and move the range indicator, but the damage and knock-up would still be applied in the original location."]}]}]}
{"id": "V7.6", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V7.6", "date": "2017-03-22", "champions": [{"name": "Aatrox", "changes": [{"about": "Blood Well", "lines": ["Passive effect \"Blood Rush\" renamed to \"Hellbent\".", "New Effect: Blood Well bar is now light red if Aatrox is both Hellbent and can revive, dark red if he can't.", "New Effect: After reviving Blood Well is now 100% full."]}, {"about": "Blood Price /  Blood Thirst", "lines": ["New Effect: After reviving will no longer reset."]}]}, {"name": "Ahri", "changes": [{"about": "Charm", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Enemies affected by Charm during a dash are no longer still able to cast spells during the dash."]}]}, {"name": "Alistar", "changes": [{"about": "SKT T1 Alistar", "lines": ["General", "Bug Fix: Recall animation audio is no longer bullishly loud.", " Triumphant Roar", "Bug Fix: No longer slides around during animation."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Flash Frost", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Slow no longer overrides her  Glacial Storm slow (giving movement speed back to affected enemies)."]}]}, {"name": "Cho'Gath", "changes": [{"about": "Feast", "lines": ["Bonus health per stack increased to 80 / 120 / 160 from 80 / 110 / 140.", "Total stacks that can be gained from minions and non-epic monsters increased to 6 from 5."]}]}, {"name": "Corki", "changes": [{"about": "Arcade Corki", "lines": [" Gatling Gun", "Bug Fix: VFX have been toned down to be less overwhelming.", " Missile Barrage", "Bug Fix: VFX have been updated to be more recognizable."]}]}, {"name": "Dr. Mundo", "changes": [{"about": "Burning Agony", "lines": ["Bug Fix: VFX no longer stutter when he turns."]}]}, {"name": "Fiddlesticks", "changes": [{"about": "Terrify", "lines": ["Range increased to 575 from 525."]}, {"about": "Drain", "lines": ["New Effect: If the target dies before the channel completes, reduces its cooldown by its remaining duration."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "Riposte", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Using it while  Banshee's Veil is active no longer causes it to visually go on cooldown in Fiora's inventory (or to visually fizzle, then instantly reappear)."]}]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "Chum the Waters", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where it wouldn't slow enemies properly when the shark erupted."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": ["Full Relaunch", {"about": "General", "lines": ["Title changed to the Colossus from the Sentinel's Sorrow.", "Complete visual upgrade across all skins.", "New artwork for  Original Galio,  Enchanted Galio,  Hextech Galio,  Commando Galio,  Gatekeeper Galio, and  Debonair Galio.", "New voice over.", "New lore."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack range increased to 150 from 125.", "Base attack speed reduced to 0.625 from 0.638.", "Base attack damage reduced to 59 from 61.97.", "Base armor increased to 27 from 26.88.", "Base health reduced to 550 from 577.8.", "Base mana increased to 400 from 369.", "Base health regeneration reduced to 8 from 8.71.", "Base mana regeneration increased to 7 from 6.", "Attack speed growth increased to 1.5% from 1.2%.", "Attack damage growth increased to 3.5 from 3.375.", "Health growth increased to 100 from 85.", "Mana growth reduced to 40 from 47.", "Health regeneration growth increased to 0.8 from 0.75.", "Mana regeneration growth reduced to 0.7 from 0.8."]}, {"about": "Colossal Smash - Passive", "lines": ["Innate: Every 8 seconds, Galio's next basic attack periodically deals 15 - 100 (based on level) (+100% AD) (+40% AP) (+40% bonus magic resistance) magic damage to his main target and all enemies around it.", "Colossal Smash's cooldown is reduced by 4 seconds every time Galio hits an enemy champion with a new ability."]}, {"about": "Winds of War - Q spell", "lines": ["Active: Galio fires two gusts of wind that arc to either side before converging to the target area, dealing 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 (+60% AP) magic damage to all enemies they pass through.", "Upon impacting with each other, the gusts form a tornado that advances for 1.5 seconds, dealing 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 (+13.3% AP) (+3% of target's maximum health) magic damage every 0.5 seconds to every enemy within, capped at 50 per hit against monsters.", "Mana cost: 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90", "Cooldown: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 seconds", "Range: 825"]}, {"about": "Shield of Durand - W spell", "lines": ["Passive: Galio gains a shield that absorbs up to 8 - 23 (based on level)% maximum health magic damage, refreshing after not taking damage for 12 seconds.", "First cast: Galio begins to charge over 1.75 seconds,  slowing himself by 30%, reducing incoming damage by 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% (+8% per bonus magic resistance) and increasing Shield of Durand's  taunt radius over the duration.", "Second cast: Galio  taunts all nearby enemies for 0.5 seconds, with the duration increasing based on how long Shield of Durand was charged, up to 1.5 seconds, and refreshes its damage reduction for 2 seconds.", "Shield of Durand cannot be interrupted by crowd control. Shield of Durand's cooldown starts on cast.", "Mana cost: 50", "Cooldown: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 seconds"]}, {"about": "Justice Punch - E spell", "lines": ["Active: Galio briefly dashes backwards before charging forward, stopping upon hitting terrain or an enemy champion, dealing 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 / 260 (+70% AP) magic damage to all enemies hit and  knocking them up for 0.75 seconds.", "Mana cost: 50", "Cooldown: 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 seconds"]}, {"about": "Hero's Entrance - R spell", "lines": ["Active: Galio designates the target allied champion's location at the time of cast as his landing spot, channeling for 1 seconds, and dashes to them, reducing the damage they take by 20 / 30 / 40% (+8% per 100 bonus magic resistance) until he lands.", "Upon impact, Galio deals 150 / 250 / 350 (+70% AP) magic damage to all nearby enemies and  knocks them up for 0.75 seconds, increased to 1.25 seconds at the center of the impact zone.", "Mana cost: 100", "