{"id": "V7.5", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V7.5", "date": "2017-03-08", "champions": [{"name": "Aatrox", "changes": [{"about": "Blood Well", "lines": ["Rework: Aatrox fills his Blood Well through his abilities, and it empties while out of combat. When the Blood Well is filled, Aatrox gains Blood Rush for 4 seconds as the Blood Well drains. During Blood Rush, dealing or taking damage against enemy champions will completely fill the Blood Well and refresh Blood Rush duration.", "Blood Rush: Aatrox gains 25% increased base AD and 20% / 30% / 40% / 50% (based on level) bonus attack speed. Upon taking fatal damage Aatrox will revive over 3 seconds, recovering 30% of maximum health over the duration. Aatrox cannot revive more than once every 180 / 160 / 140 / 120 (based on level) seconds.", "Blood Well reduced to 100 at all levels from 105 - 870 (based on level).", "Revive effect cooldown reduced to 180 / 160 / 140 / 120 (based on level) from 225 / 200 / 175 / 150 (based on level).", "Old Effect: Whenever Aatrox consumes health, he stores it into his Blood Well, which can hold up to 105 - 870 (based on level) health. The Blood Well depletes by 2% per second if Aatrox hasn't dealt or received damage in the last 5 seconds. Aatrox gains 0.3 - 0.55 (based on level)% bonus attack speed for every 1% in his Blood Well, up to a maximum of 30 - 55 (based on level)% bonus attack speed. Upon taking fatal damage, Aatrox is cleansed of all debuffs, enters  stasis and drains his Blood Well, healing himself over the next 3 seconds for 36.75 - 304.5 (based on level) health (+100% of Blood Well's stored health) up to a maximum of 141.75 - 1174.5 (based on level) health."]}, {"about": "Dark Flight", "lines": ["Removed: 10% current health cost.", "Base damage reduced to 10 / 35 / 60 / 95 / 120 from 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250.", "AD ratio changed to 110% AD from 60% bonus AD.", "New Effect: Now fills 20% of  Blood Well on cast."]}, {"about": "Blood Thirst", "lines": ["Base heal increased to 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 from 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40.", "New Effect: Heal now scales with 5% missing health.", "Removed: Heal scaling with 25% bonus AD.", "Removed: Healing triples while below 50% health."]}, {"about": "Blood Price", "lines": ["Removed: 15 / 23.75 / 32.5 / 41.25 / 50 (+25% bonus AD) health cost.", "Base bonus damage reduced to 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 from 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200.", "AD ratio reduced to 75% bonus AD from 100% bonus AD.", "New Effect: Now fills 20% of  Blood Well on-hit."]}, {"about": "Blades of Torment", "lines": ["Health cost changed to 30 health from 5% current health.", "Base damage changed to 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 from 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 / 215.", "AD ratio increased to 70% bonus AD from 60% bonus AD.", "Removed: Damage scaling with 60% AP.", "Damage type changed to physical from magic.", "Slow changed to 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% from 40% at all ranks.", "Slow duration changed to 2 seconds at all ranks from 1.75 / 2 / 2.25 / 2.5 / 2.75.", "New Effect: Now fills 20% of  Blood Well on cast."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Festival Queen Anivia and  Blackfrost Anivia", "lines": [" Crystallize", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where using flash while casting Crystallize would allow enemies and allies to walk through the wall."]}]}, {"name": "Ashe", "changes": [{"about": "PROJECT: Ashe", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where the particles for killing enemy units with basic attacks and critical strikes weren't displaying correctly."]}]}, {"name": "Brand", "changes": [{"about": "Zombie Brand", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where moving the camera away and back during his death animation would make his gravestone and earth particles to disappear."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Twin Fang", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Casting it now respects stop and hold commands for her movement queueing."]}]}, {"name": "Cho'Gath", "changes": [{"about": "Feral Scream", "lines": ["New Effect: Adjusted particle to match actual cone size."]}]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Intermediate bot now has a keystone mastery."]}, {"about": "Urchin Strike", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 55% AP from 35% AP."]}, {"about": "Seastone Trident", "lines": ["Bleed duration reduced to 3 seconds from 4.", "Mark duration increased to 6 seconds from 4."]}, {"about": "Chum the Waters", "lines": ["When fishes reach their target location without attaching to anything, the check for a nearby target to attach to is now less generous.", "Removed: Whiffed fishes are no longer picked up by enemies that walk over them."]}]}, {"name": "Jax", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Effect: Altered cast frames on Jax's basic attacks to be more visually consistent."]}, {"about": "Empower", "lines": ["New Effect: Attack now always uses crit animation."]}, {"about": "Counter Strike", "lines": ["New Effect: Resized Counterstrike hit particle and did some rotation/swirl editing to more accurately convey the range and shape of effect."]}, {"about": "Grandmaster's Might", "lines": ["New Effect: Once he levels his ultimate, Jax cycles consistently through his different basic attack animations."]}]}, {"name": "Jhin", "changes": [{"about": "High Noon Jhin", "lines": [" Curtain Call", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where the range indicator was too large."]}, {"about": "Dancing Grenade", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where casting it from fog of war / brush would not reveal Jhin to enemy champions."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Intermediate bot now has a keystone mastery."]}]}, {"name": "Kindred", "changes": [{"about": "Mark of the Kindred", "lines": ["Mark time out reduced to 3 minutes from 5.", "Mark respawn time reduced to 50 seconds from 70.", "Old mark tier system:", "0 - 2 marks:  Rift Scuttler or  Crimson Raptor", "3 - 4 marks:  Ancient Krug,  Crimson Raptor,  Gromp, or  Greater Murk Wolf", "5 - 7 marks:  Blue Senti