ade", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 from 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 / 150.", "New Effect: Now scales with 20% bonus AD."]}]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Zyra's dead body could intercept ARAM's snowball."]}, {"about": "Rampant Growth", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Zyra's seeds from both Rampant Growth and  Garden of Thorns weren't respecting their spawn cap."]}]}]}
