% bonus AD.", "Isolation bonus increased to 50% from 30%.", "Isolation damage increased to 105 / 142.5 / 180 / 217.5 / 255 (+210% bonus AD) from 91 / 123.5 / 156 / 188.5 / 221 (+156% bonus AD)."]}, {"about": "Evolved Reaper Claws", "lines": ["Renamed to Evolved Reaper Claws from Evolved Enlarged Claws.", "Removed: Increasing damage against Isolated targets.", "New Effect: If target is Isolated, refunds 60% of Taste Their Fear's cooldown."]}, {"about": "Void Spike", "lines": ["Removed: Slowing by 20% damaged enemies."]}, {"about": "Evolved Spike Racks", "lines": ["Evolved slow reduced to 40% from 50%.", "New Effect: Isolated targets are now slowed by 80% instead."]}, {"about": "Void Assault", "lines": ["Stealth reclassifed as  Invisibility.", "Stealth duration increased to 1.25 seconds from 1."]}, {"about": "Evolved Adapative Cloaking", "lines": ["Renamed to Evolved Adaptaive Cloaking from Evolved Active Camouflage.", "Removed: Increasing invisibility duration and number of charges.", "New Effect: Kha'Zix gains Void Assault for 2.5 seconds in brush, which lingers for 1.5 seconds after exiting the brush. This can only be triggered while out of combat and there is a 10-second per-brush cooldown."]}]}, {"name": "Kled", "changes": [{"about": "Skaarl the Cowardly Lizard", "lines": ["Remount delay reduced to 0.5 seconds from 1.25."]}, {"about": "Violent Tendencies", "lines": ["Bonus damage reduced to 4 / 4.5 / 5 / 5.5 / 6% of target's maximum health from 4 / 5 / 6 / 7 / 8%."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health growth increased to 80 from 75."]}, {"about": "Sigil of Malice (new innate)", "lines": ["New Innate: LeBlanc's abilities apply Sigil of Malice for 4 seconds that primes after a 1.5 second delay. Once primed, LeBlanc can use another ability to trigger the sigil and deal 40 - 300 (based on level) (+80% AP) bonus damage. This has an 5 seconds cooldown per target."]}, {"about": "Shatter Orb", "lines": ["Renamed to Shatter Orb from Sigil of Malice.", "AP ratio increased to 50% AP from 40% AP.", "Mana cost reduced to 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 from 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90.", "Removed: Applying a mark on the target.", "New Effect: If Shatter Orb triggers  Sigil of Malice, it chains to the nearest ready  Sigil of Malice, damaging them as well. Bounces deal [66 / 96 / 126 / 156 / 186 (+60% AP) magic][120%] damage to minions."]}, {"about": "Distortion", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 from 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100.", "Improved detection when traversing walls.", "New Effect: Now has a 0.25 seconds delay before returning to her original position when recasting Distortion."]}, {"about": "Ethereal Chains", "lines": ["New Effect: Tether indicator is now visible to LeBlanc and the target.", "Removed: Slowing by 25% target during the tether."]}, {"about": "Mimic (updated)", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 54 / 42 / 30 seconds from 40 / 32 / 24.", "First Cast: LeBlanc primes herself to summon a Mimic. While primed, LeBlanc's gains access to an alternate kit that consists of empowered version of her basic abilities as well as a new ultimate ability,  Shadow of the Rose. LeBlanc's empowered basic abilities do not interact with the cooldowns of her standard abilities. Shadow of the Rose has a separate 160 / 140 / 120 second cooldown and using Shadow of the Rose will refund Mimic's cooldown.", "Empowered Basic Ability: LeBlanc vanishes for 0.1 seconds and then casts an empowered version of the chosen spell, also summoning an indistinguishable Mimic that casts a damageless copy of the spell. This Mimic lasts 2.5 seconds and is dismissed if it takes single target damage from an enemy champion or turret.", " Mimic Shatter Orb damage implemented at 150 / 275 / 400 (+60% AP).", " Mimic Distortion damage reduced to 125 / 225 / 325 (+50% AP) from 150 / 300 / 450 (+90% AP).", " Mimic Ethereal Chains damage reduced to 100 / 160 / 220 (+40% AP) fro