ased on level)  from 50 - 340 (based on level).", "Slow strength changed to 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90% from 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80%.", "Slow duration reduced to 1.75 seconds from 2.5.", "Removed: Slow decay."]}, {"about": "Thrill of the Hunt", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 130 / 100 / 70 seconds from 150 / 110 / 70 seconds.", "Duration increased to 14 / 22 / 30 seconds from 7 (or 12 seconds with 12 Trophies).", "New Effect: Cooldown now starts on cast rather than when the spell ends.", "New Effect: Enters  Camouflage after 2 seconds.", "In-stealth movement speed increased to 15 / 30 / 45% from 15% (or 30% with 20 Trophies).", "New Effect: Movement speed is active at all times rather than only while moving towards enemy champions.", "New Effect: Grants vision on the closest enemy champion rather than on all enemy champions.", "New Effect: Rengar's eyes appear over the head of the target Rengar gains visions of (visible to both teams).", "Removed: Bonus movement speed after stealth.", "Removed: Bonus ferocity generation.", "Delay between casting R and when Rengar can leap implemented at 2 seconds.", "New Effect: Rengar's Unseen Predator from stealth versus his revealed target is guaranteed to  critically strike."]}]}, {"name": "Shaco", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Recommended items updated."]}, {"about": "Backstab", "lines": ["Revised Effect: Shaco's attacks critically strike for 120 - 145 (based on level)% damage when striking a unit from behind (200% versus monsters). This stacks additively with bonus critical strike damage. This cannot happen again for 3 seconds (affected by cooldown reduction). If the attack happens to roll a critical strike regardless, Shaco's total critical damage is applied but the effect is still put on cooldown."]}, {"about": "Deceive", "lines": ["Mana cost changed to 60 at all ranks from 90 / 80 / 70 / 60 / 50.", "Cooldown increased to 14 seconds from 11.", "Cast time changed to 0.125 seconds from randomly between 0.05 and 0.3.", "Duration changed to  1.5 / 2.25 / 3 / 3.75 / 4.5 seconds from 3.5 at all ranks.", "Removed: Next basic attack critically striking for bonus critical damage.", "Stealth reclassified as  Invisibility.", "New Effect: Next basic attack deals 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 (+50% AP) bonus physical damage, which can be increased with  Backstab, and reduces Deceive's cooldown by 2.5 seconds.", "New Effect: Can now place  Jack in the Box while stealthed. Placing a  Jack in the Box briefly reveals Shaco's position, but doesn't make him targetable."]}, {"about": "Jack in the Box", "lines": ["Box health increased to 150 - 550 (based on level) from 150 at all levels.", "Arm time reduced to 2 seconds from randomly between 2.1 and 2.3.", "New Effect: Boxes now instantly die to turret shots, and lose a minimum of 1/3rd of their health from champion basic attacks.", "New Effect: Boxes duration now scales with 5% AP.", "Damage against turrets reduced to 50% from 100%.", "Clarity: Boxes are  stealthed traps."]}, {"about": "Two-Shiv Poison", "lines": ["Slow increased to 20 / 22.5 / 25 / 27.5 / 30% from 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30%.", "Base damage reduced to 5 / 35 / 65 / 95 / 125 from 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210.", "AD ratio changed to 85% AD from 100% bonus AD.", "AD ratio reduced to 90% AP from 100% AP.", "New Effect: Now also deals 3 - 8 (based on level)% of target's missing health bonus magic damage.", "Removed: Slowing monsters and minions attack speed by 20 / 22.5 / 25 / 27.5 / 30%."]}, {"about": "Hallucinate", "lines": ["Cast time increased to 0.5 seconds from randomly between 0.25 and 0.5.", "Clone's damage against turrets reduced to 35% from 50%.", "New Effect: Clone's now takes double damage from turrets.", "New Effect: Clone can now attack wards.", "New Effect: In addition to dealing damage when killed, a clone now spawns 3 mini  Jack in the Boxes for 6 seconds that activate together and share damage taken.", "Mini boxes deal 25 / 50 / 75 (+15% AP) magic damage and cause the target to flee for 0.75 seconds. Gains 210-950 bonus health (from levels 6-18)."]}]}, {"name": "Talon", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New ability icons.", "Attack frame improved."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base movement speed reduced to 335 from 350.", "Health growth increased to 90 from 85.", "Base attack damage increased to 60 from 55.", "Base attack speed reduced to 0.625 from 0.668.", "Attack speed growth increased to 2.9% from 2.7%."]}, {"about": "Blade's End (new innate)", "lines": ["New Innate: Talon's abilities Wound enemy champions and epic monsters damaged for a 6 seconds, stacking up to 3 times. When Talon attacks a fully stacked enemy, they bleed for 60 - 160 (based on level) (+200% bonus AD) physical damage over the next 2 seconds. Rake and Shadow Assault will not apply multiple stacks for multiple blades, but will apply up to two stacks for the outward and inward effects."]}, {"about": "Noxian Diplomacy", "lines": ["Revised Active: Talon strikes his target, dealing them 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 / 160 (+100% bonus AD) physical damage. If cast from melee range, Talon will  critically strike them instead for [120 / 150 / 180 / 210 / 240 (+150% bonus AD) physical][150%] damage. Whenever Noxian Diplomacy kills a unit, Talon restores 17 - 51 (based on level) health and refunds 50% of its cooldown.", "Cooldown increased to 8 / 7.5 / 7 / 6.5 / 6 seconds from 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4.", "Mana cost reduced to 30 at all ranks from 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60.", "Range: 550 / 170"]}, {"about": "Rake", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 9 seconds at all ranks from 10.", "Mana cost reduced to 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 from 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80.", "Slow increased to 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% from 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40%.", "Slow duration reduced to 1 second from 2.", "New Effect: Slow now only applies when the blades return.", "New Effect: Now has a 0.7 seconds delay before returning to Talon.", "Range increased to 900 from 750.", "Arc reduced to 22\u00b0 from 40\u00b0.", "Outgoing damage changed to 50 / 65 / 80 / 95 / 110 (+40% bonus AD) from 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 (+60% bonus AD).", "Return damage increased to 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160 (+60% bonus AD) from 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 (+60% bonus AD).", "Total damage changed to 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 / 270 (+100% bonus AD) from 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260 (+120% bonus AD)."]}, {"about": "Assassin's Path (new E)", "lines": ["Active: Talon dashes over the target structure or piece of terrain, with the dash's speed based on his own movement speed. Talon cannot cast Assassin's Path on the same piece of terrain for a set duration.", "Can vault over player-made terrain as well.", "Cooldown: 2 seconds", "Per-Target Cooldown: 160 / 135 / 110 / 85 / 60 seconds (can be reduced by cooldown reduction) A red ring will highlight used terrain to Talon."]}, {"about": "Shadow Assault", "lines": ["Base damage per hit reduced to 80 / 120 / 160  from 120 / 170 / 220.", "AD ratio increased to 80% bonus AD from 75% bonus AD.", "New Effect: Blades now have a minimum lifetime of 0.8 seconds before returning to Talon.", "New Effect: If Talon breaks stealth with a basic attack or Noxian Diplomacy, the blades will converge on his target's location instead of his own.", "New Effect: Now has way more blades.", "Stealth reclassified as  Invisibility."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Guerrilla Warfare", "lines": ["Renamed from  Camouflage.", "Stealth reclassified as  Invisibility."]}, {"about": "Noxious Trap", "lines": ["For clarity, Noxious Trap is a  stealthed trap."]}]}, {"name": "Thresh", "changes": [{"about": "Dark Passage", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Can no longer be casted globally under specific circumstances. No lantern was created, but Thresh gained vision of the target area."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "Ambush", "lines": ["Stealth reclassified as  Camouflage.", "Fade time reduced to 1 second from 1.5 or 4.5 seconds based on damage taken.", "Duration increased to 10 / 11 / 12 / 13 / 14 seconds from 4 / 5 / 6 / 7 / 8.", "Movement speed reduced to 10% from 20%.", "New Effect: Movement speed is tripled to 30% while nearby enemy champions who cannot see him."]}, {"about": "Venom Cask", "lines": ["New Effect: Creates a persistent area of effect for 3 seconds that  slows and applies 1 Deadly Venom per second.", "Impact stacks reduced to 1 from 2."]}, {"about": "Spray and Pray", "lines": ["Renamed to Spray and Pray from Rat-Ta-Tat-Tat."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Final Hour", "lines": ["Stealth reclassified as  Invisibility."]}]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": [{"about": "Chaos Storm", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Lowered the volume of Creator Viktor's Chaos Storm churning."]}]}, {"name": "Wukong", "changes": [{"about": "Decoy", "lines": ["Stealth reclassified as  Invisibility."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: PROJECT: Yasuo's basic attack animations have been adjusted to visually slash the target at the same time damage is applied, rather than slightly after."]}]}, {"name": "Zed", "changes": [{"about": "Living Shadow", "lines": ["Removed: 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 20% bonus AD.", "Energy restored increased to 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 from 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40.", "Shadow swap range increased to 1300 from 1100."]}, {"about": "Shadow Slash", "lines": ["Cooldown changed to 5 / 4.5 / 4 / 3.5 / 3 seconds from 4 at all ranks.", "Base damage changed to 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 / 165 from 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180."]}, {"about": "Death Mark", "lines": ["New Effect - Reaper of Shadows: Scoring a kill or assist with Death Mark or while Death Mark is active will permanently empower Zed with 5 (+5 / 10 / 15% of target's total AD) bonus attack damage. This effect is non-stacking, but Zed will always keep the largest bonus between his current bonus and latest kill."]}]}]}
{"id": "V6.21", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V6.21", "date": "2016-10-19", "champions": [{"name": "Ashe", "changes": [{"about": "Ranger's Focus", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where rapidly pressing Q the instant Focus reaches four stacks could cause Ranger's Focus's mana cost to apply multiple times."]}]}, {"name": "Braum", "changes": [{"about": "Glacial Fissure", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Slow no longer applies inconsistently to enemies in Fog of War."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Pulsefire Ezreal's  Recall VO lines no longer stop playing after he dies."]}]}, {"name": "Draven", "changes": [{"about": "Spinning Axe", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Primetime Draven's Spinning Axe sound effects have been updated to be more noticeable."]}, {"about": "Whirling Death", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Soul Reaver Draven's Whirling Death now properly plays sound effects when it hits enemies."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: When Pool Party Fiora kills an enemy with a basic attack, the universal blue swirly death VFX now properly display."]}]}, {"name": "Graves", "changes": [{"about": "Quickdraw", "lines": ["Stack limit increased to 8 from 4.", "New Effect: Now grants 2 stacks if you dash toward an enemy champion.", "Resistances per stack reduced to 5 / 7.5 / 10 / 12.5 / 15 from 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30."]}]}, {"name": "Ivern", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a weird texture on the back of  Daisy's delicious head with the Candy King Ivern skin."]}]}, {"name": "Janna", "changes": [{"about": "Howling Gale", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug causing Forecast Janna's Howling Gale to not play audio if released after reaching max charge."]}]}, {"name": "Kog'Maw", "changes": [{"about": "Living Artillery", "lines": ["Initial and stacking mana cost reduced to 40 from 50.", "Maximum mana cost reduced to 400 from 500.", "Increased cost debuff duration reduced to 8 seconds from 10.", "Base damage increased to 100 / 140 / 180 from 70 / 110 / 150.", "New Effect: Deals 0.83% increased damage for every 1% of target's missing health, up to 50% bonus damage (versus targets above 40% of their maximum health).", "Maximum damage implemented at 150 / 210 / 270 (+97.5% bonus AD) (+37.5% AP).", "Threshold to deal double damage changed to below 40% health from below 50% health. Target's below the above threshold take double damage instead of the previous modifier.", "Base double damage increased to 200 / 280 / 360 from 140 / 220 / 300.", "Removed: Triple damage below 25% health, previously 240 / 330 / 540 (+195% bonus AD) (+75% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Lee Sin", "changes": [{"about": "Resonating Strike", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Resonating Strike and  Safeguard once again drop Lee Sin directly on top of his target."]}]}, {"name": "Leona", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Pool Party Leona now properly faces the camera during her recall animation when she has the  Hand of Baron buff."]}]}, {"name": "Master Yi", "changes": [{"about": "Double Strike", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Master Yi would not critically strike monsters after Double Striking them at certain attack speeds."]}, {"about": "Alpha Strike", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Dying during Alpha Strike will properly play Master Yi's death animation, placing him where Alpha Strike was portraying him to be.", "New Effect: Minimum untargetability of 0.25 seconds.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Alpha Strike could sometimes fail to cast but still go on cooldown, and be unable to be reset by basic attacking until Master Yi cast Alpha Strike again.", "New Effect: Alpha Strike now also grants vision of where Master Yi will strike on his next bounce.", "Alpha Strike won't place Master Yi on top of  Baron Nashor if it is the primary target.", " Meditate is no longer momentarily locked out after a failed Alpha Strike cast.", "Master Yi now becomes eligible for assists as soon as Alpha Strike visually bounces to a target (even though damage is only applied at the end of the animation)."]}, {"about": "Wuju Style", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Wuju Style's passive attack damage bonus wasn'' counting toward the 25% bonus AD scaling of its active effect if Wuju Style was cast immediately as its cooldown expired."]}]}, {"name": "Nasus", "changes": [{"about": "Siphoning Strike", "lines": ["New Effect: Bonus range now stack with the bonus range from  Fury of the Sands.", "Total range while under the effects of both  Siphoning Strike and  Fury of the Sands increased to 200 from 175."]}, {"about": "Fury of the Sands", "lines": ["Removed: Converting damage dealt into bonus AD.", "New Effect: Now instantly grants 15 / 35 / 55 armor and magic resistance, which increases by 1 / 2 / 3 per second, for a maximum of 30 / 65 / 100 total bonus resistances."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": [{"about": "Takedown", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 6 seconds at all ranks from 5."]}, {"about": "Pounce", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 6 seconds at all ranks from 5."]}, {"about": "Primal Surge", "lines": ["Heal reduced to 25 / 45 / 65 / 85 / 105 (+27.5% AP) from 45 / 85 / 125 / 165 / 205 (+50% AP).", "New Effect: Increases heal by 1% for 1% of the target's missing health, for a maximum of 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+55% AP)."]}, {"about": "Swipe", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 6 seconds at all ranks from 5."]}]}, {"name": "Nocturne", "changes": [{"about": "Shroud of Darkness", "lines": ["Void Nocturne and Frozen Nocturne now use the base skin's particle for their spell shields."]}]}, {"name": "Nunu & Willump", "changes": [{"about": "Consume", "lines": ["Well Fed bonus health per stack reduced to 2% maximum health from 3% maximum health.", "Well Fed maximum bonus health reduced to 10% maximum health from 15% maximum health."]}]}, {"name": "Poppy", "changes": [{"about": "Iron Ambassador", "lines": ["Bug Fix: When Star Guardian Poppy's Iron Ambassador grants her a shield, sound effects no longer play slightly before visual effects."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "Broken Wings", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer prevented from dashing over walls with the third cast of Broken Wings if she's under the effects of  Valor."]}]}, {"name": "Thresh", "changes": [{"about": "Death Sentence", "lines": ["Bug Fix: No longer sometimes sends Thresh to weird places if he tries to fly through a base gate."]}]}, {"name": "Udyr", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed an issue causing Spirit Guard Udyr's ability animations (not VFX) to play more than once when form-swapping while running."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": [{"about": "Steel Tempest", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed pixelation on the max range indicator of PROJECT: Yasuo's third Steel Tempest cast."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "Eulogy of the Isles", "lines": ["If Yorick summons the Maiden inside of a lane, she'll start pushing that lane."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Recommended items updated."]}, {"about": "Elastic Slingshot", "lines": ["Warning indicator and shadow particles now show up 0.75 seconds before Zac lands. If his travel duration is shorter than that, they appear immediately.", "Cast range updated to be more accurate for Zac."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Hexplosive Minefield", "lines": ["Detonate timer now checks every 0.1 seconds from 0.25."]}]}]}
{"id": "V6.20", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V6.20", "date": "2016-10-05", "champions": [{"name": "Ashe", "changes": [{"about": "Frost Shot", "lines": ["Base slow changed to 10% - 20% (based on level) from 5% - 25% (based on level).", "Critical strikes slow increased to 30% - 60% (based on level) from 10% - 50% (based on level).", "New Effect: Critical strikes slow now decays to the base slow value over the first half of the slow duration."]}, {"about": "Ranger's Focus", "lines": ["New Effect: Instead of fully resetting Ashe's basic attack, casting Ranger's Focus reduces her basic attack delay to 40% of the full value (no reduction if the delay is already below 40%). If Ashe's delay between basic attacks is 1 second, casting Ranger's Focus brings that delay down to 0.4 seconds for the next attack.", "Active's damage per arrow reduced to 21 / 22 / 23 / 24 / 25% AD from 23 / 24 / 25 / 26 / 27% AD.", "Total damage per flurry reduced to 105 / 110 / 115 / 120 / 125% AD from 115 / 120 / 125 / 130 / 135% AD."]}]}, {"name": "Cho'Gath", "changes": [{"about": "Feral Scream", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 seconds from 13.", "Range increased to 650 from 585.", "Silence duration reduced to 1.5 / 1.625 / 1.75 / 1.875 / 2 seconds from 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 / 2.25 / 2.5.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where units would be hit if they had escaped the area after the cast."]}]}, {"name": "Diana", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Lunar Goddess Diana's health bar has been moved up to match her base skin."]}]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Cottontail Fizz's health bar has been moved up to match his base skin."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Perseverance", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where  Rift Herald couldn't disable Perseverance after it 'ranked up' at level 11."]}]}, {"name": "Hecarim", "changes": [{"about": "Devastating Charge", "lines": ["Bug Fix: The basic attack component of Devastating Charge can now critically strike, in line with similar abilities such as  Nasus'  Siphoning Strike."]}]}, {"name": "Ivern", "changes": [{"about": "Friend of the Forest - Innate", "lines": ["Ivern cannot attack or damage non-epic monsters. Instead, targeting a jungle camp initiates a 2.5-second channel that, upon completion, places the monsters within a grove. Placing a grove costs health and mana, and cannot be cast if Ivern lacks the resources.", "The grove matures over 40 - 6 (based on level) seconds. When fully matured, Ivern can interact with the camp again to instantly free the monsters, sending them away while receiving their full gold and experience bounty.  Smiting a camp within a grove will instantly free the monsters, regardless of its maturity or the monster's current health.", "If the camp's large monster has already been slain, Ivern will free the camp upon completing the channel at no cost. Similarly, the grove will instantly mature if the large monster is slain.", "Starting at level 5, freeing the  Red Brambleback or  Blue Sentinel leaves behind a sapling that can be picked up by an allied champion to gain the camp's buff, consuming it in the process. If at least one allied champion is nearby, Ivern can pick up the sapling to transfer it to the nearest one in range. If an ally kills either monster, they also leave behind a sapling that only Ivern can consume."]}, {"about": "Rootcaller - Q spell", "lines": ["Ivern throws a vine in the target direction, dealing 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 (+70% AP) magic damage to the first enemy hit and  rooting them for 1.2 / 1.4 / 1.6 / 1.8 / 2 seconds.", "Ivern and his allies can target enemies  rooted by Rootcaller to dash to them, placing themselves at their attack range from the target.", "Cost: 60 mana", "Cooldown: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12"]}, {"about": "Brushmaker - W spell", "lines": ["Passive: While in brush, Ivern's basic attacks gain bonus range and deal bonus magic damage. These bonuses persist for 3 seconds after leaving brush.", "Active: Ivern grows a patch of brush at the target location,  revealing the area within and around it for 3 seconds. Brushmaker spawns more brush if used near terrain or more brush.", "Brushmaker uses a stock system and Ivern can keep X in reserve.", "Cost: 30 mana", "Recharge: 40 / 36 / 32 / 28 / 24 seconds", "Cooldown: 0.5 seconds"]}, {"about": "Triggerseed - E spell", "lines": ["Ivern gifts a seed to the target allied champion, himself or Daisy, shielding them for 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 (+80% AP) for 2 seconds.", "After the 2 seconds, Triggerseed bursts, dealing 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+70% AP) magic damage to all nearby enemies and  slowing them by 70% for 3 seconds.", "Cost: 50 mana", "Cooldown: 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8"]}, {"about": "Daisy! - R spell", "lines": ["Ivern summons his sentinel friend Daisy, who remains on the field for 60 seconds as a controllable minion.", "While Daisy is active, Daisy! can be used to move her to the target location.", "Cost: 100 mana", "Cooldown: 160 / 140 / 120"]}]}, {"name": "Jinx", "changes": [{"about": "Flame Chompers!", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 70 / 120 / 170 / 220 / 270 from 80 / 135 / 190 / 240 / 300.", "Mana cost increased to 70 from 50.", "New Effect: Enemies now only take damage from one Flame Chomper per cast, even if they're hit by multiple explosions."]}]}, {"name": "Kled", "changes": [{"about": "Chaaaaaaaarge!!!", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Can now issue pings during Chaaaaaaaarge!!!."]}]}, {"name": "Kog'Maw", "changes": [{"about": "Bio-Arcane Barrage", "lines": ["Made Bio-Arcane Barrage's attack animation cool again.", "Updated Lion Dance Kog'Maw's hit particles for even more fireworks.", "Updated Bio-Arcane Barrage's visual effects across skins to match the new duration."]}]}, {"name": "Nunu & Willump", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Recommended items have been updated."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 59 from 56.86.", "Attack damage growth increased to 4 from 3.45."]}, {"about": "Visionary", "lines": ["New Effect: Now starts the game with 5 stacks, and refreshes the buff upon recalling or respawning."]}, {"about": "Consume", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds from 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9.", "Removed: Nunu receiving unique benefits for casting Consume on certain neutral monsters.", " Elemental Delight: Nunu gains 10% increased size and 10% maximum health as bonus health, also restoring health equal to the amount gained.", " Spooky Snacks: Killing a unit grants Nunu 15% bonus movement speed for 3 seconds.", " Mystery Meat: Nunu's attacks and abilities deal 1% of his maximum health as bonus magic damage.", "New Passive Effect - Feed the Yeti: Every large monster consumed feeds Willump, granting him a stack of Well Fed. Each stack of Well Fed grants Nunu 10 movement speed out of combat, 3% maximum health and size (stacking 5 times). Stacks refresh on each cast of Consume, falling off every 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 seconds.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where bonus health received from Consume didn't stack with  Cinderhulk."]}, {"about": "Absolute Zero", "lines": ["Removed: 0.25 seconds cast time.", "New Effect: Movement speed slow now increases to 95% over duration of channel."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Grand Skyfall", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Pantheon is no longer locked out of his active items if he dies during Grand Skyfall's channel."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "Broken Wings", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Battle Bunny Riven's sound effects for Broken Wings and  Wind Slash have been restored."]}]}, {"name": "Shyvana", "changes": [{"about": "Twin Bite", "lines": ["Animation has been visually sped up."]}]}, {"name": "Taliyah", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regeneration increased to 7 from 6."]}, {"about": "Threaded Volley", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 8 / 7.5 / 6 / 4.5 / 3 seconds from 10 / 8.5 / 7 / 6.5 / 4.", "Worked Ground duration reduced to 120 seconds from 140."]}]}, {"name": "Tryndamere", "changes": [{"about": "Spinning Slash", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed an edge case where Spinning Slash could damage allies he spins through if they were directly on top of an enemy unit."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Tumble", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a few spots where Tumble was able to move across ledges."]}]}, {"name": "Vladimir", "changes": [{"about": "Transfusion", "lines": ["Heal AP ratio increased to 35% AP from 15% AP.", "Crimson Rush bonus heal against minion reduced to 35% from 50%."]}, {"about": "Tides of Blood", "lines": ["Maximum magic damage AP ratio increased to 100% AP from 70% AP.", "Maximum magic damage health ratio reduced to 6% maximum health from 8% maximum health.", "Missile wifth increased to 60 from 40.", "Missiles spawned reduced to 15 from 20."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Mistwalkers and the Maiden will now teleport with Yorick if they were following him (does not occur if they were pushing a lane)."]}, {"about": "Shepherd of Souls", "lines": ["Threshold for summoning graves set to 4 on Howling Abyss."]}, {"about": "Dark Procession", "lines": ["Will now cast at his maximum range if Dark Procession is cast outside of its maximum range.", "New health bar."]}, {"about": "Mourning Mist", "lines": ["Removed: Minions marking. Now only marks champions and monsters."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Bouncing Bomb", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Master Arcanist Ziggs's Bouncing Bomb explosion visuals have been restored."]}]}, {"name": "Ivern", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health growth increased to 90 from 74.", "Base magic resistance increased to 32.1 from 30.", "Base attack speed increased to 0.644 from 0.625.", "Attack speed growth increased to 3.4% from 2.8%."]}]}]}
