{"id": "V6.14", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V6.14", "date": "2016-07-13", "champions": [{"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "Summon Tibbers", "lines": ["If Tibbers' target enters Fog of War, Tibbers now continues pathing to the target's last known location, rather than stopping in his tracks.", "Tibbers no longer forgets how to attack his target if crowd controlled.", "Bug Fix:  Fixed a bug where Tibbers couldn't be ordered to attack Inhibitors or the Nexus, though he sometimes decided to do so on his own.", "Bug Fix: Fixed a bug where Tibbers could fail to go berserk if Annie gave him a command at the moment she died."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Arise!", "lines": ["Soldier base damage changed to 50 - 170 (based on level) from 50 - 170 (based on level). Formula changed.", "Soldier vision range reduced to 350 from 575."]}]}, {"name": "Bard", "changes": [{"about": "Magical Journey", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Restored the pathing indicator line that appears between clicking on Snow Day Bard's Magical Journey and entering it to become a penguin."]}]}, {"name": "Braum", "changes": [{"about": "Unbreakable", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Braum no longer instantly dies if he tries to block  Baron Nashor's Acid Shot with Unbreakable at the exact wrong moment."]}]}, {"name": "Darius", "changes": [{"about": "Apprehend", "lines": ["Bug Fix: When pulling enemies over walls, no longer chest-bumps them back to the side they were on to begin with."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "Duelist's Dance", "lines": ["Health on vital hit increased to 30 - 115 (based on level) from 25 - 110 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Lunge", "lines": ["Bonus AD ratio increased to 95 / 100 / 105 / 110 / 115% bonus AD from 55 / 70 / 85 / 100 / 115% bonus AD."]}]}, {"name": "Gragas", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Fixed a texture issue on the top of Fnatic Gragas's barrel."]}]}, {"name": "Graves", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Bug 