 / 1.5 / 1.75% bonus damage per 1% missing health from 1.5% at all ranks.", "Maximum base damage changed to 8 / 45 / 125 / 247.5 from 10 / 50 / 125 / 225.", "Maximum AD ratio changed to 150 / 168.75 / 187.5 / 206.25% AD from 187.5% AD at all ranks.", "Maximum AP ratio changed to 72 / 81 / 90 / 99% AP from 90% AP at all ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Rengar", "changes": [{"about": "Unseen Predator", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the empowered attack wasn't trigger  Kircheis Shard's bonus damage nor its upgrades."]}, {"about": "Savagery", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where some on-hit effects weren't applying to the Savagery-empowered attack - including  Dead Man's Plate and  Sheen."]}, {"about": "Bola Strike", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Bola Strike was using target location instead of target direction input. This would cause him to throw the bola in a seemingly random direction if he was displaced during the cast time, including being displaced by Flash or Unseen Predator.", "Fixed a bug where the cast time on Bola Strike was sometimes shorter than 0.25 seconds.", "Fixed a bug where gaining 5 Ferocity during the cast time of Bola Strike would cause Bola Strike to consume the Ferocity upon completing the cast time, wasting the empowerment. This happens if his ultimate is active."]}, {"about": "Thrill of the Hunt", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where using an ability to exit stealth would sometimes cause his ultimate to only grant him 4 Ferocity over 5 seconds instead of 5."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "Starcall", "lines": ["Slow reduced to 30% at all ranks from 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50%.", "Rejuvenation movement speed reduced to 10% from 15%.", "Removed: Rejuvenation refreshing Windspeaker's Blessing bonus resistance."]}]}, {"name": "Swain", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Basic attack missile speed increased to 1800 from 1500."]}, {"about": "Carrion Renewal", "lines": ["Mana restoration increased to 13 - 30 (based on level) from 10 - 27 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Decrepify", "lines": ["Revised Active: Swain commands Beatrice to the fly to the target location, where she remains for 4 seconds. Beatrice will attack enemies within the area, prioritizing the target of  Torment, other champions in range and then any target in range. Beatrice's attacks deal magic damage and  slows.", "Mana cost reduced to 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 from 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100.", "Cooldown increased to 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 from 8 at all ranks.", "Duration increased to 4 seconds from 3.", "New Effect: Deals double damage against minions."]}, {"about": "Nevermove", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100 from 80 / 90 / 100 / 110 / 120."]}, {"about": "Torment", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 from 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235.", "AP ratio increased to 100% AP from 80% AP.", "Damage amplification increased to 20% at all ranks from 8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20%."]}, {"about": "Ravenous Flock", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 10 seconds from 8.", "Mana cost increased per second reduced to 5 at all ranks from 5 / 6 / 7.", "Number of ravens increased to 5 from 3.", "Now spawns 1 raven every 0.2 seconds, changed from 3 ravens every second.", "Heal from minions reduced to 15% from 25% of damage dealt.", "New Effect: Ravenous Flock cannot damage the same target for 1 second."]}]}, {"name": "Syndra", "changes": [{"about": "Transcendent", "lines": ["New Effect: Max rank  Dark Spheres now last for 8 seconds. Previous effect removed.", "New Effect: Max rank  Force of Will now grabs up to 2 additional spheres near the target. Syndra will throw the assortment of units in a way that increases Force of Will's area of effect, but it does not cause the ability to deal increased damage. Previous effect removed.", "The main purpose of this change is that Syndra will now reset the lifespan of up to 3 spheres, as well as placing all 3 spheres in a convenient location for Scatter the Weak."]}, {"about": "Dark Sphere", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 75% AP from 60% AP."]}, {"about": "Force of Will", "lines": ["Now displays a maximum throw radius while bending units to your will."]}, {"about": "Scatter the Weak", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 seconds from 18 / 16.5 / 15 / 13.5 / 12."]}]}, {"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base mana increased to 300 from 250.", "Mana growth reduced to 60 from 75."]}, {"about": "Bastion", "lines": ["Cast range reduced to 800 from 1100.", "Tether range reduced to 1300 from 1600."]}, {"about": "Dazzle", "lines": ["Range reduced to 575 from 650.", "Width reduced to 140 from 150."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Camouflage", "lines": ["Entering stealth won't interrupt autoattacks in wind-up."]}, {"about": "Blinding Dart", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 from 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110."]}, {"about": "Noxious Trap", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 75 at all ranks from 75 / 100 / 125.", "Recharge time reduced to 30 / 25 / 20 seconds from 34 / 28 / 22."]}]}, {"name": "Veigar", "changes": [{"about": "Phenomenal Evil Power (New Innate)", "lines": ["New Innate: Veigar gains a stack of Phenomenal Evil whenever he hits an enemy champion with an ability, and 3 stacks whenever he scores a champion takedown. Veigar gains 1 Ability Power for every stack of Phenomenal Evil."]}, {"about": "Baleful Strike", "lines": ["Passive AP stacking removed.", "Revised Tooltip: Killing a unit with Baleful Strike grants 1 stack of Phenomenal Evil, doubled for large minions and monsters.", "Champion kills with Baleful Strike grant a total of 5 stacks, combining the effects of hitting a champion with an ability (+1) and scoring a champion takedown (+3) in his passive and the killing a unit (+1) in this ability.", "Mana cost reduced to 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 from 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80."]}, {"about": "Dark Matter", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 from 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90."]}, {"about": "Event Horizon", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 from 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 / 100."]}, {"about": "Primordial Burst", "lines": ["Mana cost reducd to 100 from 125.", "Removed: Enemy AP ratio.", "Base damage reduced to 175 / 250 / 325 from 250 / 375 / 500.", "AP ratio reduced to 75% AP from 100% AP", "New Effect: Now deals [1% increased damage for every 0.67% of his target's missing health][1.5% increased damage for every 1% of his target's missing health], up to double damage to targets at 33% of their maximum health or less.", "Maximum damage: 350 / 500 / 650 (+150% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Vel'Koz", "changes": [{"about": "Organic Deconstruction", "lines": ["Base damage increase per level reduced to 8 from 10.", "Removed: Ultimate applying stacks.", "New Effect: Now scales with 40% AP."]}, {"about": "Plasma Fission", "lines": ["New Effect: Vel'Koz restores 20 / 22.5 / 25 / 27.5 / 30 Mana per target killed.", "Removed: Enemies can no longer see the target indicator."]}, {"about": "Void Rift", "lines": ["Initial AP ratio reduced to 15% AP from 25% AP.", "Detonation AP ratio reduced to 25% AP from 37.5% AP."]}, {"about": "Tectonic Disruption", "lines": ["AP ratio reduced to 30% AP from 50% AP."]}, {"about": "Lifeform Disintegration Ray", "lines": ["New Passive: Deconstructing enemies marks them as  Researched from 7 seconds. Basic attacks and ability damage will refresh this duration.", "New Effect:  Researched enemies take True Damage instead.", "Base damage increased to 500 / 725 / 950 from 500 / 700 / 900.", "AP ratio increased to 100% AP from 60% AP.", "Cooldown reduced to 120 / 100 / 80 seconds from 130 / 110 / 90."]}]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": [{"about": "Siphon Power", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 seconds from 10 / 8.5 / 7 / 5.5 / 4.", "Active's base damage increased to 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 from 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120.", "Active's AP ratio increased to 40% AP from 20% AP.", "Base shield changed to 8% of maximum mana from 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110.", "Shield's AP ratio reduced to 15% AP from 20% AP.", " Discharge's base damage changed to 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 from 20 - 210 (based on level)."]}, {"about": "Death Ray", "lines": ["Missile speed increased to 1050 from 780.", "AP ratio reduced to 50% AP from 70% AP.", " Aftershock's base damage reduced to 20 / 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 from 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230.", " Aftershock's delay increased to 1 second from 0.6.", "Removed:  Aftershock's damage reduction.", "Total damage changed to 90 / 170 / 250 / 330 / 410 (+120% AP) from 98 / 154 / 210 / 266 / 322 (+98% AP)."]}, {"about": "Chaos Storm", "lines": ["Duration reduced to 6.5 seconds from 7.", "Initial base damage reduced to 100 / 175 / 250 from 150 / 250 / 350.", "Initial damage AP ratio reduced to 50% AP from 55% AP.", "Tick base damage increased to 150 / 250 / 350 from 15 / 30 / 45.", "Tick damage AP ratio increased to 60% AP from 10% AP.", "Tick interval increased to 2 seconds from 0.5.", "Total damage increased to 550 / 925 / 1300 (+230% AP) from 360 / 670 / 980 (+195% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Vladimir", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health increased to 550 from 543.", "Health growth reduced to 84 from 85.", "Attack damage increased to 52 from 48.", "Base armor increased to 23 from 21.88.", "Armor growth reduced to 3.3 from 3.5."]}, {"about": "Crimson Pact", "lines": ["Bonus ability power increased to 4% bonus health from 2.5% bonus health.", "Bonus health reduced to 100% AP from 140% AP."]}, {"about": "Transfusion", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 / 160 from 90 / 125 / 160 / 195 / 230.", "Damage AP ratio reduced to 45% AP from 60% AP.", "Heal AP ratio reduced to 15% AP from 25% AP.", "New Effect: After casting Transfusion twice, Vladimir gains 10% bonus movement speed for 0.5 and Crimson Rush for 2.5 seconds the next time it becomes available to cast.", "Crimson Rush: Transfusion deals 100% increased damage and restores an additional 40 - 240 (based on level) (+5% (+2.5% per 100 AP) of his missing health) (healing halved versus minions). The empowered cast will count as the first stack toward the next Crimson Rush.", "Cooldown changed to 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 seconds from 10 / 8.5 / 7 / 5.5 / 4."]}, {"about": "Sanguine Pool", "lines": ["Health ratio reduced to 10% bonus health from 15% bonus health."]}, {"about": "Tides of Blood", "lines": ["First Cast: Vladimir begins charging, increasing Tides of Blood's damage while rapidly consuming 10% of his maximum health over the next 1 second. Vladimir is slowed by X% after the initial 1 second if he continues to charge. After 1.5 seconds or if interrupted, Vladimir will automatically use the second cast.", "Second Cast: Vladimir unleashes the stored blood in a nova of bolts, each dealing between 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 (+2.5% maximum health) (+35% AP) and 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 (+10% maximum health) (+70% AP) magic damage to the first enemy they strike. Enemies can intercept multiple bolts but can only be damaged once. Minions cannot block more than 5 bolts and if the bolts strike a minion, the bolt will do area of effect damage that only affects other nearby minions. If charged for at least 1 second, enemies hit are also  slowed by 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% for 0.5 seconds.", "Vladimir can cast Sanguine Pool without interrupting the charge of Tides of Blood, but the second cast of Tides of Blood will cause Vladimir to surface from Sanguine Pool early.", "Cooldown increased to 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 seconds from 4.5.", "Range: 600"]}, {"about": "Hemoplague", "lines": ["Duration reduced to 4 seconds from 5.", "Damage amplifier reduced to 10% from 12%.", "New Effect: Vladimir now heals for 75 / 125 / 175 (+35% AP) per champion damaged by the plague's detonation."]}]}, {"name": "Xerath", "changes": [{"about": "Arcanopulse", "lines": ["Width reduced to 145 from 150.", "Warning indicator now better matches the damage zone."]}, {"about": "Shocking Orb", "lines": [" Stun duration changed to 0.5-2 seconds from 0.75-1.75."]}, {"about": "Rite of the Arcane", "lines": ["Number of barrages increased to 3 / 4 / 5 from 3 at all ranks.", "Base damage changed to 200 / 230 / 260 from 190 / 245 / 300.", "Total damage increased to 600 / 920 / 1300 (+129 / 172 / 215% AP) from 570 / 735 / 900 (+129% AP).", "Range increased to 3520 / 4840 / 6160 from 3200 / 4400 / 5600", "Impact radius increased to 200 from 190.", "Delay between shots increased to 0.8 seconds from 0.6.", "New Effect: Camera now zooms out a bit when casting this spell.", "Updated particles."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated recommended items."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Movement speed increased to 340 from 335."]}, {"about": "Cell Division", "lines": ["Revive time reduced to 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 (based on level) seconds from 8 at all ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Short Fuse", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 30 / 40 / 50 (based on level)% AP from 25 / 30 / 35 (based on level)% AP.", "Cooldown reduction on ability use increased to 4 / 5 / 6 (based on level) seconds from 4."]}, {"about": "Satchel Charge", "lines": ["New Effect: Demolishes turrets below 25 / 27.5 / 30 / 32.5 / 35% of their maximum health."]}, {"about": "Mega Inferno Bomb", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 120 / 105 / 90 from 120 at all ranks.", "Removed: Double damage against minions."]}]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health increased to 499 from 479.", "Movement speed increased to 340 from 325."]}, {"about": "Garden of Thorns (Innate)", "lines": ["New Passive: Zyra spawns seeds nearby every 11 / 10 / X / X (based on level) seconds, occasionally spawning two at once. Seeds spawned by Garden of Thorns do not grant vision. There doesn't appear to be a metric to determine this. Seeds prefer spawning in brush and cannot spawn too close together, and the timer on her next seed wait if Zyra is concealed within a brush and there is no room for additional seeds. Zyra can only have 8 seeds planted at a time, which last for 45 seconds. Casting  Deadly Spines or  Grasping Roots causes nearby seeds to bloom plants, which last for a short duration and deal magic damage per attack. Plants beyond the first attacking a single target deal only 50% damage.", "Plant health reduced to 4 from 6.", "Plants now take 0.5 damage from on-hit effects per on-hit effect (e.g.  Blade of the Ruined King and  Toxic Shot) and applied damage over times (e.g.  Noxious Blast and  Blaze).", "Plant magic damage reduced to 29 - 114 (based on level) (+15% AP) from 29.5 - 140 (based on level) (+20% AP).", "Plant duration reduced to 5 - 7.5 (based on level) seconds from 10."]}, {"about": "Deadly Spines", "lines": ["Area of effect changed to a wide rectangle perpendicular to Zyra, from a circle.", "Increased plant spawning area relative to the damage area.", "Mana cost reduced to 60 at all ranks from 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 / 95.", "Base damage reduced to 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 from 70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210.", "AP ratio reduced to 55% AP from 65% AP."]}, {"about": "Rampant Growth", "lines": ["Removed: Cooldown reduction passive. Relative to what is listed on her article, it has been increased, but only because we track its cooldown factoring its own passive.", "New Passive: The health of Zyra's plants is increased by 0.4 / 0.8 / 1.2 / 1.6 / 2, for a total of 4.4 / 4.8 / 5.2 / 5.6 / 6.", "Active seed duration increased to 60 seconds from 30. Innate seeds last only 45 seconds."]}, {"about": "Stranglethorns", "lines": ["Removed: Plants gain 50% bonus attack speed.", "Added: Plants deal 50% bonus damage."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Twin Fang", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 0.75 from 0.9.", "Mana cost reduced to 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 from 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80.", "Cast range increased to 700 from 550.", "Range calculation changed to  center to center from  edge to edge."]}]}, {"name": "Malzahar", "changes": [{"about": "Call of the Void", "lines": ["Mana cost increased to 80 from 60."]}, {"about": "Void Swarm", "lines": ["Mana cost increased to 80 from 60.", "Damage versus monsters reduced to 50% from 75%."]}, {"about": "Nether Grasp", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 5 / 7 / 9% of the target's maximum health from 6 / 8 / 10%."]}]}, {"name": "Mordekaiser", "changes": [{"about": "Dragon Force", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where triggering Dragon Force would break the minimap notifications for dragons spawning."]}]}, {"name": "Swain", "changes": [{"about": "Decrepify", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 from 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85.", "Clarity: Added max leash range against minions and non-minions."]}, {"about": "Ravenous Flock", "lines": ["Bugfix: Ravenous Flock had a cast time."]}]}, {"name": "Vladimir", "changes": [{"about": "Transfusion", "lines": [" Crimson Rush's missing health heal AP ratio increased to 4% per 100 AP from 2.5%."]}, {"about": "Tides of Blood", "lines": ["Minimum damage increased to 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70.", "Maximum damage increased to 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 from 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140."]}]}]}
{"id": "V6.8", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V6.8", "date": "2016-04-20", "champions": [{"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Visual upgrade across all skins.", "New splash artwork for all skins.", " Original Taric", " Emerald Taric", " Armor of the Fifth Age Taric", " Bloodstone Taric", "New voice over.", "New lore.", "New ability icons.", "Title changed to the Shield of Valoran from the Gem Knight."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack range increased to 150 from 125.", "Base health reduced to 575 from 619.2.", "Base health regen reduced to 6 from 7.94.", "Base mana reduced to 250 from 349.08.", "Mana growth increased to 75 from 56.", "Base mana regen reduced to 5 from 8.5.", "Mana regen growth increased to 1 from 0.8.", "Base armor reduced to 25 from 25.876.", "Armor growth reduced to 3.4 from 3.7.", "Base attack damage reduced to 55 from 57.88."]}, {"about": "Gemcraft (Innate)", "lines": ["Renamed  Bravado.", "Number of empowered attacks increased to 2 from 1.", "Damage adjusted to 22 - 90 (based on level) (+15% bonus Armor) from 20% total armor.", "On-hit cooldown reduction reduced to 1 - 0.55 second from 2.", "Removed: On-hit cooldown reduction reducing his ultimate.", "New Effect: On-hit cooldown reduction is increased to 6 - 3.3 seconds toward his  Starlight's Touch cooldown.", "New Effect: Taric gains 100% total attack speed for the two attacks."]}, {"about": "Starlight's Touch (Q)", "lines": ["New Active: Taric expends all his current charges to heal himself and surrounding allied champion, as well as those surrounding his Bastion-protected champion, for 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 (+20% AP) (+1.5% bonus Health) per charge. Taric can store up to 3 charges, for a maximum heal of 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 (+60% AP) (+4.5% bonus Health).", "Cost: 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 mana", "Recharge time: 15 seconds"]}, {"about": "Bastion (W)", "lines": ["New Passive: Taric's and  Bastion-protected champion's armor are increased b