{"id": "V5.15", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V5.15", "date": "2015-08-05", "champions": [{"name": "Ekko", "changes": [{"about": "Z-Drive Resonance", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to (+80% AP) from (+70% AP).", "Slow reduced to 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 (based on level)% from 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 (based on level)%.", "Movement speed buff increased to 40 / 50 / 60 / 80 (based on level)% from 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 (based on level)%."]}, {"about": "Parallel Convergence", "lines": ["Base shield reduced to 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 / 160  from 150 / 195 / 240 / 285 / 330 .", "Shield Ability power ratio increased to (+150% AP) from (+80% AP)."]}, {"about": "Chronobreak", "lines": ["Base heal reduced to 20% of damage taken at all ranks from 20 / 25 / 30%.", "Heal Ability power ratio increased to (+6.66% per 100 AP) from (+3.33% per 100 AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash art.", "Model upgrade across all skins with a new animations for the new abilities."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "Bulwark", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it wasn't granting assists."]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Classic skin featuring Gangplank as he appears after the events of The Burning Tide.", "New voice over, which is applied to all of Gangplank's existing skins.", "His traditional skin (which was visually upgraded in V5.14) is being rebranded as Captain Gangplank and will be available in the store for  975. No word if the skin will be permanently available or whether it will be a legacy skin. Players also have the opportunity to unlock the skin for free by completing The Burning Tide's Epilogue: complete one matchmade game with Gangplank during the event. You do not need to have completed Acts 1, 2 and 3 to earn this reward. This skin will feature his traditional voice over (the one introduced in V5.14)."]}, {"about": "Parrrley", "lines": ["Barrel hitbox for Parrrley substantially reduced (i.e. how close the projectile has to get to count as having hit the barrel).", "On Dominion, Twisted Treeline and ARAM, you now passively gain 1  Silver Serpent per second."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": [{"about": "Javelin Toss", "lines": ["Cast time increased to 0.25 seconds from 0.125.", "Minimum damage reduced to 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 from 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150.", "Maximum damage reduced to 150 / 210 / 270 / 330 / 390 from 150 / 225 / 300 / 375 / 450."]}, {"about": "Bushwhack", "lines": ["On-cast vision radius reduced to 400."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "On the Hunt", "lines": ["Initial movement speed reduced to 40 / 50 / 60% from 60% at all ranks.", "New Effect: Allies that join the hunt later on will receivethe same movement speed boost Sivir has at the time. Previously any who entered the aura at any time would receive the enhanced MS boost for its 2/3/4s regardless of leftover duration."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Camouflage", "lines": ["Timer reduced to 1.5 seconds from 2.", "Attack speed changed to 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 (based on level)% from 40%.", "New Effect: While in brush, Camouflage will only take 0.75 seconds to trigger and moving within the brush will not break the stealth."]}, {"about": "Noxious Trap", "lines": ["Life span reduced to 5 minutes from 10 minutes.", "Slow now decays over the duration.", "Arm time increased to 1.5 seconds from 1 second.", "Cooldown reduced to 0.25 seconds from 1 second.", "New Effect: Shrooms now have 6 health and take 2 damage from ranged attacks and 3 damage from melee attacks.", "New Effect: Shrooms are now thrown rather than placed.", "Cast range increased to 300 / 600 / 900 from 230.", "New Effect: Shrooms will now bounce an additional 300 / 400 / 500 units if they are thrown onto another shroom. Shrooms can only bounce once, even if they land on a further shroom."]}]}, {"name": "Thresh", "changes": [{"about": "Damnation", "lines": [" Rift Scuttler now has a soul."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health growth increased to 92 from 80.", "Damage growth increased to 3.3 from 2.5."]}, {"about": "Lunge", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 from 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45.", "Cooldown reduced to 16 / 14 / 12 / 10 / 8 seconds from 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 / 10."]}, {"about": "Riposte", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 19 / 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 seconds from 21 / 19.5 / 18 / 16.5 / 15."]}]}]}
{"id": "V5.14", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V5.14", "date": "2015-07-22", "champions": [{"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "A new announcer pack has been added to the game for The Burning Tides.", "lines": ["Includes quotes for Summoner's Rift, Twisted Treeline, ARAM, Crystal Scar and Spectator.", "New announcements for successful surrender votes and victory.", "New announcements for when your structures are under attack (not just when they die).", "New \"encouraging\" quotes for the losing side when the enemy scores a kill (e.g. \"Make them pay!\").", "Alternative quotes for classic lines (e.g. \"Twice the bounty!\" as well as the standard \"Double kill!\", or \"Your matey's feedin' the fishes\" as well as \"Your ally has been slain\").", "Full voice-over can be found here."]}]}, {"name": "Ahri", "changes": [{"about": "Charm", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Charm causes monsters to freak out."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Shurima's Legacy", "lines": ["Removed: Granting Azir bonus attack speed from cooldown reduction"]}, {"about": "Arise!", "lines": ["New Passive: Azir gains 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60% bonus attack speed."]}, {"about": "Shifting Sands", "lines": ["No longer knocks up the first champion hit."]}]}, {"name": "Darius", "changes": [{"about": "Apprehend", "lines": ["Now briefly grants vision over the target area."]}]}, {"name": "Ekko", "changes": [{"about": "Timewinder", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 from 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100."]}, {"about": "Phase Dive", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 13 / 11.5 / 10 / 8.5 / 7 seconds from 15 / 13 / 11 / 9 / 7."]}]}, {"name": "Elise", "changes": [{"about": "Cocoon", "lines": ["Stun duration increased to 1.6 / 1.7 / 1.8 / 1.9 / 2 seconds from 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2."]}, {"about": "Spiderlings", "lines": ["Damage type changed to magical from physical.", "AP ratio increased to (+15% AP) from (+10% AP).", "Movement speed increased to 355 from 345.", "Fixed a bug which caused Spiderlings to not move or attack for 4 seconds after the first cast of Rappel."]}]}, {"name": "Evelynn", "changes": [{"about": "Hate Spike", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 from 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 / 100."]}, {"about": "Agony's Embrace", "lines": ["Slow increased to 40 / 60 / 80% from 30 / 50 / 70%."]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Complete visual upgrade featuring a re-imagined model as well as new animations, sounds and voiceover."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 56 from 62.", "Base health reduced to 710 from 712.", "Health growth reduced to 79 from 81.", "Health regen growth reduced to 0.6 from 0.75.", "Base mana reduced to 282 from 282.2.", "Base mana regen reduced to 7.5 from 7.675.", "Attack speed growth increased to 3.2 from 2.75.", "Base armor reduced to 26 from 26.044.", "Armor growth reduced to 3 from 3.3."]}, {"about": "Trial by Fire (Innate)", "lines": ["New Innate: Gangplank's next attack ignites the target dealing bonus true damage and grants bonus movement speed. Destroying a Powder Keg instantly refreshes Trial by Fire and grants the same bonus movement speed. Parrrley cannot activate Trial by Fire."]}, {"about": "Parrrley (Q)", "lines": ["New Effect: Killing units also grants Silver Serpents, a unique currency that can be spent to upgrade Cannon Barrage.", "Mana cost reduced to 50 from 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70.", "Mana refund on kill reduced to 25 at all ranks from 25 / 27.5 / 30 / 32.5 / 35."]}, {"about": "Remove Scurvy (W)", "lines": ["Heal changed to 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150 (+90% AP) (+15% of missing health) from 80 / 150 / 220 / 290 / 360 (+100% AP).", "Cost changed to 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 mana from 65 at all ranks.", "Cooldown reduced to 22 / 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 seconds from 22 / 21 / 20 / 19 / 18."]}, {"about": "Powder Keg (E)", "lines": ["New Active: Gangplank places a powder keg at the target location that he can attack to detonate, splashing the attack's damage to surroFixed a bug where forced action crowd control effects were stunning Scuttles.Fixed a bug where forced action crowd control effects and \u2603\u2603 were not triggering Scuttles' \"loses resistances while disabled\".unding enemies and slowing them for a short duration. The damage benefits from 60% armor penetration and champions take bonus damage. If detonated by  Parrrley, Gangplank will plunder from all enemies slain. The explosion sets off a chain reaction that explodes other nearby kegs - but the damage does not overlap. Enemies can also attack the kegs to safely destroy them (worth gold).", "No cost."]}, {"about": "Cannon Barrage (R)", "lines": ["Now fires clusters of 3 waves every 2 seconds, for a total of 12 waves over an 8-second period (changed from 7 waves over 7 seconds).", "Now  slows by 30% for 0.5 second (1 second per cluster) instead of 25% for the duration.", "Damage per wave changed to 50 / 70 / 90 (+10% AP) from 75 / 120 / 165 (+20% AP).", "Cooldown increased to 140 / 130 / 120 from 125."]}, {"about": "Gangplank has access to three unique items that can be purchased with Silver Serpents, a unique currency.", "lines": ["Death's Daughter: An initial, mega-cannonball precedes the barrage, dealing [a cluster worth][150 / 210 / 270 (+30%AP)] of true damageand  slowing enemies by 60% for 1.5 seconds.", "Raise Morale: Allies within the area gain 60% bonus movement speed for 2 seconds.", "Fire at Will: Launches 6 additional waves."]}]}, {"name": "Kalista", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated recommended items."]}, {"about": "Pierce /  Sentinel", "lines": ["Now properly queues up to cast after her basic attack completes."]}]}, {"name": "Miss Fortune", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Complete visual upgrade featuring an upgraded model as well as new animations and sounds."]}, {"about": "Strut", "lines": ["No longer falls off upon taking non-periodic damage."]}, {"about": "Double Up", "lines": ["Secondary targeting paradigm improved (again).", "New Effect: If the first shot kills the target, Double Up deals 50% bonus damage to the second target. Uses the crit animation."]}, {"about": "Impure Shots", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 12 seconds from 16.", "New Effect: Now instantly readies  Strut at full power.", " Grievous Wounds removed."]}, {"about": "Make It Rain", "lines": ["Slow changed to 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% from 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65%.", "Duratio reduced to 2 seconds from 3. Total damage unchanged."]}, {"about": "Bullet Time", "lines": ["Tooltip updated to indicate its  Impure Shots bonus magic damage."]}]}, {"name": "Rumble", "changes": [{"about": "Flamespitter", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Flamespitter was damaging untargetable enemies.", "Fixed a bug where the range wasn't consistent."]}, {"about": "The Equalizer", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where The Equalizer was damaging untargetable enemies."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Arcane Mastery", "lines": ["Stack duration decreased to 6 seconds from 10 seconds."]}, {"about": "Overload", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160 from 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200."]}, {"about": "Spell Flux", "lines": ["Initial damage reduced to 36 / 52 / 68 / 84 / 100 (+20% AP) from 50 / 66 / 82 / 98 / 114 (+30% AP).", "Secondary damage reduced to 18 / 26 / 34 / 42 / 50 (+10% AP) from 25 / 33 / 41 / 49 / 57 (+15% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Syndra", "changes": [{"about": "Force of Will", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Syndra could pick up  Baron Nashor."]}]}, {"name": "Tahm Kench", "changes": [{"about": "Tongue Lash", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 from 80 / 115 / 150 / 185 / 220."]}, {"about": "Abyssal Voyage", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 160 / 130 / 100.", "Passive health ratio increased to 4 / 6 / 8% from 4 / 5 / 6%."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Tumble", "lines": ["Cooldown now begins upon lauching the attack instead of upon