n if he exceeds maximum range."]}]}, {"name": "Veigar", "changes": [{"about": "Primordial Burst", "lines": ["Missile size now scales with Veigar's ability power. This will reduce the base size of the projectile for some skins, and is capped at 1500 ability power."]}]}, {"name": "Xin Zhao", "changes": [{"about": "Battle Cry", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to (+50% AP) from (+70% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "Rewind", "lines": ["New Effect: Cannot be cast if it wouldn't affect anything."]}]}]}
