s. Transforming into a human puts Spiderlings back into their dormant state."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "Idol of Durand", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 200 / 300 / 400 from 220 / 330 / 440.", "Damage amplifier increased to 10% from 5%.", "Maximum damage amplifier increased to 80% from 40%.", "Maximum damage increased to 360 / 540 / 720 (+108% AP) from 308 / 462 / 616 (+84% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Gragas", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regeneration reduced to 5.5 from 8.678.", "Health regeneration growth reduced to 0.5 from 0.85."]}, {"about": "Barrel Roll", "lines": ["Slow duration reduced to 1.3 seconds from 2.", "New Effect: Slow duration now increased to 1.95 seconds over the ferment duration."]}]}, {"name": "Jarvan IV", "changes": [{"about": "Demacian Standard", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 13 / 12.5 / 12 / 11.5 / 11 seconds from 13 at all ranks.", "No longer obstructs monster unit collision."]}]}, {"name": "Jax", "changes": [{"about": "Grandmaster's Might", "lines": ["Base resists increased to 30 / 50 / 70 from 20 / 35 / 50."]}]}, {"name": "Lux", "changes": [{"about": "Prismatic Barrier", "lines": ["New Effect: Lux now gains her initial shield instantaneously instead of after the 0.25 second cast time."]}, {"about": "Lucent Singularity", "lines": ["Slow zone radius increased to 350 from 300.", "New Effect: Can now be activated while in-flight to immediately detonate upon arrival."]}]}, {"name": "Malphite", "changes": [{"about": "Brutal Strikes", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 15 / 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 from 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85.", "Scaling changed to (+10% AP) (+10% armor) from (+15% AP).", "Damage radius increased to 225 from 200.", "Fixed a bug where Brutal Strikes could be seen through Fog of War."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Arcane Mastery", "lines": ["Duration reduced to 2.5 seconds from 6.", "Stack duration reduced to 10 seconds from 12.", "Cooldowns can now be completely reset rather than brought down to 0.25 seconds."]}, {"about": "Overload", "lines": ["New Passive: Increases  Arcane Mastery's duration to 3 / 3.5 / 4 / 4.5 / 5 seconds.", "Damage changed to 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 from 65 / 95 / 125 / 155 / 185.", "Missile width increased to 55 from 50.", "Mana cost changed to 40 at all ranks from 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50."]}, {"about": "Rune Prison", "lines": ["Damage changed to 80 / 100 / 130 / 140 / 160 from 65 / 95 / 125 / 155 / 185.", " Root duration changed to 1 / 1.1 / 1.2 / 1.3 / 1.4 seconds at all ranks from 0.75 / 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75.", "No longer cancels active movement/attack commands."]}, {"about": "Spell Flux", "lines": ["No longer cancels active movement/attack commands."]}]}, {"name": "Trundle", "changes": [{"about": "Subjugate", "lines": ["Total target's maximum health ratio increased to 20 / 27.5 / 35% from 20 / 24 / 28%."]}]}, {"name": "Tryndamere", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Tryndamere's critical strikes were taking longer to resolve than standard basic attacks."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Elastic Slingshot /  Let's Bounce!", "lines": ["Cleaned up the animations and animation bugs. No more running quickly out of the fog, hopefully."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "Rewind", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Q-W-Q was firing slower than intended."]}]}]}
{"id": "V5.11", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V5.11", "date": "2015-06-10", "champions": [{"name": "Aatrox", "changes": [{"about": "Blood Well", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 225 / 200 / 175 / 150 (based on level) seconds from 225 at all levels."]}]}, {"name": "Ashe", "changes": [{"about": "Ranger's Focus", "lines": ["The flurry no longer occurs against structures."]}, {"about": "Volley", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 from 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80."]}, {"about": "Hawkshot", "lines": ["The hawk's vision now updates more seamlessly while in flight.", "The hawk's vision radius while in flight has been reduced to 1000 units from 1500."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Arise!", "lines": ["Soldiers no longer spam their autoattack animation while idle."]}]}, {"name": "Brand", "changes": [{"about": "Pyroclasm", "lines": ["New Effect: If Brand's initial target becomes untargetable while the inferno is in flight, the projectile will select a new target instead of fizzling.", "Coming Soon: Pyroclasm will always select a new target if it's current target becomes untargetable while in flight. This didn't make it into this patch, though. Sorry."]}]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "Headshot", "lines": ["New Effect: Now ignores 50% of the target's bonus armor against enemy champions."]}, {"about": "Yordle Snap Trap", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the trap could take any time between 1 and 1.25 seconds to arm. It is now always 1.1 seconds.", "Fixed a bug where certain dashes could pass over the trap without triggering it."]}, {"about": "Ace in the Hole", "lines": [" Standard Sight is now granted on-click instead of after the 0.25 second cast time. The ability should no longer cancel if you lose sight of the target."]}]}, {"name": "Ekko", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Movement speed reduced to 340 from 345."]}, {"about": "Parallel Convergence", "lines": ["Tooltip corrected to show the actual maximum damage to monsters. (150, not 400)", "Mana cost increased to 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70.", "Parallel Convergence will now grant sight after 2 seconds - i.e. the ability grants sight only when enemies can also see the ability."]}, {"about": "Chronobreak", "lines": ["Improved visibility of the clone for the enemy team. You should only lose sight of the clone when it walks into the brush/fog, rather then when you lose sight of Ekko."]}, "Coming Soon: Mana cost implemented at 100. Although Riot is sceptical that this will solve any of the issues players have against Ekko."]}, {"name": "Hecarim", "changes": [{"about": "Warpath", "lines": ["The amount of bonus attack damage granted is now checked every 0.25 seconds instead of every 1 second."]}, {"about": "Devastating Charge", "lines": ["The bonus movement speed is now additive instead of multiplicative."]}]}, {"name": "Jayce", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New Efect:  Transform Mercury Cannon /   Transform Mercury Hammer can no longer be ranked and will automatically improve at levels 6, 11 and 16. Values unchanged.", "Each of Jayce's basic abilities now has 6 ranks."]}, {"about": "To the Skies!", "lines": ["Base damage changed to 30 / 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 from 20 / 65 / 110 / 155 / 200.", " Slow percentage progression remains unchanged and is 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 / 55%.", "Cooldown progression remains unchanged and is 16 / 14 / 12 / 10 / 8 / 6 seconds.", "Mana cost progression remains unchanged and is 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 mana."]}, {"about": "Lightning Field", "lines": ["Base damage changed to 100 / 160 / 220 / 280 / 340 / 400 from 100 / 170 / 240 / 310 / 380.", "Mana refund per basic attack progression is unchanged and is 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 14 / 16."]}, {"about": "Thundering Blow", "lines": ["Damage ratio changed to (+8 / 10.4 / 12.8 / 15.2 / 17.6 / 20% of target's max. health) from (+8 / 11 / 14 / 17 / 20% of target's max. health).", "Cooldown changed to 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 seconds from 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10.", "Mana cost progression remains unchanged and is 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 mana.", "Max damage to monster progression remains unchanged and is 200 / 300 / 400 / 500 / 600 / 700."]}, {"about": "Shock Blast", "lines": ["Base damage changed to 70 / 120 / 170 / 220 / 270 / 320 from 60 / 115 / 170 / 225 / 280.", "Mana cost progression remains unchanged and is 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 mana."]}, {"about": "Hyper Charge", "lines": ["Damage modifier changed to 70 / 78 / 86 / 94 / 102 / 110% from 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 110%.", "Cooldown changed to 13 / 11.4 / 9.8 / 8.2 / 6.6 / 4 from 13 / 11 / 9 / 7 / 5."]}, {"about": "Acceleration Gate", "lines": ["Movement speed bonus progression remains unchanged and is 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 / 55%."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Shunpo", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 from 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160.", "AP scaling reduced to (+25% AP) from (+40% AP)"]}]}, {"name": "Kha'Zix", "changes": [{"about": "Taste Their Fear", "lines": ["Isolation radius reduced to 425 from 500."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Distortion /  Mimic Distortion", "lines": ["Dash speed reduced to 1300 from 1600."]}, {"about": "Ethereal Chains /  Mimic Ethereal Chains", "lines": ["Missile width reduced to 55 from 70.", "Improved the rate at which the ability checks if the tether is broken by 400%.", "Fixed a bug where the ability would not root targets if they were protected by  Black Shield when hit initially, even if the shield was broken before the ability resolves."]}]}, {"name": "Malphite", "changes": [{"about": "Brutal Strikes - Rework", "lines": ["New Passive: 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% increased Armor.", "New Active: For the next 6 seconds, Malphite's basic attacks deal 25 / 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 (+15% AP) bonus physical damage to his target and surrounding enemies.", "New Effect: Attacks during the active now properly display the ability's AoE.", "New Effect: Attacks during the active use the critical strike animation."]}]}, {"name": "Orianna", "changes": [{"about": "Command Shockwave", "lines": ["The global cooldown on Orianna's abilities when the Ball snaps back to her is increased to 0.75 seconds from 0.5 seconds on Shockwave (ONLY)."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Arcane Mastery", "lines": ["A second attempt at fixing the bug from V5.10 where stacks were being generated on-click rather than after his ability's cast times - i.e. he will no longer gain stacks if his abilities fail to cancel due to his target dying or losing sight. The previous bug-fix only applied to  Overload."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "Flail of the Northern Winds", "lines": ["Updated the gameplay to match the change that erroneously only affected the tooltip last patch."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Base magic resistance increased to 32.1 from 30.", "Magic resistance growth increased to 1.25 from 0."]}, {"about": "Ki Strike", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 9 / 8 / 7 (based on level) seconds from 9 at all levels."]}, {"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Energy cost reduced to 100 / 95 / 90 / 85 / 80 from 100 at all ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Shyvana", "changes": [{"about": "Burnout", "lines": ["New Effect: While active, Shyvana's attacks will deal [25% of Burnout's damage][5 / 8.75 / 12.5 / 16.25 / 20 (+5% bonus AD)] as bonus magic damage.", "Fixed a bug where Burnout had double the AD ratio while in Dragon Form."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "On the Hunt", "lines": ["Duration of initial speed boost reduced to 2 / 3 / 4 seconds from 2 / 4 / 6. Total duration unaffected."]}]}, {"name": "Brand", "changes": ["The fireball will now select a new target whenever its active target becomes unavailable. As promised above."]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": ["Fixed a bug where Ace in the Hole would grant permanent vision of the target if they block the ability with a spell shield."]}, {"name": "Jayce", "changes": ["Fixed a bug where Hyper Charge would cause Jayce's melee form attacks to deal no damage.", "Fixed a bug where an in-the-air Hyper Charged attack would deal tons of damage if Jayce swapped into melee form before it hit."]}]}
{"id": "V5.10", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V5.10", "date": "2015-05-28", "champions": [{"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Dance", "lines": ["Distance placed behind enemy units is reduced to 100-200 from 150-250.", "New Effect: If the target is marked with  Mark of the Assassin, the distance is halved to 50-100."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Aspect of the Serpent", "lines": ["Health regain's AP ratio reduced to (+6% AP) from (+10% AP)"]}, {"about": "Twin Fang", "lines": ["Mana refund's Mana ratio reduced to (+1.5% of max. mana) from (+3% of max. mana)."]}]}, {"name": "Ekko", "changes": ["New champion."]}, {"name": "Gragas", "changes": [{"about": "Body Slam", "lines": ["Collision radius while moving reduced to 180 from 200.", "Collision radius at maximum range reduced to 210 from 250."]}]}, {"name": "Jinx", "changes": [{"about": "Pow-Pow[1]", "lines": ["Maximum attack speed bonus reduced to 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70% from 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130%.", "New Effect: Now also grants 0% - 70% (based on level) based on Jinx's level.", "Max. attack speed bonus increased to 140% from 130%."]}]}, {"name": "Karma", "changes": [{"about": "Gathering Fire", "lines": ["Cooldown reduction on-spell hit increased to 2 / 2.5 / 3 (based on level) from 2 at all levels.", "Cooldown reduction on-hit increased to 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 (based on level) from 1 at all levels."]}, {"about": "Focused Resolve", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to (+90% AP) from (+60% AP)", "New Effect: Can now also target monsters."]}, {"about": "Renewal", "lines": ["Bonus damage removed.", "New Effect: Root duration increased by 0.5 / 0.75 / 1 / 1.25 seconds."]}, {"about": "Inspire", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 from 10 seconds at all ranks.", "Mana cost reduced to 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 from 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100.", "Base shield amount reduced to 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 / 200 from 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240."]}, {"about": "Defiance", "lines": ["No longer deals damage.", "Now increases the target's shield by 30 / 90 / 150 / 210 (+30% AP).", "AoE shield changed to 50% total shield to target from 30 / 70 / 110 / 150 (+30% AP).", "New shield amount: 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 / 100 (+25% AP) (50% base shield to target) + 15 / 45 / 75 / 105 (+15% AP) (50% mantra bonus amount)"]}]}, {"name": "Leona", "changes": [{"about": "Zenith Blade", "lines": ["Missile width reduced to 70 from 90"]}]}, {"name": "Lulu", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base Mana regen. per 5s increased to 8.5 from 6.005.", "Mana Regen. Per 5s Growth reduced to 0.6 from 0.8."]}]}, {"name": "Rek'Sai", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 570 from 611.2."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Arcane Mastery", "lines": ["Duration increased to 6 seconds at all ranks from 4 / 5 / 6 based on rank.", "Effect is now triggered upon completing the 5th spell's cast time, rather than at the beginning the cast time. Arcane Mastery will no longer go off even if the spell cancels due to losing sight of the target."]}, {"about": "Overload", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 65 / 95 / 125 / 155 / 185 from 65 / 90 / 115 / 140 / 165."]}, {"about": "Desperate Power", "lines": ["Duration increased to 6 seconds at all ranks from 4 / 5 / 6 based on rank."]}]}, {"name": "Sejuani", "changes": [{"about": "Flail of the Northern Winds", "lines": ["On-hit magic damage lowered to (+4 / 4.5 / 5 / 5.5 / 6% of target's max. health) from (+4 / 5.5 / 7 / 8.5 / 10% of target's max. health). Due to a bug, this is only a tooltip change - but the in-game values will be nerfed ASAP."]}]}, {"name": "Sion", "changes": [{"about": "Unstoppable Onslaught", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it was scaling with the target's bonus attack damage instead of Sion's."]}]}, {"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "Imbue", "lines": ["Mana cost lowered to 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 from 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140."]}]}]}
{"id": "V5.9", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V5.9", "date": "2015-05-14", "champions": [{"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Crescent Slash", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to (+40% AP), up from (+30% AP).", "Cooldown reduced to 5 / 4 / 3 / 2 / 1 from 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 / 3.", "Now has a visual effect to show it's range, visible by both self/ally and enemy."]}, {"about": "Shadow Dance", "lines": ["New Effect: Now leaves Akali 150 - 250 units on the far side of target. The distance behind the target increases the closer the target is from Akali on-cast.[1]"]}]}, {"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack range reduced to 575 from 625."]}]}, {"name": "Ashe", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Basic attack's projectile speed increased to 2500 from 2000.", "Attack speed growth reduced to 3.333% from 4%."]}, {"about": "Frost Shots - Repurposed Ability", "lines": ["New Innate: Ashe's basic attacks and abilities apply Frost to enemies damaged, slowing them by 5 - 35 (based on level)% for 2 seconds. Ashe's basic attacks against frosted units always critically strike, dealing [10 +(X * (1 +Y))% AD bonus critical damage, where X is her critical strike chance and Y is her bonus critical strike damage (both in decimal format)][10% AD bonus critical damage, plus an additional 1% AD for every 1% of her critical strike chance that is modified by 1% for every 1% of her bonus critical strike damage]. Ashe cannot otherwise critically strike.", "Notes:", "Frosted targets are distinct from Slowed targets - only Ashe's Frost Shot can trigger the bonus damage. Other slows don't trigger it.", "Ashe's empowered attacks (even the base 10% AD with no crit chance) are classified as critical strikes for gameplay purposes and will trigger effects such as  Frenzy and  Reinforced Armor.[2] As such, it is also not applied by  Runaan's Hurricane.", "Here are examples on the behaviour of Frost Shot's bonus damage.[3] None of the following considers the 100% AD base damage from basic attacks.", " Infinity Edge will deal 40% AD bonus damage (10+ (20 x  (1+0.5)).", "Adding a  Phantom Dancer increases the aforementioned to 92.5% AD bonus damage (10+ (55 x  (1+0.5)).", "With 100% critical strike chance and  Infinity Edge's bonus critical damage, you will deal 160% AD bonus damage (10+ (100 x  (1+0.5)).", "Probable Bug: Critical strike damage from runes is stacking multiplicatively with Infinity Edge, rather than additively, for a maximum of 228.265% bonus damage (10+100 x 1.5 x 1.4551)."]}, {"about": "Ranger's Focus - New Ability", "lines": ["Passive: Ashe gains a stack of  Focus for 4 seconds whenever she slows an enemy, stacking up to 5 times. Ashe will not generate stacks while Ranger's Focus is on cooldown.", "Active: Ashe consumes all  Focus stacks to gain 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% bonus attack speed and increases  Frost Shot's slow strength [by 20%][to 25 - 55 (based on level)%] for 4 seconds. If Ashe consumes 5 stacks of  Focus on activation, Ranger's Focus will also cause each of Ashe's attacks to fire a flurry of five arrows, dealing [23 / 24 / 25 / 26 / 27% modified attack damage with each arrow][a total of 115 / 120 / 125 / 130 / 135% attack damage on each empowered attack]. The flurry will stack multiplicatively with  Frost Shots, will benefit from life steal and triggers on-attack effects five times, but on-hit effects are only applied once.", "Cost: 50 mana", "Cooldown: 18 seconds", "Notes:", "The multi-attack effect is similar to  Lightslinger and  Double Strike, except that on-hit effects aren't applied by the extra attacks.", "Triggering On Attack Effects multiple times is intentional.[4] - namely,  Runaan's Hurricane and  Pix. Note that Pix's cannot attack more than twice per second.", "On-hit effects are disabled on the latter four attacks and will not be triggered even by Runaan's minor bolts. As such, the item's 10 on-hit damage is only applied by the first attack.", "Runaan's splash damage is affected by the damage modifier - dealing [10 (+57.5 / 60 / 62.5 / 65 / 67.5 AD) damage per flurry][11.5 / 12 / 12.5 / 13 / 13.5% AD damage per arrow (+ 10 on the first)] to secondary targets.", "As with  Headshot, attacks against structures will refresh the timer on Focus but will not generate new stacks.", "The multi-attack effect will work on structures - i.e. you will plink towers faster than  Jinx."]}, {"about": "Volley", "lines": ["Arrows increased to 9 from 7. Radius is unaffected.", "Cost reduced to 50 mana from 60.", "Cooldown reduced to 12 / 10 / 8 / 6 / 4 seconds from 16 / 13 / 10 / 7 / 4.", "New Effect: Targets can now intercept multiple arrows, but will take no damage from arrows beyond the first. Arrows beyond the first will still generate Focus."]}, {"about": "Hawkshot", "lines": ["Passive gold generation removed.", "Range increased to Global from 2500 / 3250 / 4000 / 4750 / 5500.", "New Effect: Now works with a stock system, able to hold up to two charges.", "Static cooldown implemented at 5 seconds.", "Recharge time increased to 90 / 80 / 70 / 60 / 50 versus the current 60 / 55 / 50 / 45 / 40 cooldown."]}, {"about": "Enchanted Crystal Arrow", "lines": ["No longer innately slows, but will apply  Frost Shots' slow.", "Slow percentage effectively reduced to 5 - 35 (based on level) (+20% during Ranger's Focus)% from 50%.", "Slow duration effectively reduced to 2 from 3."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Arise!", "lines": ["Range indicator now shows the soldier's attack range at the end of the skill shot reticle."]}]}, {"name": "Bard", "changes": [{"about": "Caretaker's Shrine", "lines": ["Fixed a bug introduced in V5.8 that prevented Shrines from being self-cast."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Petrifying Gaze", "lines": ["Visual effects updated to match the actual area of effect."]}]}, {"name": "Hecarim", "changes": [{"about": "Rampage", "lines": ["Damage penalty against neutral monsters removed.", "Mana cost increased to 32 / 34 / 36 / 38 / 40 from 20 / 23 / 26 / 29 / 32."]}]}, {"name": "Kalista", "changes": [{"about": "Martial Poise", "lines": ["The dash range is no longer increased when moving away from the target."]}]}, {"name": "Morgana", "changes": [{"about": "Tormented Soil", "lines": ["Base damage per second reduced to 16 / 32 / 48 / 64 / 80 from 24 / 38 / 52 / 66 / 80.", "Max. base damage per second reduced to 24 / 46 / 72 / 96 / 120 to 36 / 57 / 78 / 99 / 120"]}]}, {"name": "Nasus", "changes": [{"about": "Fury of the Sands", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the health gained did not always happen instantly."]}]}, {"name": "Nocturne", "changes": [{"about": "Unspeakable Horror", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260 from 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250.", "Fixed a bug where the bonus movement speed wasn't triggering on fears other than Nocturne's."]}]}, {"name": "Olaf", "changes": [{"about": "Ragnarok", "lines": ["New Effect: Active now grants Olaf a 50 / 60 / 70% movement speed bonus when moving towards enemies for 1 second."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": [{"about": "Powerball", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where  Dash would send Rammus into space if dash paths him over a unit."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "Ruthless Predator", "lines": ["Now grants 50 bonus attack range.", "Cast time reduced to 0.5 seconds from 0.75. The \"self-stun\" duration."]}, {"about": "Dominus", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the health gained did not always happen instantly."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Movement speed reduced to 340 from 345."]}, {"about": "Wind Slash", "lines": ["Missile speed reduced to 1600 from 2200."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Spell Flux", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the secondary effect was classified as a single-target ability (and was triggering things like Muramana). The initial spell continues to be classified as a single-target abilities."]}, {"about": "Desperate Power", "lines": ["Passive's tooltip now properly displays  Arcane Mastery's increased duration.", "Fixed a bug where casting a spell at the end of Desperate Power's duration would cause that spell to not go on cooldown."]}]}, {"name": "Tristana", "changes": [{"about": "Explosive Shot", "lines": ["Now uses Tristana's basic attack cast time. (This means the spell's cast animation is reduced with your attack speed).", "Active's damage increase per basic attack increased to 30% from 25%.", "Max. damage increased to 132 / 154 / 176 / 198 / 220 / (+110 / 145 / 176 / 209 / 242% bonus AD) (+110% AP) from 120 / 140 / 160 / 180 / 200 (+100 / 130 / 160 / 190 / 220% bonus AD) (+100% AP)."]}]}, {"name": "Trundle", "changes": [{"about": "Pillar of Ice", "lines": ["Slow percentage increased to 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% from 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45%.", "Knockback distance increased to 225 from 150."]}]}, {"name": "Veigar", "changes": [{"about": "Event Horizon", "lines": ["Tooltip updated to reflect the actual delay of 0.5 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Xin Zhao", "changes": [{"about": "Crescent Sweep", "lines": ["Enemies are now stunned for 0.75 seconds upon landing."]}]}, {"name": "Zed", "changes": [{"about": "Death Mark", "lines": ["There is now a 1-second cooldown before Death Mark can be reactivated."]}]}]}
