", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 16 / 14.5 / 13 / 11.5 / 10 seconds from 10 at all ranks."]}, {"about": "Puncturing Taunt", "lines": ["Armor reduction reduced to 5 / 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 from 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30."]}]}, {"name": "Sion", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health regeneration growth reduced to +0.8 per 5 seconds from +1."]}, {"about": "Glory in Death", "lines": ["Initial health decay changed to 1 + (1 x level) from 2 x level.", "Health decay growth changed to 0.7 + (0.7 x level) from 1.4 x level."]}]}, {"name": "Sona", "changes": [{"about": "Hymn of Valor", "lines": ["On-hit damage AP ratio reduced to 20% from 25%."]}, {"about": "Aria of Perseverance", "lines": ["Base heal increased to 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 from 25 / 45 / 65 / 85 / 105.", "Heal modifier per% missing health reduced to 0.5% from 1%.", "Mana cost increased to 80 / 85 / 90 / 95 /100 from 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage reduced to 50.04 from 56.04."]}, {"about": "Astral Infusion", "lines": ["Range increased to 550 from 450."]}, {"about": "Equinox", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 24 / 22 / 20 / 18 / 16 seconds from 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14."]}]}, {"name": "Tryndamere", "changes": [{"about": "Spinning Slash", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it would occasionally deal double damage."]}]}, {"name": "Warwick", "changes": [{"about": "Infinite Duress", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 110 / 90 / 70 seconds from 90 / 80 / 70."]}]}]}
{"id": "V4.19", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V4.19", "date": "2014-11-05", "champions": [{"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Geometry and texture update to all skins, except Snow Day Singed.", "New base splash.", "New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Fling", "lines": ["Flinging an enemy champion into an area of  Mega Adhesive will root them for 1 second.", "Fixed a bug where Singed would occasionally Fling his targets in completely wrong directions."]}, {"about": "Insanity Potion", "lines": ["Bonus stats increased to 35 / 50 / 80 from 35 / 50 / 65."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Flash Frost", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Anivia wouldn't cast Flash Frost in the direction of the cursor if she wasn't in range to cast it."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Shurima's Legacy", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the damage from Azir's  Sun Disk would not ramp up properly like a tower."]}, {"about": "Emperor's Divide", "lines": ["Fixed a number of bugs around detecting enemies that are behind Azir at cast time.", "Fixed a number of double bounce bugs.", "Fixed a number of bugs that allowed enemies to dash through the wall if they timed their dash correctly."]}]}, {"name": "Fiddlesticks", "changes": [{"about": "Crowstorm", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where rapidly spamming a basic ability at the very end of Crowstorm's channel sometimes caused that ability to go on cooldown without casting or appearing to be on cooldown in the HUD."]}]}, {"name": "Janna", "changes": [{"about": "Howling Gale", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Janna wouldn't cast Howling Gale in the direction of the cursor if she wasn't in range to cast it."]}, {"about": "Zephyr", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 12 seconds at all ranks from 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Mirror Image", "lines": ["Flashing no longer de-stealths LeBlanc and her clone when Mirror Image is triggered."]}]}, {"name": "Lucian", "changes": [{"about": "Ardent Blaze", "lines": ["Bonus movement speed increased to 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 from 40 at all ranks.", "Attack damage ratio removed."]}, {"about": "The Culling", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 110 / 100 / 90 seconds from 100 / 75 / 50."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Grand Skyfall", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where rapidly spamming a basic ability at the very end of Grand Skyfall's channel sometimes caused that ability to go on cooldown without casting or appearing to be on cooldown in the HUD."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "Overload", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 from 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160."]}]}, {"name": "Sion", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health per level increased to 73 from 70."]}, {"about": "Glory in Death", "lines": ["Health decay's scale changed to champion level (2 x level first tick, increasing by 1.4 x level per tick) from max health (0.5% max health first tick, increasing by 0.4% max health per tick).", "Fixed a bug where  Sunfire Cape wasn't working while Sion was in his passive zombie state."]}, {"about": "Decimating Smash", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 from 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70.", "All crowd-control types now correctly refund Decimating Smash's cooldown to 2 seconds when they interrupt Sion while he's charging up."]}, {"about": "Soul Furnace", "lines": ["Health gain from large units increased to 10 from 8.", "Mana cost reduced to 65 / 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 mana from 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90."]}, {"about": "Roar of the Slayer", "lines": ["Mana cost increased to 35 from 25.", "Knocked back minions are no longer invulnerable to damage while in flight but can't be killed before landing unless Sion casts  Smite on them."]}]}, {"name": "Vi", "changes": [{"about": "Excessive Force", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Excessive Force wasn't properly dealing splash damage in its cone of damage."]}]}, {"name": "Warwick", "changes": [{"about": "Infinite Duress", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where rapidly spamming a basic ability at the very end of Infinite Duress's channel sometimes caused that ability to go on cooldown without casting or appearing to be on cooldown in the HUD."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "Heightened Learning", "lines": ["Range reduced to 1500 from global."]}]}]}
{"id": "V4.18", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V4.18", "date": "2014-10-09", "champions": [{"name": "Sion", "changes": ["Complete relaunch (essentially a new champion) - including new model (for all skins), animations, abilities, voice over, and artwork."]}, {"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Twilight Shroud", "lines": ["No longer grants 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 bonus resistances.", "Now grants 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 / 100% bonus movement speed, which decays over 1 second."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Flash Frost", "lines": ["Now has an indicator for the range of the explosion."]}]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 47 from 43.", "Base attack speed increased to 0.600 from 0.556."]}, {"about": "Shurima's Legacy", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where two Azirs could summon a Sun Disc at the same time.", "Fixed a bug where allies could use the ruins of a tower as a unit for allied-targeted dashes (e.g.  Safeguard).", "Reduced the interaction radius for summoning the Sun Disc by 20%.", "Fixed a bug in spectator where blue-side Sun Discs had no call-out on death.", "Coming soon: Fixed a bug where the Sun Disc does not benefit from Warming Up and Heating Up.", "Coming soon: Fixed a bug where attack-moving could activate Disc of the Sun. (this bug also applies to  Thresh's  Dark Passage."]}, {"about": "Conquering Sands", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where moving inactive soldiers into combat range with Conquering Sands would fail to activate their attacks properly, causing their attacks to deal 0 damage.", "Fixed a bug where Azir's soldiers would fail to cross a wall.", "Fixed a bug where damaging units at the very end of the charge would fail to attribute the damage to Azir (which affects things such as buff transfers, getting the kill credit, not applying spell effects, etc.)."]}, {"about": "Arise!", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where soldiers beyond the first were dealing no damage, rather than reduced damage. (This will be a functional buff).", "Fixed a bug where dancing would break Azir's soldier's basic attacks.", "Coming soon: Fixed a bug where soldiers only last 6 seconds on the Crystal Scar at rank-1 in Arise! (returns to normal at rank 2)."]}, {"about": "Shifting Sands", "lines": ["Azir can now cast Shifting Sands on soldiers moving through Conquering Sands, and will follow the soldiers to their destination (unless he collides with a champion).", "Improved the targeting AI: in the event that there is only one soldier on the field, you will automatically target it regardless of cursor position.", "Fixed a bug where Azir would occasionally dash to the wrong soldier.", "Fixed a bug where Azir could not cast Shifting Sands on soldiers very recently summoned.", "Coming soon: Fixed a but where Azir can leave the fountain on the Crystal Scar using W+Q+E."]}, {"about": "Emperor's Divide", "lines": ["Improved the targeting reticule to include the start point and existence of the dash.", "Fixed a bug where the initial charge was not applying crowd control (i.e. enemies could still cast and attack while being moved). Consequently, enemies can no longer activate dashes during the ability to get over the wall; and the charge will now correctly interrupt channels.", "The following things should no longer happen:", "Deal damage multiple times.", "Multi-bounce targets before they ever hit the ground.", "Pin targets to terrain, and will now push them over the terrain.", "Interact weirdly with spell shields; sometimes breaking and sometimes not, but always knocking enemies back. Spell shields will now correctly block the knockback.", "Low cooldown dashes can now longer get over the wall, such as  Spirit Rush and  Unseen Predator.", "Move the greater relics on Crystal Scar.", "Coming soon: Grant kill credit to Azir for invisible minions that are used as placeholders in many spells (e.g.  Acceleration Gate's pillars)."]}]}, {"name": "Diana", "changes": [{"about": "Moonfall", "lines": ["Now briefly reveals enemies hit."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Rising Spell Force", "lines": ["Attack speed buff duration increased to 6 seconds from 5 seconds."]}, {"about": "Mystic Shot", "lines": ["AD ratio increased to (+110% AD) from (+100% AD)."]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "Cannon Barrage", "lines": ["Damage is now dealt per second to the entire area, instead of per cannonball.", "There is now a maximum potential damage of 525 / 840 / 1155 (+140% AP), changed from anything between 0 (+0% AP) and 1875 / 3000 / 4125 (+500% AP) based on RNG.", "Cooldown changed to 125 / 110 / 95 seconds from 120 / 115 / 110 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Demacian Justice", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Demacian Justice would cancel if Garen lost sight of his target."]}]}, {"name": "Kha'Zix", "changes": [{"about": "Void Spike", "lines": ["Damage changed to 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 / 200 from 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235."]}]}, {"name": "Lucian", "changes": [{"about": "Relentless Pursuit", "lines": ["Mana cost increased to 40 / 30 / 20 / 10 / 0 from 0 at all ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Nunu & Willump", "changes": [{"about": "Absolute Zero", "lines": ["Will now list the minimum damage in the tooltip."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Soraka had no recommended items in ARAM."]}]}, {"name": "Tristana", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Attack speed per level reduced to 2.5% from 4%."]}, {"about": "Rapid Fire", "lines": ["Attack speed increased to 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110% from  30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90%.", "Duration reduced to 5 seconds from 7 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": ["Fixed SKT T1's logo on  SKT T1 Vayne's cloak."]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": [{"about": "Siphon Power", "lines": ["Bonus damage can no longer critically strike.", "Fixed a bug where the shield would not properly break against small amounts of damage."]}]}, {"name": "Wukong", "changes": [{"about": "Nimbus Strike", "lines": ["Can no longer select enemies Wukong cannot see as one of the additional targets."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": ["Base health reduced to 380 from 430.", "Base movement speed reduced to 340 from 350."]}, {"name": "Azir", "changes": [{"about": "Shurima's Legacy", "lines": ["The Sun Disc's health bar is no longer a blue blob."]}, {"about": "Emperor's Divide", "lines": ["Removed various unintended interactions between Emperor's Divide and untargetable stuff such as  Jayce's  Acceleration Gate."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Mystic Shot", "lines": ["Tooltip has been properly updated to reflect its new total AD ratio."]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "Cannon Barrage", "lines": ["Minions and monsters no longer attempt to attack Gangplank's ult.", "The center of Gangplank's ult no longer blocks first-target-hit skillshots."]}]}]}
{"id": "V4.17", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V4.17", "date": "2014-09-25", "champions": [{"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base mana increased to 280 from 250.", "Mana per level increased to 60 from 50."]}, {"about": "Noxious Blast", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 45% from 35%."]}, {"about": "Twin Fang", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Twin Fang's cooldown was only being reset to 0.7 seconds instead of the intended 0.5 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Perseverance", "lines": ["Cooldown changed to 9 / 6 / 4 (based on level) seconds from 9 at all levels.", "Health regeneration rescaled to 0.4 / 0.8 / 2 (based on level)% of max health per second from 0.4% at all levels.", "At level 11, non-epic monsters will no longer interrupt the effect."]}]}, {"name": "Heimerdinger", "changes": [{"about": "UPGRADE!!!", "lines": ["Can now be primed while Heimerdinger is disabled."]}]}, {"name": "Karma", "changes": [{"about": "Soulflare", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the ground effect would fizzle on Karma's death."]}, {"about": "Mantra", "lines": ["Can now be primed while Karma is disabled."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Mirror Image", "lines": ["The clone now spawns instantly and stealthed.", "Stealth duration increased to 1 second from 0.5.", "Breaking the stealth on either the clone or LeBlanc will remove the stealth on the other."]}, {"about": "Distortion", "lines": ["Reactivation time increased to 4 seconds from 3."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": [{"about": "Vengeful Maelstrom", "lines": ["Maximum bonus damage reduced to 100 / 150 / 200 from 200 / 250 / 300."]}]}, {"name": "Miss Fortune", "changes": [{"about": "Strut", "lines": ["Buff will no longer be removed by non-damaging effects."]}]}, {"name": "Nautilus", "changes": [{"about": "Dredge Line", "lines": ["Nautilus can now pull himself toward champion-created terrain."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage reduced to 44 from 49.", "Base attack speed reduced to 0.638 from 0.670."]}, {"about": "Takedown", "lines": ["Attack Damage ratio reduced to 0.75 / 1.875 / 2.5 from 1 / 2.5 / 3.33 (min/max/maxHunt).", "Ability Power ratio increased to 0.36 / 0.9 / 1.2 from 0.24 / 0.6 / 0.8 (min/max/maxHunt)."]}, {"about": "Pounce", "lines": ["On-kill cooldown reduction increased to 1.5 seconds (affected by cooldown reduction) from 1 (static).", "Revised Hunt Bonus: Nidalee can pounce on Hunted enemies at up to double range and  Pounce's cooldown is reduced to 1.5 seconds (affected by cooldown reduction) if she hit her target."]}, {"about": "Swipe", "lines": ["No longer affects the cooldown of  Pounce when used on a Hunted target."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": [{"about": "Powerball and  Defensive Ball Curl", "lines": ["The effects of Rammus' stances will now persist for 1 second after he changes the stance, instead of being removed instantly."]}]}, {"name": "Sona", "changes": [{"about": "Hymn of Valor", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the damage range was 700 instead of the intended 850."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 53 from 44.8.", "Base health reduced to 398 from 405.", "Health per level increased to 78 from 76.", "Base health regen reduced to 3.5 from 4.5.", "Health regen per level increased to 0.7 from 0.55.", "Base mana increased to 250 from 240.", "Base mana regen increased to 7.8 from 6.8.", "Base movement speed reduced to 325 from 340."]}, {"about": "Salvation", "lines": ["New Innate: Soraka gains 70% bonus movement speed while moving toward allied champions below 40% of their maximum health who are outside of  Astral Infusion's range. (Allies must be within 2500 range of Soraka.)"]}, {"about": "Starcall", "lines": ["Revised Active: Soraka calls down a star at a target location, dealing damage to enemies at the point of impact. The drop speed is longer the further away the ability is cast. Enemies hit directly take 50% increased damage and are slowed by 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% for 2 seconds.", "Base damage increased to 70 / 110 / 15 / 190 / 230 from 40 / 65 / 90 / 115 / 140.", "AP ratio reduced to 35% AP from 40% AP.", "Cooldown increased to 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 seconds from 2.5.", "Mana cost increased to 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90 from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70."]}, {"about": "Astral Blessing", "lines": ["Changed to  Astral Infusion", "Armor buff removed.", "Heal rescalled to 120 / 150 / 180 / 210 / 240 (+60% AP) from 70 / 120 / 170 / 220 / 270 (+35% AP).", "Now costs 10% of Soraka's maximum health in addition to mana.", "Mana cost reduced to 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 from 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 / 160.", "Remember that health costs cannot kill, and will always leave the caster on at least 1 health.", "Cannot be cast while below 5% of her maximum health.", "Cooldown reduced to 4 / 3.5 / 3 / 2.5 / 2 seconds from 20.", "Range reduced to 450 from 750.", "New passive: For each enemy champion hit by  Starcall, Soraka restores 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 (+20% AP) health. The amount is increased by 1% for every 1% of Soraka's missing health to a maximum of 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 (+40% AP)."]}, {"about": "Infuse", "lines": ["Changed to  Equinox.", "New Active: Soraka creates a zone at the target location for 1.5 seconds, dealing 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 (+40% AP) magic damage to the enemy Champions in the cast radius. Enemies standing in the zone are silenced till they leave. When the zone disappears all enemy Champions still standing on the zone are rooted for 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds and are dealt 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 (+40% AP) magic damage.", "Cost: 70 mana", "Cooldown: 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14 seconds", "Range: 925"]}, {"about": "Wish", "lines": ["Heal is now increased by 50% on allied champions below 40% of their maximum health.", "Now notes it removes all instances of Grievous Wounds before healing."]}]}, {"name": "Talon", "changes": [{"about": "Noxian Diplomacy", "lines": ["Animation sped up. This does not affect gameplay."]}, {"about": "Cutthroat", "lines": ["Silence removed.", "Now slows the enemy champion by 99% for 0.25 seconds."]}, {"about": "Shadow Assault", "lines": ["Now has a haste animation for while Talon is hasted."]}]}, {"name": "Tristana", "changes": [{"about": "Buster Shot", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 100 / 85 / 70 seconds from 60 at all ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash artwork.", "Model and texture update.", "New ability icons."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack speed increased to 0.658 from 0.625."]}, {"about": "Glorious Evolution (Innate)", "lines": ["Viktor starts the game with a  Prototype Hex Core, which grants 3 AP per level. Viktor can upgrade the core 3 times for 1000 gold each, with each upgrading granting +1 AP per level, +20 AP, +150 Mana and an augment to the basic ability of Viktor's choice. The upgrades accumulate into  Perfect Hex Core, which grants a total of +6 AP per level, +60 AP, +500 Mana, augments for each of his basic abilities and also upgrading his ultimate."]}, {"about": "Power Transfer (Q)", "lines": ["Renamed to  Siphon Power.", "Upgrade renamed to Augment: Turbocharge from Augment: Power.", "Range is now calculated edge-to-edge instead of center-to-center, increasing the range by an average of 100 units (although varies depending on the size of the target).", "Cooldown changed to 10 / 8.5 / 7 / 5.5 / 4 from 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5.", "Base damage reduced to 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 from 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260.", "AP ratio reduced to  20% AP from 65% AP.", "Now modifies Viktor's next basic attack to deal 20-210 (depending on Viktor's level) (+50% AP)(+100% AD) magic damage.", "There is no physical damage component.", "Base shield amount changed to 30 / 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 from 32 / 50 / 68 / 86 / 104.", "Shield AP scaling reduced to 20% AP from 26% AP.", "Shield and speed boost (Augment) duration reduced to 2.5 seconds from 3 seconds.", "Shield, speed boost and empower all granted immediately upon cast."]}, {"about": "Gravity Field (W)", "lines": ["Upgrade renamed to Augment: Implosion from Augment: Gravity.", "Range increased to 700 from 625.", "Particle starts playing as soon as Viktor starts cast, time between start of cast and enemy being slowed is unchanged.", "Stunned enemies are no longer affected by the slow.", "Evolution no longer increases range but instead drags stunned enemies into the center."]}, {"about": "Death Ray (E)", "lines": ["Upgrade renamed to Augment: Aftershock from Augment: Death.", "Evolution no longer applies a damage over time.", "Evolution now causes a trail of explosions to follow the  Death Ray's path, dealing the same damage again.", "Enemies hit by the laser will take only 40% damage from the trail.", "The total damage of landing both parts increased to 140% from 130%.", "Missile speed of the exploding trail is faster than the laser."]}, {"about": "Chaos Storm (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Cast time reduced to 0.25 seconds from 0.33.", "Cooldown reduced to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 120 at all ranks.", "Radius of initial impact increased to 325 from 250.", "Radius of DOT zone reduced to 325 from 350.", "Storm always moves at maximum speed when moving towards Viktor (still moves slower when moving away from him, based on how far away).", "Damage changed to 15 / 30 / 45 (+10% AP) per 0.5 seconds from 10 / 15 / 20 (+6% AP) per 0.25 seconds.", "Damage per second changed to 30 / 60 / 90 (+20% AP) from 40 / 60 / 80 (+24% AP).", "No longer silences on impact, but will still interrupt channels.", "Now has an Augment:", "Augment: Velocity -  Chaos Storm moves 20% faster."]}]}, {"name": "Yasuo", "changes": [{"about": "Steel Tempest", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Steel Tempest was put on a shorter cooldown if cast in conjunction with  Sweeping Blade."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "Chronoshift", "lines": ["Size of spinning hourglasses increased by 50%."]}]}]}
{"id": "V4.16", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V4.16", "date": "2014-09-10", "champions": [{"name": "Azir", "changes": ["New champion."]}, {"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash artwork."]}]}, {"name": "Amumu", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New lore."]}]}, {"name": "Brand", "changes": [{"about": "Pyroclasm", "lines": ["Now has a secondary targeting indicator that shows bounce radius."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash artwork.", "Model and texture upgrade to all skins.", "New voice over, including special quotes for Ascension.", "New lore."]}, {"about": "Aspect of the Serpent", "lines": ["New Innate: Cassiopeia permanently gains a stack of Aspect of the Serpent for:", "Poisoning an enemy champion (per second)", "Killing a poisoned unit", "Casting Twin Fang on an enemy champion.", "A maximum of 400 stacks can be held, and grants different bonuses based on the current amount:", "75 Stacks: 5% increased ability power. Twin Fang now heals Cassiopeia for 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 16 (+10% AP).", "200 Stacks: 10% increased ability power and gains 25% cooldown reduction.", "400 Stacks: 30% increased ability power."]}, {"about": "Noxious Blast", "lines": ["New ability animation.", "AP scaling reduced to (+35% AP) from (+80% AP).", "Bonus movement speed changed to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% from 15 / 17.5 / 20 / 22.5 / 25%.", "Cooldown increased to 4 seconds from 3.", "Mana cost changed to 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60 from 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 / 75.", "Delay increased to 0.65 seconds from 0.6."]}, {"about": "Miasma", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 per second from 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65.", "AP scaling reduced to (+10% AP) per second from (+15% AP).", "Slow increased to 25 / 30 / 35 / 40 / 45% from 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35%.", "Cooldown increased to 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 seconds from 9 at all ranks.", "Mana cost reduced to 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 from 70 / 80 / 90 / 100 / 120."]}, {"about": "Twin Fang", "lines": ["Base damage changed to 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 / 155 from 50 / 85 / 120 / 155 / 190.", "AP scaling changed to (+40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% AP) from (+55% AP) at all ranks.", "Mana cost reduced to 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 from 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90.", "Killing an enemy with Twin Fang will restore 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 (+3% max mana).", "Significantly improved poison-detection for the purposes of on-hit cooldown reduction.", "This includes detecting if the target is poisoned on-cast, meaning the cooldown can be reduced before you've even damaged the enemy."]}, {"about": "Petrifying Gaze", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 150 / 250 / 350 from 200 / 325 / 450.", "AP scaling reduced to (+50% AP) from (+60% AP).", "Cooldown reduced to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 130 / 120 / 110."]}]}, {"name": "Corki", "changes": [{"about": "Valkyrie", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Valkyrie being interrupted would halt Corki's movement but still extend Valkyrie's damage field."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New lore."]}]}, {"name": "Gnar", "changes": [{"about": "GNAR!", "lines": ["Now detects collision with player created terrain (Anivia's Crystallize, Azir's Emperor's Divide, Jarvan's Cataclysm and Trundle's Pillar of Ice).", "Fixed a bug where using GNAR! on a dashing unit would cancel their movement, but not stun them, if they hit a wall."]}]}, {"name": "Irelia", "changes": [{"about": "Bladesurge", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where stopping Bladesurge mid-dash would still deal damage to her target."]}]}, {"name": "Nasus", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New lore."]}]}, {"name": "Orianna", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash artwork."]}]}, {"name": "Poppy", "changes": [{"about": "Heroic Charge", "lines": ["Now detects collision with player created terrain (Anivia's Crystallize, Azir's Emperor's Divide, Jarvan's Cataclysm and Trundle's Pillar of Ice)."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New lore."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Model and texture upgrade to Classic, Galactic, Outback and Bloodfury Renekton.", "Additional quotes, including special quotes for Ascension.", "New lore.", "New splash artwork."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where taunting dead champions would give Shen bonus energy."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Additional quotes, including special quotes for Ascension."]}]}, {"name": "Skarner", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New lore."]}]}, {"name": "Urgot", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New basic attack animation."]}]}, {"name": "Varus", "changes": [{"about": "Piercing Arrow", "lines": ["Line indicator removed (Now uses range circle again as per previous functionality)."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Condemn", "lines": ["Now detects collision with player created terrain (Anivia's Crystallize, Azir's Emperor's Divide, Jarvan's Cataclysm and Trundle's Pillar of Ice)."]}]}, {"name": "Vladimir", "changes": [{"about": "Tides of Blood", "lines": ["Now correctly increases healing from Vladimir's Spell Vamp (and Lifesteal)."]}]}, {"name": "Xerath", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New lore.", "Additional quotes, including special quotes for Ascension."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "Chronoshift", "lines": ["Now subtly tints the target's screen."]}]}]}
{"id": "V4.15", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V4.15", "date": "2014-08-27", "champions": [{"name": "Alistar", "changes": [{"about": "Headbutt", "lines": ["Alistar can no longer land an additional basic attack on his target while airborne."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Miasma", "lines": ["Base magic damage per second reduced to 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 from 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65.", "Maximum potential magic damage reduced to 180 / 270 / 360 / 450 / 540 from 225 / 315 / 405 / 495 / 585."]}]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where abilities that give true sight of enemy champions would reveal stealth wards under certain circumstances."]}]}, {"name": "Fiddlesticks", "changes": [{"about": "Drain", "lines": ["Tether range increased to 800 from 750.", "Refresh rate reduced to 0.25 seconds from 0.5 seconds.", "Overall damage unchanged.", "Fixed a bug where the tether would occasionally snap prematurely if an opponent moved out of a specific range within a certain window of time."]}]}, {"name": "Graves", "changes": [{"about": "Collateral Damage", "lines": ["Tooltip fixed to state the actual explosion damage as 200 / 320 / 440 instead of 200 / 280 / 360 (undocumented change from V4.13)."]}]}, {"name": "Gnar", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Recommended items have been updated."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regen increased to 5 per 5 seconds from 3."]}, {"about": "Rage Gene", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Gnar wouldn't gain bonus health immediately upon transformation."]}, {"about": "Boomerang Throw", "lines": ["Outgoing missile width increased to 60 from 45.", "Return missile width increased to 75 from 70.", "Minimum missile speed increased to 1400 from 1000.", "Boomerang's return logic has been improved to better track Gnar.", "Boomerang's return particles have been improved."]}, {"about": "Boulder Toss", "lines": ["Missile speed increased to 2100 from 2000.", "Missile width increased to 90 from 80.", "The delay before picking up boulders off the ground reduced to 0.3 seconds from 0.5 seconds.", "Now checks to for enemy champions that are very close to Gnar's center point when he casts (and now hits them).", "Now deals area of effect damage in a small radius on landing if it hits no enemies."]}, {"about": "Wallop", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where enemies could sometimes cast spells when Wallop's stun was overlapped with GNAR!'s stun."]}, {"about": "GNAR!", "lines": ["Now has a 50% AP scaling.", "Casting time reduced to 0.4 seconds from 0.5 seconds.", "Fixed a bug where GNAR!'s knockback ministun (not the wall stun) would sometimes be removed too early."]}]}, {"name": "Jarvan IV", "changes": [{"about": "Martial Cadence", "lines": ["Debuff duration increased to 10 / 9 / 8 seconds from 10 / 8 / 6."]}, {"about": "Dragon Strike", "lines": ["Armor shred reduced to 10 / 12 / 14 / 16 / 18% from 10 / 14 / 18 / 22 / 26%."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Shunpo", "lines": ["No longer benefits from spell vamp on wards despite doing no damage."]}]}, {"name": "Kayle", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated Twisted Treeline recommended items."]}]}, {"name": "Lee Sin", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where abilities that give true sight of enemy champions would reveal stealth wards under certain circumstances."]}]}, {"name": "Leona", "changes": [{"about": "Solar Flare", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 100 / 90 / 80 seconds from 90 / 75 / 60."]}]}, {"name": "Nocturne", "changes": [{"about": "Duskbringer", "lines": ["The particles for Dusk Trail no longer obscure other particle effects."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Aegis Protection (Dominion only)", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Aegis Protection was not blocking shots from Dominion towers."]}, {"about": "Grand Skyfall", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the landing circle indicator for  Grand Skyfall sometimes showed as green (blue in colorblind mode) for his enemies instead of red."]}]}, {"name": "Rengar", "changes": [{"about": "Thrill of the Hunt", "lines": ["The stealth indicator no longer persists through death if Rengar dies after casting Thrill of the Hunt but before gaining the stealth effect."]}]}, {"name": "Rumble", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Rumble's  Flamespitter and  Scrap Shield should be more responsive in being affected (or not affected) by  Danger Zone bonuses even if they're cast immediately after going above or below 50 Heat.", "Fixed a bug where Rumble's basic attack would cancel if he was in the middle of attacking while Overheat expired.", "Fixed a bug where Rumble would occasionally not receive bonus magic damage on his first basic attack during Overheat .", "Fixed a bug where Rumble wouldn't fade out when he entered brush during Overheat .", "Fixed a bug where  Super Galaxy Rumble would occasionally fire a  Danger Zone  Electro Harpoon on his second cast, even if his first cast wasn't in the  Danger Zone."]}]}, {"name": "Shyvana", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New splash art."]}, {"about": "Flame Breath", "lines": ["Adjusted Flame Breath's dragon form particles to better match the damage cone.", "Actual area of effect remains unchanged.", "Fixed a bug where Flame Breath was dealing an extra 20 damage at Rank 1. Shyvana's damage now accurately reflects the tooltip (at 60 damage)."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "Boomerang Blade", "lines": ["The crossblade now accurately deals damage when the edge of the projectile hits an opponent, changed from thecenter of the projectile.", "Range increased to 1250 from 1175 (to match the visuals).", "Fixed a bug where Sivir's basic attacks would cancel whenever  Boomerang Blade would begin its return."]}]}, {"name": "Twisted Fate", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where abilities that give true sight of enemy champions would reveal stealth wards unde