uff icon."]}, {"about": "Double Up", "lines": ["Damage to first target changed to 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 (+85% AD) from 25 / 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 (+75% AD).", "Damage to second target changed to 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+100% AD) from 30 / 72 / 114 / 156 / 195 (+90% AD).", "Criteria for 2nd target selection rework.", "Will first prioritize enemy champions marked by Impure Shots within a 40\u00b0 cone.", "Will then attempt to find a target immediately behind the target, to avoid cases where it looks like it should have bounced to them.", "Will then attempt to find a target within a 20\u00b0 cone, prioritizing minions/monsters over champions.", "Will then attempt to find a target within a 40\u00b0 cone, prioritizing minions/monsters over champions.", "Will then attempt to find any target within a 90\u00b0 cone.", "Mana cost reduced to 43 / 46 / 49 / 52 / 55 from 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90.", "Cooldown reduced to 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 / 3 seconds from 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5."]}, {"about": "Impure Shots", "lines": ["Passive now deals 6% AD bonus magical damage per stack instead of 4 / 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 (+5% AP) bonus magical damage.", "Maximum damage changed to 30% AD magical damage from 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 (+25% AP) magical damage.", "Attack speed bonus changed to 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60% from 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50%.", "Grievous Wounds duration reduced to 2 seconds from 3.", "Mana cost reduced to 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 from 50 at all ranks.", "Cooldown reduced to 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 from 16."]}, {"about": "Make It Rain", "lines": ["Tooltip updated to clarify that there's a half-second delay.", "Area of sight increased to match the area of damage.", "Slow increased to 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65% from 20 / 28 / 36 / 44 / 52%.", "Cooldown reduced to 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 seconds from 15 at all ranks.", "Duration increased to 3 seconds from 2.", "Total damage is unchanged."]}, {"about": "Bullet Time", "lines": ["New Passive: Increases the stack limit of Impure Shots to 6 / 7 / 8, for a new maximum potential damage of 36 / 42 / 48% AD.", "Damage per wave reduced to 50 / 75 / 125 (+20% AP) from 65 / 95 / 125 (+20% AP)(+35% bonus AD).", "Now applies the passive on Impure Shots (not the active Grievous Wound)."]}]}, {"name": "Nami", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["New recommended items."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Aegis Protection", "lines": ["Will now block the next attack from a tower, champion, large monster or large minion attacks, instead of any attack that deal above a certain value of damage."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "Dominus", "lines": ["Bonus health changed to 200 / 400 / 800 from 300 / 450 / 600.", "Damage per second changed to 30 / 60 / 120 from 40 / 70 / 100."]}]}, {"name": "Rengar", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base armor increased to 20 from 16.", "Base health increased to 525 from 520.", "Health per level increased to 90 from 85."]}, {"about": "Bonetooth Necklace", "lines": ["Item reclassified as a trinket and is now free. It is available in four different versions:  Blue,  Red,  Yellow and Green (for maps where sight trinkets are unavailable). Upgrades at 6 Trophies.", "Attack damage and attack damage per level removed.", "Trophy passive given the name \"Mementos of the Hunt\". All trophy bonuses changed.", "3 Trophies - Rengar gains flat movement speed while out of combat or while in brush.", "6 Trophies -  Unseen Predator's range is increased by 125.", "12 Trophies -  Thrill of the Hunt stealth duration is increased.", "20 Trophies -  Thrill of the Hunt's bonus movement speed is doubled.", "Trophies are no longer lost on-death."]}, {"about": "Savagery", "lines": ["Time to trigger the enhanced attack increased to 3 seconds from 2.", "Base damage changed to 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 from 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150.", "Attack damage scaling increased to (+100 / 105 / 110 / 115 / 120% AD) from (+100% AD) at all ranks.", "Cooldown reduced to 6 / 5.5 / 5 / 4.5 / 4 seconds from 8 / 7.5 / 7 / 6.5 / 6.", "Bonus attack speed removed.", "Savagery can no longer be triggered on towers.", "Bug fix: The ability's damage is no longer affected when the attack critical strikes."]}, {"about": "Savagery", "lines": ["Damage changed to 10 + (10 * level) (+150% AD) from 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+200% AD).", "Attack speed changed to 47 + (3 * level)% from 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 / 100%.", "Attack speed duration increased to 5 seconds from 4.", "Now additionally increases his attack damage by 10% for 5 seconds."]}, {"about": "Battle Roar", "lines": ["Cooldown changed to 12 seconds from 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11.", "Bonus resistances reduced to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 from 15 / 22 / 29 / 36 / 43.", "Bonus resistances duration increased to 4 seconds from 3.", "Bonus resistances are now granted regardless of if Rengar hits an enemy, but are now increased by 50% for every enemy champion or large monster hit."]}, {"about": "Battle Roar", "lines": ["Damage changed to 25 + (15 * level) (+80% AP) from 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 (+80% AP).", "Healing reduced to 8 + (4 * level) from 20 + (10 * level).", "Bonus healing per 1% of missing health increased to 6.25% from 1%."]}, {"about": "Bola Strike", "lines": ["Now a linear, collision skill shot instead of a targeted ability.", "Range increased to 1000 from 550.", "Damage changed to 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 from 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240.", "Slow increased to 60 / 65 / 70 / 75 / 80% from 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70%.", "Cooldown changed to 10 seconds from 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8."]}, {"about": "Bola Strike", "lines": ["Damage changed to 25 + (25 * level) (+70% bonus AD) from 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240 (+70% bonus AD).", "Snare duration increased to 1.75 seconds from 1 second."]}, {"about": "Thrill of the Hunt", "lines": ["Bonus movement speed while stealthed reduced to 15% at all ranks from 20 / 25 / 30%, and now only applies while moving toward an enemy champion.", "No longer grants ferocity generation while stealthed.", "Now grants 25 / 35 / 45% bonus movement speed and ferocity generation for 5 seconds after exiting stealth.", "Enemies are now made aware when Rengar is within 1000 units of them, similar to  Blood Scent.", "Cooldown reduced to 120 / 95 / 70 seconds from 140 / 105 / 70."]}]}, {"name": "Talon", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Assault", "lines": ["Bug Fix: Activating  Flash will no longer break stealth.", "Activating  Noxian Diplomacy will no longer break stealth."]}]}, {"name": "Twisted Fate", "changes": [{"about": "Pick a Card", "lines": ["Card selection window reduced to 6 seconds from 8.", "Card usage window increased to 6 seconds from 4."]}]}, {"name": "Wukong", "changes": [{"about": "Crushing Blow", "lines": ["Armor reduction reduced to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% from 30% at all ranks."]}, {"about": "Cyclone", "lines": ["AD ratio reduced to 110% from 120%."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack range reduced to 550 from 575."]}]}]}
{"id": "V4.4", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V4.4", "date": "2014-03-18", "champions": [{"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "Disintegrate", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 80 / 115 / 150 / 185 / 220 from 85 / 125 / 165 / 205 / 245.", "AP scaling increased to (+80% AP) from (+70% AP).", "50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 AP offsets the base damage nerf.", "If Disintegrate kills its target, the cooldown is reduced by half (in addition to refunding the mana)."]}, {"about": "Incinerate", "lines": ["Damage changed to 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 from 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280.", "AP scaling increased to (+85% AP) from (+75% AP).", "100 / 150 / 200 / 250 / 300 AP offsets the base damage nerf."]}, {"about": "Summon Tibbers", "lines": ["Damage changed to 175 / 300 / 425 (+80% AP) from 200 / 325 / 450 (+70% AP).", "250 AP offsets the base damage nerf."]}]}, {"name": "Diana", "changes": [{"about": "Moonsilver Blade", "lines": ["AP scaling increased to 80% from 60%."]}]}, {"name": "Elise", "changes": [{"about": "Neurotoxin", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 40 / 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 from 40 / 80 / 120 / 160 / 200.", "Max damage to monsters reduced to 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150."]}, {"about": "Venomous Bite", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 from 60 / 110 / 160 / 210 / 260.", "Max damage to monsters reduced to 50 / 75 / 100 / 125 / 150."]}, {"about": "Cocoon", "lines": ["Stun duration changed to 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 seconds from 1.5 at all ranks."]}, {"about": "Rappel", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 26 / 23 / 20 / 17 / 14 seconds from 26 / 24 / 22 / 20 / 18."]}, {"about": "Spider Form", "lines": ["Spiderlings health changed to 85-390 from 90-260."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Mystic Shot", "lines": ["AP ratio increased to 40% from 20%."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": [{"about": "Blade Waltz", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Fiora would occasionally be locked out of using  Flash if Blade Waltz was interrupted."]