 if they did not hit a wall.", "Condemn's damage is now dealt after the knock-back, rather than when the projectile hits. If the target hits a wall, the damage splat is now larger (as with critical strikes)."]}]}, {"name": "Vi", "changes": [{"about": "Assault and Battery", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where, if Vi's Banshee's Veil is popped at same moment Vi casts Assault and Battery, Assault and Battery would cause Vi to be locked into her charging animation."]}]}, {"name": "Janna", "changes": [{"about": "Tailwind", "lines": ["Tailwind range reduced to 800 from global.", "Tailwind movement speed buff increased to 5% from 3%."]}, {"about": "Howling Gale", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 0.35 from 0.75.", "Charge damage reduced to 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 (+10% AP) from 25 / 30 / 40 / 50 / 60."]}, {"about": "Zephyr", "lines": ["Passive self-movement speed buff changed to 4 / 6 / 8 / 10 / 12% (+2% per 100 AP) from a flat 4 / 7 / 10 / 13 / 16%.", "Slow debuff now scales at +6% per 100 ability power, capped at 80% total.", "Base slow reduced to 24 / 28 / 32 / 36 / 40% from 24 / 30 / 36 / 42 / 48%.", "Ability power ratio reduced to 0.5 from 0.6."]}, {"about": "Eye of the Storm", "lines": ["Attack damage buff of the shield now scales with (+10% AP).", "Shield health ratio reduced to 0.7 of ability power from 0.9."]}]}, {"name": "Leona", "changes": [{"about": "Eclipse", "lines": ["Bonus armor changed to 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 (+20% bonus armor) from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70.", "Bonus magic resist changed to 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 65 (+20% bonus MR) from 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70."]}]}, {"name": "Lulu", "changes": [{"about": "Pix, Faerie Companion", "lines": ["Damage per bolt changed to 3-27 (+5% AP) from 3-35."]}, {"about": "Glitterlance", "lines": ["The slow now increases/decreases to (13.3% per 100 AP) over the duration.", "0 AP - The slow decays to 0% over the duration.", "602 AP - The slow remains constant for the duration.", "602+ AP - The slow will get stronger over the duration."]}, {"about": "Whimsy", "lines": ["Ability power buff removed.", "Movement speed bonus changed to 30% (+10% per 100 AP) movement speed from a fixed 35%."]}, {"about": "Help, Pix!", "lines": ["Damage ability power ratio reduced to 40% from 60%."]}]}, {"name": "Nami", "changes": [{"about": "Surging Tides", "lines": ["Movement speed bonus now scales with (+10% AP)."]}, {"about": "Aqua Prison", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 50% from 65%."]}, {"about": "Ebb and Flow", "lines": ["Damage reduction changed from a flat 15% reduction per bounce to a -15% (+7.5% per 100 AP) damage modifier with each bounce. The damage modifier can become positive, leading to increased damage."]}, {"about": "Tidecaller's Blessing", "lines": ["On-hit movement speed slow now scaled with (+5% per 100 AP)."]}, {"about": "Tidal Wave", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 60% from 70%."]}]}, {"name": "Sona", "changes": [{"about": "Hymn of Valor", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 50% from 70%.", " Power Chord: Staccato damage now scales with (+20% AP)."]}, {"about": "Aria of Perseverance", "lines": ["Base heal reduced to 40 / 55 / 70 / 85 / 100 from 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120.", " Power Chord: Diminuendo damage reduction now scales with (+2% per 100 AP)."]}, {"about": "Song of Celerity", "lines": ["Activated movement speed bonus changed to 4 / 6 / 8 / 10 / 12% (+2% per 100 AP) from 6 / 8 / 10 / 12 / 14%.", " Power Chord: Tempo slow now scales with (+4% per 100 AP)."]}, {"about": "Crescendo", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 50% from 80%."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Improved Soraka's running animation."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health increased to 405 from 375.", "Health per level increased to 76 from 71.", "Base armor increased to 9.4 from 7.4."]}, {"about": "Salvation", "lines": ["New Passive: Soraka's health and mana restoring abilities are 1% more powerful for every 2% of the target's missing health or mana."]}, {"about": "Starcall", "lines": ["Magic resistance reduction change to 6 (+1% AP) from 8 / 9 / 10 / 11 / 12.", "Mana cost changed 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 from 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80.", "Base damage increased to 60 / 95 / 130 / 160 / 200 from 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160.", "Gains the following effect: If Starcall hits at least one enemy champion, Astral Blessing's coolding is reduced by 5 / 6.25 / 7.5 / 8.75 / 10% of its base cooldown (factoring CDR)."]}, {"about": "Astral Blessing", "lines": ["Heal reduced to 70 / 120 / 170 / 220 / 270 (+35% AP) from 70 / 140 / 210 / 280 / 350 (+45% AP).", "Armor buff increased to 50 / 65 / 80 / 95 / 110 (+15% AP) from 25 / 45 / 65 / 85 / 105.", "Armor buff duration reduced to 2 seconds from 3 seconds.", "Mana cost reduced to 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 / 160 from 80 / 110 / 140 / 170 / 200."]}, {"about": "Infuse", "lines": ["Revised Active - On Ally Cast: Soraka drains 5% of her maximum mana to restore 20 / 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 (+5% maximum mana) to the target allied champion.", "Can no longer be cast on targets who do not use mana or are already at maximum mana.", "Damage changed to 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+40% AP)(+5% maximum mana) from 50 / 100 / 150 / 200 / 250 (+60% AP).", "Note that the ability is still free to cast on enemies."]}, {"about": "Wish", "lines": ["Heal reduced to 150 / 250 / 350 (+55% AP) from 200 / 320 / 440 (+70% AP).", "Now affects untargetable allies."]}]}, {"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "Gemcraft", "lines": ["New Passive: After using an ability, Taric's next basic attack deals bonus magic damage equal to 30% of Taric's armor and reduces his abilities' cooldown by 2 seconds."]}, {"about": "Imbue", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14 seconds from 20 / 19 / 18 / 17 / 16.", "Mana cost reduced to 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140 from 80 / 95 / 110 / 125 / 140.", "Heal ability power ratio reduced to 30% from 60%.", "Heal now additionally scales with (+5% Taric's bonus health).", "Cooldown reduction on autoattacks removed (moved to passive)."]}, {"about": "Shatter", "lines": ["Damage changed to 40 / 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 (+50% armor) from 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+60% AP)(+20% armor)."]}, {"about": "Dazzle", "lines": ["AP ratio reduced to 20-40% from 40-80%.", "Cooldown increased to 18 / 17 / 16 / 15 / 14 seconds from 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10."]}, {"about": "Radiance", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 50% from 70%.", "Cooldown increased to 75 seconds from 60."]}]}, {"name": "Heimerdinger", "changes": [{"about": "H-28G Evolution Turret", "lines": ["The skill reticle will now mark the age of each turret (1, 2 and 3; with 1 being the youngest)."]}, {"about": "H-28Q Apex Turret", "lines": ["Are now immune to disables."]}, {"about": "CH-3X Lightning Grenade", "lines": ["Heimerdinger will now cast throw the grenade at maximum range if you attempt to cast outside of maximum range, rather than having Heimerdinger move forward to get in range."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": ["New lore."]}, {"name": "Poppy", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Adjusted splash artwork for  Lollipoppy."]}]}, {"name": "Taric", "changes": ["Undocumented: Damage armor ratio decreased to 30% of his armor from 50%."]}, {"name": "Gragas", "changes": [{"about": "Barrel Roll", "lines": ["Bugfix: Fixed a bug where Gragas' Barrel Roll became unavailable if Gragas died immediately after throwing his barrel."]}]}, {"name": "Syndra", "changes": [{"about": "Scatter the Weak", "lines": ["Bugfix: Fixed a bug where the E-W combo would not stun the target if they were hit by  Force of Will first."]}]}, {"name": "Olaf", "changes": [{"about": "Undertow", "lines": ["Bugfix: Fixed a bug where dropping a  ward after using Undertow would create new axes that would both do damage and reduce Undertow's cooldown."]}]}]}
{"id": "V3.13", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V3.13", "date": "2013-10-29", "champions": [{"name": "Heimerdinger", "changes": [{"about": "H-28G Evolution Turret", "lines": ["Active: Heimerdinger constructs a turret at the target location equip with a cannon that shoots nearby foes and a laser beam that tears through all enemies in a line."]}, {"about": "Hextech Micro-Rockets", "lines": ["Active: Heimerdinger unleashes a barrage of rockets that converge on the target location and fan out past it, damaging the first enemies they hit."]}, {"about": "CH-1 Electron Storm Grenade", "lines": ["Active: Heimerdinger hurls a grenade that explodes at the target location, damaging and slowing enemies caught in the blast. Enemies hit directly are also stunned."]}, {"about": "UPGRADE!!!", "lines": ["Heimerdinger switches to an empowered selection of the abilities. This ability on cooldown after casting one of the following:", "H-28Q Apex Turret - Active: Heimerdinger places an apex turret that has more health, shoots faster, and gains a slow and splash damage on its attacks.", "Hextech Rocket Swarm - Active: Heimerdinger launches 4 waves of missiles one after the other.", "CH-3X Lightning Grenade - Active: Heimerdinger hurls a modified grenade that bounces 3 times, damaging and disabling enemies at each impact zone."]}]}, {"name": "Aatrox", "changes": [{"about": "Blood Well", "lines": ["Passive attack speed changed to 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 / 55% (upgrades every 3 champion levels) from 50% flat."]}, {"about": "Blades of Torment", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 75 / 110 / 145 / 180 / 215 from 75 / 120 / 165 / 210 / 255."]}]}, {"name": "Ahri", "changes": [{"about": "Essence Theft", "lines": ["Now heals 2 + (1 * level) + (9% AP) per enemy hit by the empowered ability, rather than granting spell vamp."]}, {"about": "Fox-Fire:", "lines": ["Enemies hit with multiple fox-fires take 30% damage from each additional fox-fire beyond the first, down from 50%.", "Maximum damag