lds."]}]}, {"name": "Olaf", "changes": [{"about": "Undertow", "lines": ["Slow duration increased to 1.5-2.5 seconds from 1-2 seconds.", "Mana cost changed to 60 from 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 / 75."]}, {"about": "Vicious Strikes", "lines": ["Bonus attack speed increased to 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80% from 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80%."]}, {"about": "Reckless Swing", "lines": ["Cost reduced to 30% of the damage dealt from 40%."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": ["Texture upgrade (a soft-visual upgrade)."]}, {"name": "Rengar", "changes": [{"about": "Unseen Predator", "lines": ["Rengar now becomes visible the moment he starts leaping, rather than mid-leap."]}]}, {"name": "Shaco", "changes": [{"about": "Jack in the Box", "lines": ["Bug fix: Shaco's boxes are now properly revealed by Trap Detection."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Collision radius has been reduced at the start and end points of the dash."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": ["Visual upgrade across all skins.", "New voice, ability icons, and splash art.", {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack speed per level reduced to 1.6% from 3.28%."]}, {"about": "Ricochet changed", "lines": ["Active: Sivir's next 3 basic attacks bounce to nearby enemies, dealing standard damage to her target and 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70% of her attack damage to additional enemies hit. Enemies can only be hit once but there is no limit on how many targets can be hit per attack.", "Cooldown increased to 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 seconds from 7 / 6 / 5 / 4 / 3."]}, {"about": "Spell Shield", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 0 from 75.", "Mana returned reduced to 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120 mana from 150."]}, {"about": "On the Hunt", "lines": ["Passive: Sivir gains 40 / 60 / 80% attack speed while Ricochet is active.", "Active: Sivir rallies her allies for 10 seconds, granting all nearby allies an initial 60% Movement Speed bonus that reduces to 20% after 4 seconds.", "Cooldown changed to 120 / 90 / 60 seconds from 100 / 90 / 80.", "Cast time removed."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "Wish", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 100 at all ranks from 100 / 175 / 250."]}]}, {"name": "Syndra", "changes": [{"about": "Scatter the Weak", "lines": ["Range increased to 700 from 650.", "Dark Spheres display a small triangle that points directly away from Syndra (similar to the triangle that points to Orianna's ball), indicating the direction the sphere will move in if she uses Scatter the Weak.", "Dark Sphere stun detection should now be more accurate."]}, {"about": "Unleashed Power", "lines": ["Now tracks how many Dark Spheres are active with a counter on top of the skill's icon."]}]}, {"name": "Swain", "changes": [{"about": "Carrion Renewal", "lines": ["Now additionally restores 9% of maximum mana on champion kill/assist."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Move Quick", "lines": ["Bug fix: Dominion towers will now properly remove the movement speed bonus."]}, {"about": "Noxious Trap", "lines": ["Bug fix: No longer grants experience."]}]}, {"name": "Thresh", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Basic attack wind up is reduced by 0.25% per 1% attack speed, rather than the standard 1%."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack speed per level increased to 3% from 1%."]}]}, {"name": "Tryndamere", "changes": [{"about": "Spinning Slash", "lines": ["On-crit cooldown reduction reduced to 1 second from 2. The effect is now doubled against champions."]}]}, {"name": "Varus", "changes": [{"about": "Chain of Corruption", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 100 from 120."]}]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": [{"about": "Chaos Storm", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 100 at all ranks from 125 / 175 / 225."]}]}, {"name": "Vladimir", "changes": [{"about": "Hemoplague", "lines": ["Bug fix: The wind-down time on Hemoplague is now 0.5 seconds as intended (was occasionally longer)."]}]}, {"name": "Zed", "changes": [{"about": "Living Shadow", "lines": ["Missile speed reduced to 1500 from 2500."]}, {"about": "Death Mark", "lines": ["Tooltip updated to clarify that the shadow lasts 6 seconds.", "Travel duration increased to 0.75 seconds from 0.35.", "Zed now spawns the shadow at the cast location, instead of behind the target.", "Increased the range at which Zed can switch places with his Death Mark shadow to any range from 1100."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Short Fuse", "lines": ["Max damage increased to 150 from 139."]}, {"about": "Bouncing Bomb", "lines": ["If you attempt to cast outside of maximum range, Ziggs will now cast the ability at maximum range rather than move to get in range."]}, {"about": "Satchel Charge", "lines": ["Radius increased to 325 from 275."]}, {"about": "Hexplosive Minefield", "lines": ["No longer deals reduced damage on multiple hits to minions.", "Detonation radius per mine increased to 150 from 135."]}, {"about": "Mega Inferno Bomb", "lines": ["Now deals double damage to minions."]}]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "Deadly Bloom", "lines": ["Range reduced to 800 from 825.", "Base damage reduced to 70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210 from 75 / 115 / 155 / 195 / 235.", "AP ratio increased to 65% AP from 60% AP."]}, {"about": "Rampant Growth", "lines": ["Range increased to 850 from 825.", "Passive cooldown reduction reduced to 2 / 4 / 6 / 8 / 10% from 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 20%.", "Plant base damage changed to 23 (+6.5 per level) from 26 (+6 per level).", "Reduced the delay before seeds can be stepped on by enemies to 1.5 seconds from 3.", "Fixed a bug where spells would rarely not turn seeds into plants."]}, {"about": "Stranglethorns", "lines": ["No longer stuns after the knockup ends.", "Bug Fix: Plants summoned in the thicket will now correctly receive the buff (currently only applies to plants already active)."]}]}]}
{"id": "V3.12", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V3.12", "date": "2013-10-01", "champions": [{"name": "Jinx", "changes": ["Jinx, the Loose Cannon, is in this build but will be turned on at a later date."]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Petrifying Gaze", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 100 at all ranks from 120 / 160 / 200."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": ["Visual Upgrade."]}, {"name": "Heimerdinger", "changes": [{"about": "H-28G Evolution Turret", "lines": ["Fixed a bug that caused cooldown values to be extraordinarily high under certain conditions."]}]}, {"name": "Karthus", "changes": [{"about": "Requiem", "lines": ["Warning buff on enemy champions now has a duration that matches the impact delay."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Death Lotus", "lines": ["Cast time delay before channeling removed (reduced to 0 seconds from a 0.25 second delay).", "Total damage increased to 400 / 575 / 750 (+2.5 ability power) (+3.75 bonus attack damage) from 400 / 450 / 500 / 550 / 600 (+2.0 ability power) (+3.0 bonus attack damage).", "Channel time increased to 2.5 seconds from 2.", "Cooldown reduced to 60 / 52.5 / 45 seconds from 60 / 55 / 50."]}]}, {"name": "Lucian", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated Lucian's recommended items."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base mana regeneration increased to 7 from 6.", "Mana regeneration gained per level increased to 0.7 from 0.65."]}, {"about": "Lightslinger", "lines": ["When Lightslinger's target dies before the second shot hits, the second shot will now always attempt to find another target."]}, "Piercing Light", "Laser hit box width reduced to 100 units from 120.", "Piercing Light now leads its target by 80 units when cast on an enemy champion."]}, {"name": "Olaf", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base mana reduced to 235 from 270."]}, {"about": "Undertow", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 from 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260.", "Slow percent increased to 35 / 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 from 24 / 28 / 32 / 36 / 40.", "Slow duration reduced to 1 - 2 (based on distance traveled) from 2.5 seconds flat.", "Slow no longer decays.", "Minimum throw distance added (400).", "Axes now stick in walls and structures only if they would land in impassible terrain.", "Axes now make jungle monsters ignore unit collision (to better enable Olaf's axe pickup play in the jungle)."]}, {"about": "Vicious Strikes", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 30 at all ranks from 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60.", "Now grants 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 attack speed.", "Now provides 1% extra healing for every 2.5% health that Olaf is missing", "Bonus life steal retained.", "Bonus attack damage and spell vamp removed."]}, {"about": "Reckless Swing", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 seconds from 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 5.", "Damage reduced to 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 from 100 / 160 / 220 / 280 / 340.", "Bonus damage increased to 0.4 of total attack damage ratio from 0.", "Health cost is equal to 40% of total damage dealt (unchanged ratio).", "Health cost is now refunded if it kills the target.", "Basic attacks lower the cooldown of Reckless Swing by 1 second."]}, {"about": "Ragnarok", "lines": ["Cooldown changed to 120 / 100 / 80 seconds from 100 at all ranks.", "Mana cost removed.", "Now passively provides 10 / 20 / 30 armor and magic resist.", "Active reworked: now removes the bonus armor and magic resist passive and grants 40 / 60 / 80 bonus attack damage while active.", "Olaf now turns red when Ragnarok is active.", "Crowd control immunity retained."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Adjusted recommended items to incorporate  Spirit Visage instead of  Banshee's Veil.", "Improved basic attack to be more responsive"]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base movement speed increased to 340 from 335."]}, {"about": "Desperate Power", "lines": ["Movement speed increased to 80 at all ranks from 60 / 70 / 80."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Shen's damage reduction from taunted enemies now only applies to their basic attacks (previously reduced all physical damage)."]}]}, {"name": "Thresh", "changes": [{"about": "Death Sentence", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 seconds from 18 / 16.5 / 15 / 13.5 / 12.", "Cooldown now reduced by 3 seconds if Death Sentence strikes an enemy."]}, {"about": "Flay", "lines": ["Passive basic attack \"wind up\" damage now only grows when Thresh's basic attack cooldown completes."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": ["Fixed a bug that sometimes allowed Nidalee to perform  Takedown from range."]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Noxious Trap", "lines": ["Noxious Traps gold award increased to 10 from 0."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": ["Ghouls now award 5 gold from 0."]}, {"name": "Kayle", "changes": [{"about": "Intervention", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 100 / 90 / 80 seconds from 90 / 75 / 60."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "Noxious Blast", "lines": ["Movement speed boost changed to 16 / 17 / 18 / 19 / 20 from 15 / 17.5 / 20 / 22.5 / 25."]}, {"about": "Twin Fang", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 0.45 from 0.55."]}]}, {"name": "Lulu", "changes": [{"about": "Wild Growth", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 110 / 95 / 80."]}]}, {"name": "Tryndamere", "changes": [{"about": "Spinning Slash", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 seconds from 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9."]}, {"about": "Undying Rage", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 110 / 100 / 90."]}]}, {"name": "Wukong", "changes": [{"about": "Stone Skin", "lines": ["Armor and magic resist boost reduced to 4 / 5 / 6 (based on level) from 4 / 6 / 8 (based on level)."]}, "Cyclone", "Cooldown increased to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 120 / 105 / 90."]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": ["Zyra Bot is now available in the Co-op vs. AI rotation.