{"id": "V3.11", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V3.11", "date": "2013-09-04", "champions": [{"name": "Thresh", "changes": [{"about": "Death Sentence", "lines": ["If Death Sentence is blocked by a spell shield, the chain will shatter and Thresh will be unable to cast Death Leap (previously, the chain would still tether with the target).", "Quicksilver,  Cleanse,  Mikael's Crucible and champion abilities that remove crowd control will now shatter the chain, preventing Thresh from activating Death Leap (previously, the tether and crowd control were separate effects).", "Crowd control immunity."]}]}, {"name": "Lulu", "changes": [{"about": "Wild Growth", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 120 / 110 / 100 seconds from 110 / 102.5 / 95 / 87.5 / 80."]}]}]}
{"id": "V3.10a", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V3.10a", "date": "2013-08-22", "champions": [{"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regen increased to 7.05 from 5.05.", "Attack damage per level increased to 3.5 from 3.1."]}]}, {"name": "Master Yi", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack speed per level decreased to 2% from 2.75%."]}, {"about": "Double Strike", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the second strike would damage targets even when Master Yi was blinded."]}, {"about": "Meditate", "lines": ["Damage reduction increased at later ranks to 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 from 40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60."]}, {"about": "Wuju Style", "lines": ["Passive attack damage bonus changed to 10% at all ranks from 7 / 9 / 11 / 13 / 15."]}, {"about": "Highlander", "lines": ["Now passively reduces the remaining cooldown for Master Yi's basic abilities by 70% on a kill or assist from 18 seconds on kill or 9 seconds on assist."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed an issue where several of Riven's particle effects were missing."]}, {"about": "Broken Wings", "lines": ["Third hit now knocks up affected targets rather than knocking them back.", "Only the third cast can now leap over walls.", "Hitbox has been re-tuned to more closely match the particles."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Feint", "lines": ["Shield amount reduced to 60 / 100 / 140 / 180 / 220 from 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250."]}, {"about": "Stand United", "lines": ["Can now be interrupted by root effects."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "Expunge", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 from 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80."]}]}, {"name": "Zac", "changes": [{"about": "Cell Division", "lines": ["Blob absorption and squish radius reduced to 25 from 100."]}, {"about": "Let's Bounce!", "lines": ["No longer grants tenacity.", "Fixed the tooltip to state that Zac removes all slows affecting him upon activation.