tic Shot", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 28 / 31 / 34 / 37 / 40 from 30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50."]}, {"about": "Essence Flux", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 from 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280.", "Ability power ratio increased to 0.8 from 0.6.", "Missile width reduced to 80 from 120."]}]}, {"name": "Gragas", "changes": [{"about": "Body Slam", "lines": ["Charge speed reduced to 900 from 1050.", "Mana cost increased to 75 from 50."]}, {"about": "Explosive Cask", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 100 / 90 / 80 seconds from 90 / 75 / 60."]}]}, {"name": "Graves", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Base attack speed reduced to 0.625 from 0.638."]}, {"about": "Quickdraw", "lines": ["Attack speed reduced to 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70% from 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80%."]}]}, {"name": "Jarvan IV", "changes": [{"about": "Demacian Standard", "lines": ["When targeting a location outside of Demacian Standard's range, Demacian Standard will now be cast at its maximum range in the direction of the targeted location."]}]}, {"name": "Karthus", "changes": [{"about": "Wall of Pain", "lines": ["No longer reduces armor.", "Magic resist reduction changed to 15% at all ranks from a flat 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Voracity", "lines": ["Cooldown reduction on kill or assist increased to 15 seconds from 10."]}, {"about": "Bouncing Blades", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 from 50 / 85 / 120 / 155 / 190.", "Ability power ratio decreased to 0.45 from 0.5.", "Mark detonation ability power ratio reduced to 0.15 from 0.2."]}, {"about": "Sinister Steel", "lines": ["Ability power ratio decreased to 0.25 from 0.3."]}, {"about": "Shunpo", "lines": ["Damage increased to 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160 from 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160.", "Cooldown reduced to 12 / 10.5 / 9 / 7.5 / 6 seconds from 14 / 12 / 10 / 8 / 6.", "Fixed: Tooltip now states the correct damage reduction amount (15%, not 20%)."]}]}, {"name": "Mordekaiser", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Increased model size."]}]}, {"name": "Nunu & Willump", "changes": [{"about": "Ice Blast", "lines": ["Slow duration reduced to 3 seconds from 4."]}]}, {"name": "Rengar", "changes": [{"about": "Unseen Predator", "lines": ["Now leaps directly on top of the target instead of slightly behind them."]}, {"about": "Bola Strike", "lines": ["Fixed: Bola Strike will no longer fail to cast."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 16 / 14 / 12 / 10 / 8 seconds from 10 / 9.5 / 9 / 8.5 / 8."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Toxic Shot", "lines": ["Fixed: Poison damage now works correctly at higher attack speeds."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "Expunge", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 40 / 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 from 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80.", "Mana cost reduced to 50 / 60 / 70 / 80 / 90 from 70 / 75 / 80 / 85 / 90."]}, {"about": "Spray and Pray", "lines": ["Reduced cast frame to make his attacks more responsive."]}]}, {"name": "Warwick", "changes": [{"about": "Eternal Thirst", "lines": ["Now has a buff icon and will work properly on consecutive hits."]}]}]}
{"id": "V1.0.0.145", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.145", "date": "2012-08-14", "champions": [{"name": "Rengar", "changes": ["After the completion of some further testing on PBE, Rengar was released seven days after the actual patch.", {"about": "Unseen Predator (Innate)", "lines": ["While in brush or stealth, Rengar will leap at the target when using his basic attack. Rengar builds 1 Ferocity with each ability he uses on enemies. When reaching 5 Ferocity, Rengar's next ability becomes empowered, granting it a bonus effect."]}, {"about": "Savagery (Q)", "lines": ["Rengar's next basic attack deals bonus damage and grants him increased Attack Speed for a short duration.", "Ferocity Bonus: Rengar deals enhanced damage and his Attack Speed bonus increases."]}, {"about": "Battle Roar (W)", "lines": ["Rengar lets out a battle roar, damaging enemies and gaining bonus Armor and Magic Resist for a short duration.", "Ferocity Bonus: Rengar heals himself for a percentage of his maximum health."]}, {"about": "Bola Strike (E)", "lines": ["Rengar throws a bola at his target, slowing them for a short duration.", "Ferocity Bonus: Rengar roots the target."]}, {"about": "Thrill of the Hunt (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Rengar activates his predatory instincts, stealthing and revealing all enemy champions in a large radius around him. He gains Movement Speed and rapidly generates Ferocity while stealthed."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regen per 5 reduced to 8.25 from 9.85.", "Health regen per 5 per level reduced to 0.75 from 0.85.", "Base attack damage reduced to 56 from 60.1.", "Attack damage per level increased to 3.5 from 3."]}, {"about": "Perseverance", "lines": ["Delay increased to 9 seconds from 7.", "No longer deactivates when damaged by minions.", "Now displays the health regen gained in the tooltip."]}, {"about": "Decisive Strike", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 8 seconds at all ranks from 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8.", "Movement speed increased to 35% at all ranks from 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35%.", "Movement speed duration adjusted to 1.5 / 2.25 / 3 / 3.75 / 4.5 seconds from 4 at all ranks.", "Base damage increased to 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 from 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90.", "Silence duration reduced to 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 / 2.25 / 2.5 seconds from 2.5 at all ranks.", "Now removes slows on activation.", "Can now critically strike again.", "Buff duration reduced to 4.5 seconds from 6.", "Fixed: Garen's next basic attack after Decisive Strike no longer occurs unusually quickly.", "Fixed: Decisive Strike is no longer consumed if Garen fails to finish attacking.", "While performing Decisive Strike, Garen now continues to follow his target if they are moving."]}, {"about": "Courage", "lines": ["Changed to passively increase armor and magic resist by 20% rather than 0 to 25 based on kills.", "Damage reduction changed to 30% from 20 / 24 / 28 / 32 / 36%.", "Active now additionally grants 30% crowd control reduction.", "Duration changed to 2 / 3 / 4 / 5 / 6 seconds from 3.", "Cooldown changed to 24 / 23 / 22 / 21 / 20 seconds from 30 / 27 / 24 / 21 / 18."]}, {"about": "Judgment", "lines": ["Damage adjusted to 20 / 45 / 70 / 95 / 120 (+0.7 / 0.8 / 0.9 / 1 / 1.1 total attack damage) from 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210 (+1.4 bonus attack damage).", "Damage dealt to minions increased to 75% from 50%.", "No longer removes slows on activation or reduces the duration of incoming slows while active.", "Ignores unit collision during Judgment but takes a 20% movement speed penalty when spinning through minions.", "Fixed: Judgment no longer locks out Garen from taking other actions longer than intended."]}, {"about": "Demacian Justice", "lines": ["Cooldown changed to 160 / 120 / 80 seconds from 140 / 120 / 100."]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "Remove Scurvy", "lines": ["Now removes  blinds."]}]}, {"name": "Jayce", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Improved the responsiveness of his basic attacks, primarily in Hammer stance.", "Fixed: The first basic attack after swapping to Mercury Cannon is now more responsive"]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Voracity (Innate)", "lines": ["Champion kills or assists reduce Death Lotus's cooldown by 10 seconds and refresh basic abilities."]}, {"about": "Bouncing Blades (Q)", "lines": ["10 / 9.5 / 9 / 8.5 / 8 second cooldown.", "Katarina throws a dagger which deals 50 / 85 / 120 / 155 / 190 (+0.5 ability power) magic damage. The dagger bounces to the 4 closest enemies dealing 10% less damage with each bounce.", "Enemies hit are marked for 4 seconds. Katarina's basic attacks or spells will consume the mark dealing 15 / 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 (+0.2 ability power) magic damage."]}, {"about": "Sinister Steel (W)", "lines": ["4 second cooldown.", "Whirls daggers in a circle dealing 40 / 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 (+0.5 bonus attack damage) (+0.35 ability power) magic damage. If she hits an enemy champion, Katarina gains 12 / 20 / 28 / 36 / 44% movement speed for 1 second."]}, {"about": "Shunpo (E)", "lines": ["14 / 12 / 10 / 8 / 6 second cooldown.", "Moves to a target's location. Deals 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160 (+0.5 ability power) magic damage if the target is an enemy", "After using Shunpo, Katarina gains 20% damage reduction for 3 seconds."]}, {"about": "Death Lotus (Ultimate)", "lines": ["60 / 55 / 50 second cooldown.", "Becomes a flurry of blades, throwing daggers at the closest 3 enemy champions dealing 400 / 500 / 600 (+3 bonus attack damage) (+1.75 ability power) magic damage over 2 seconds.", "Daggers apply  Grievous Wounds, reducing incoming healing by 50% for 3 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Kayle", "changes": [{"about": "Righteous Fury", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to 0.4 from 0.2."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Aegis of Zeonia", "lines": ["Jump speed slightly increased.", "Now places Pantheon slightly in front of the target instead of directly on top of the enemy."]}]}, {"name": "Shyvana", "changes": [{"about": "Dragon's Descent", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it would hitch on initial use when using skins."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Toxic Shot", "lines": ["Damage on impact increased to 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50 (+0.4 ability power) from 9 / 18 / 27 / 36 / 45 (+0.14 ability power).", "Poison ability power ratio reduced to 0.1 from 0.14.", "Fixed: Fixed a bug where the poison was lasting longer than intended.", "Fixed: Damage values will now update correctly when Teemo hits a unit with a lower level Toxic Shot poison."]}]}, {"name": "Varus", "changes": [{"about": "Piercing Arrow", "lines": ["Fixed: Piercing Arrow no longer sometimes fires from a point above his bow.", "Fixed: Piercing Arrow now more reliably hits targets at the end of its range."]}, {"about": "Blighted Quiver", "lines": ["Ability power ratio on Blight stack detonation increased to 0.02 per stack from 0.01."]}, {"about": "Chain of Corruption", "lines": ["Missile width increased to 100 from 60.", "Increased missile visibility.", "Spread range from primary target to nearby targets increased to 550 from 450.", "Tendril break range increased to 600 from 550."]}]}, {"name": "Ziggs", "changes": [{"about": "Satchel Charge", "lines": ["Fixed: Timeout tone will now play properly."]}]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "Rise of the Thorns", "lines": ["Now properly cancels spell casts upon activation."]}, {"about": "Rampant Growth", "lines": ["Destroying a seed no longer breaks spell shields.", "Plant selection radius increased slightly."]}, {"about": "Grasping Roots", "lines": ["Modified the vine particle to be easier to see."]}]}, {"name": "Lux", "changes": [{"about": "Final Spark", "lines": ["Renamed from  Infinite Light."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Lore changed.", " Bilgewater Katarina,  Mercenary Katarina,  Red Card Katarina and  Kitty Cat Katarina skin artwork changed."]}]}, {"name": "Varus", "changes": [{"about": "Chain of Corruption", "lines": ["Now will continue to creep from corpses of those affected while alive, rather than fizzling. This includes targets dying to its initial damage."]}]}]}
{"id": "V1.0.0.144", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.144", "date": "2012-08-01", "champions": [{"name": "Diana", "changes": [{"about": "Moonsilver Blade (Innate)", "lines": ["Gains attack speed. Every third strike cleaves nearby enemies for additional magic damage."]}, {"about": "Crescent Strike (Q)", "lines": ["Diana swings her blade to unleash a bolt of lunar energy that deals damage in an arc before exploding."]}, {"about": "Pale Cascade (W)", "lines": ["Diana creates three orbiting spheres that explode on contact with enemies to deal damage in an area. She also gains a temporary shield that absorbs damage. The shield is refreshed if the third sphere detonates."]}, {"about": "Moonfall (E)", "lines": ["Diana draws in and slows nearby enemies."]}, {"about": "Lunar Rush (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Diana teleports to an enemy and deals magic damage. Lunar Rush has no cooldown when used to teleport to a target afflicted by Moonlight."]}]}, {"name": "Amumu", "changes": [{"about": "Cursed Touch", "lines": ["Debuff duration reduced to 3 seconds from 4."]}, {"about": "Tantrum", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 35 from 50."]}, {"about": "Bandage Toss", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 0.7 from 1.0."]}, {"about": "Curse of the Sad Mummy", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 0.8 from 1.0."]}]}, {"name": "Brand", "changes": [{"about": "Pyroclasm", "lines": ["Missile speed increased to 1000 from 800.", "Missile speed no longer increases when hitting ablaze targets.", "If Pyroclasm strikes an ablaze target, the next bounce will now prioritize champions."]}]}, {"name": "Cho'Gath", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Magic resist per level increased to 1.25.", "Attack range normalized to 125 from 130."]}, {"about": "Rupture", "lines": ["Cast time reduced to 0.5 seconds from 0.672.", "Delay normalized to 0.625 seconds from 0.5 - 0.75."]}, {"about": "Feral Scream", "lines": ["Cast time reduced to 0.5 seconds from 0.6417."]}, {"about": "Vorpal Spikes", "lines": ["Width now increases based on Cho'Gath's size."]}, {"about": "Feast", "lines": ["Now grants Cho'Gath up to 50 additional Attack Range, based on Feast rank and amount of stacks.", "Cast time normalized to 0.5 seconds from 0.43.", "Range increased to 150 from 100."]}]}, {"name": "Evelynn", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Recommended items on Summoner's Rift now include  Boots of Mobility."]}, {"about": "Shadow Walk", "lines": ["Restealth duration reduced to 6 seconds from 8.", "Dealing periodic damage (ex.  Ignite) no longer prevents her from restealthing."]}, {"about": "Agony's Embrace", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 120 / 100 / 80 seconds from 150 / 120 / 90."]}]}, {"name": "Hecarim", "changes": [{"about": "Devastating Charge", "lines": ["Now more responsive when colliding with opponents.", "Initial movement speed bonus increased to 25% from 0% (still reaches max speed at the same time)."]}, {"about": "Onslaught of Shadows", "lines": ["Enemy flee speed is now higher based on how close the enemy is to Hecarim."]}]}, {"name": "Janna", "changes": [{"about": "Zephyr", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 0.6 from 0.8.", "Janna will no longer sometimes retain the passive bonuses while Zephyr is on cooldown."]}]}, {"name": "Lulu", "changes": [{"about": "Wild Growth", "lines": ["Now completes its effects even if the allied target was about to take lethal damage at the time of casting."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Magic resist per level increased to 1.25 from 0."]}]}, {"name": "Rumble", "changes": [{"about": "Junkyard Titan", "lines": ["Danger Zone damage bonus reduced to 25% from 30%."]}, {"about": "Flamespitter", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 90 / 160 / 230 / 300 / 370 from 90 / 180 / 270 / 360 / 450.", "Fixed: Flamespitter no longer lasts slightly longer than intended."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 52 from 50."]}, {"about": "Venom Cask", "lines": ["Missile speed increased to 1400 from 1300."]}]}, {"name": "Urgot", "changes": [{"about": "Acid Hunter", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 10 / 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 from 50 / 80 / 110 / 140 / 170.", "Scaling changed to +0.85 per total attack damage from +1.2 per bonus attack damage."]}]}, {"name": "Xin Zhao", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage reduced to 55.3 from 59.", "Attack damage per level increased to 3.3 from 3."]}, {"about": "Audacious Charge", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 from 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "Omen of Famine", "lines": ["Ravenous Ghoul will only heal Yorick for 50% of the damage it deals to minions"]}, {"about": "Omen of Death", "lines": ["The Revenant no longer instantly dies upon casting Omen of Death on an allied  Evelynn."]}]}, {"name": "Fiora", "changes": ["Lore was revised and updated."]}, {"name": "Lux", "changes": [{"about": "Infinite Light", "lines": ["Rename from  Finales Funkeln."]}]}, {"name": "Shyvana", "changes": ["Lore was revised and updated."]}, {"name": "Alistar", "changes": [{"about": "Headbutt", "lines": ["Damage adjusted to 55 / 110 / 165 / 220 / 275 from 85 / 130 / 175 / 220 / 265."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": [{"about": "Twisted Advance", "lines": ["Maokai will no longer become untargetable or disappear after casting."]}]}, {"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Base movement speed reduced to 300 from 310.", "Plant damage for additional plants reduced to 50% from 75% when multiple plants are attacking the same target."]}, {"about": "Grasping Roots", "lines": ["Damage adjusted to 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 from 60 / 105 / 150 / 195 / 240."]}, {"about": "Stranglethorns", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 180 / 265 / 350 from 200 / 300 / 400.", "Cast range reduced to 700 from 800."]}]}]}
{"id": "V1.0.0.143", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.143", "date": "2012-07-19", "champions": [{"name": "Zyra", "changes": [{"about": "Rise of the Thorns (Innate)", "lines": ["Upon dying, Zyra transforms into a vengeful plant that fires one last shot before expiring."]}, {"about": "Deadly Bloom (Q)", "lines": ["Zyra grows a bud at target location. After a brief delay it explodes, launching damaging thorns at all nearby enemies. If cast on a seed, Deadly Bloom grows a Thorn Spitter plant, which fires at enemies from afar."]}, {"about": "Rampant Growth (W)", "lines": ["Zyra gains bonus cooldown reduction. Zyra can plant a seed, granting vision of an area for up to 30 seconds and revealing enemy champions that step on it. Other spells cast on seeds will turn them into plants who fight for Zyra."]}, {"about": "Grasping Roots (E)", "lines": ["Zyra sends forth vines through the ground to ensnare her target, dealing damage and rooting enemies they come across. If cast on a seed, Grasping Roots grows a Vine Lasher, whose short range attacks reduce enemy movement speed."]}, {"about": "Stranglethorns (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Zyra summons a twisted thicket at her target location, dealing damage to enemies as it expands and knocking them airborne as it contracts. Plants in the area are enraged, increasing their attack speed."]}]}, {"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Mark of the Assassin", "lines": ["Tooltip now states the correct energy return amount."]}]}, {"name": "Amumu", "changes": [{"about": "Despair", "lines": ["Now displays a range indicator when hovered over."]}]}, {"name": "Corki", "changes": [{"about": "Valkyrie", "lines": ["Targeting indicator now scales with distance from Corki."]}]}, {"name": "Evelynn", "changes": [{"about": "Shadow Walk (Innate)", "lines": ["Evelynn fades away into the shadows. She can only be seen by nearby enemy champions or true sight.", "While in stealth, Evelynn regenerates 1% of her maximum mana every second.", "Casting spells, taking damage, or dealing damage unstealths Evelynn for 8 seconds."]}, {"about": "Hate Spike (Q)", "lines": ["Evelynn fires a line of spikes through a nearby enemy, dealing 40 / 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 (+45% AP) (+40% AD) magic damage to all enemies in its path.", "Hate spike prioritizes targets that Evelynn has attacked recently.", "Cost: 19 / 23 / 27 / 31 / 35 mana", "Cooldown: 1.5 seconds"]}, {"about": "Dark Frenzy", "lines": ["Passive: Evelynn's spell hits on enemy champions grant her 4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 20 bonus movement speed for 3 seconds, stacking up to 4 times.", "Active: Evelynn removes all slows affecting her and gains 30 / 40 / 50 / 60 / 70% bonus movement speed for 3 seconds.", "Cost: None", "Cooldown: 20 seconds", "Champion kills and assists refresh Dark Frenzy's cooldown."]}, {"about": "Ravage", "lines": ["Evelynn slashes a target enemy 2 times, dealing 35 / 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 (+50% AP) (+40% bonus AD) magic damage with each strike, then gains 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120% bonus attack speed for 3 seconds.", "Cost: 50 / 55 / 60 / 65 / 70 mana", "Cooldown: 9 seconds"]}, {"about": "Agony's Embrace", "lines": ["Evelynn impales all enemies in the targeted area, dealing 15 / 20 / 25% (+2% per 100 AP) of their maximum health in magic damage and slowing their movement speed by 30 / 50 / 70% for 2 seconds.", "Evelynn siphons their pain, gaining a 150 / 225 / 300 health shield for each enemy champion hit which lasts up to 6 seconds.", "Cost: 100 mana", "Cooldown: 150 / 120 / 90 seconds"]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "Parrrley", "lines": ["Now refunds half the mana cost if it kills the target."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Perseverance", "lines": ["Added a buff timer to show when it will reactivate."]}]}, {"name": "Gragas", "changes": [{"about": "Body Slam", "lines": ["No longer stops when encountering created terrain (e.g.  Anivia's  Crystallize)."]}]}, {"name": "Graves", "changes": [{"about": "Smoke Screen", "lines": ["Sight reduction range reduced to 675 from 800."]}]}, {"name": "Jax", "changes": [{"about": "Counter Strike", "lines": ["Dodge component now works properly against  Shen."]}]}, {"name": "Kassadin", "changes": [{"about": "Riftwalk", "lines": ["Damage reduced to 60 / 70 / 80 from 60 / 90 / 120.", "Ability power ratio increased to 80% AP from 50% AP."]}]}, {"name": "Malphite", "changes": [{"about": "Ground Slam", "lines": ["Armor ratio reduced to 30% armor from 50% armor.", "Now has a 20% AP ratio.", "Attack speed reduction duration reduced to 3 seconds from 4."]}]}, {"name": "Malzahar", "changes": [{"about": "Summon Voidling", "lines": ["Voidlings prioritize enemies Malzahar is autoattacking if  Malefic Visions isn't present.", "Voidling pathing and general AI improved.", "Voidlings now hide in brush and won't attack if Malzahar is in brush and not in combat.", "Voidling dance animation added."]}, {"about": "Call of the Void", "lines": ["Delay is now consistent at 0.6 seconds.", "Now deals damage in a single hit rather than two separate hits.", "Now grants vision along the entire line path rather than only at the two end points.", "Now deals damage to units surrounding the end points."]}, {"about": "Null Zone", "lines": ["Cast time removed. Malzahar may now cast this ability while moving.", "Damage now starts 0.25 seconds after casting the ability."]}, {"about": "Nether Grasp", "lines": ["Malzahar ignores orders that would cancel his ultimate within the first 0.5 seconds of casting.", "Voidlings prioritize champions immobilized by Nether Grasp above all other priorities."]}]}, {"name": "Mordekaiser", "changes": [{"about": "Children of the Grave", "lines": ["Initial damage now correctly draws turret aggro."]}]}, {"name": "Morgana", "changes": [{"about": "Black Shield", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 23 / 21 / 19 / 17 / 15 seconds from 15 at all ranks.", "Cast range increased to 750 from 600."]}, {"about": "Soul Shackles", "lines": ["Leash range is now more accurate. 