{"id": "V1.0.0.131", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.131", "date": "2011-12-13", "champions": [{"name": "Ahri", "changes": [{"about": "Soul Eater (Innate)", "lines": ["Ahri gains a charge of Soul Eater whenever one of her spells hits an enemy (max: 3 charges per spell). Upon reaching 9 charges, Ahri's next spell will have bonus Spell Vamp."]}, {"about": "Orb of Deception (Q)", "lines": ["Ahri throws out and pulls back her orb, dealing magic damage on the way out and true damage on the way back."]}, {"about": "Fox-Fire (W)", "lines": ["Ahri releases three fox-fires, which after a short delay lock on and attack nearby enemies."]}, {"about": "Charm (E)", "lines": ["Ahri blows a kiss that damages and charms an enemy it encounters, causing them to walk harmlessly towards her."]}, {"about": "Spirit Rush (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Ahri dashes forward and fires essence bolts, damaging 3 nearby champions. Spirit Rush can be cast up to three times before going on cooldown."]}]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": ["Evolving Technology (Innate): Viktor starts with a Hex Core that provides him with stats and can be upgraded in the store to augment one of his abilities. The Hex Core can only be upgraded once, and cannot be sold back to the store.", {"about": "Power Transfer (Q)", "lines": ["Viktor blasts an enemy unit dealing magic damage, returning a portion of the damage dealt as a shield."]}, {"about": "Gravity Field (W)", "lines": ["Viktor conjures a heavy gravitational field that slows any target in its radius. If enemies stay too long within the radius of the device, it gets stunned."]}, {"about": "Death Ray (E)", "lines": ["Viktor uses his robotic arm to fire a chaos beam that cuts across the field in a line, dealing damage to any opponents struck in its path."]}, {"about": "Chaos Storm (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Viktor conjures a singularity on the field which deals magic damage and briefly silences enemies. The singularity then does magic damage to all nearby enemies every second. Viktor can redirect the singularity."]}]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health regen per 5 reduced to 7 from 9."]}, {"about": "Urchin Strike", "lines": ["Ability power ratio reduced to 0.6 from 0.7."]}, {"about": "Seastone Trident", "lines": ["Active base damage reduced to 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 from 10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50."]}, {"about": "Chum the Waters not actually implemented", "lines": ["Added a 3-2-1 timer like  Time Bomb.", "No longer hits untargetable units like  Vladimir in  Sanguine Pool.", "Hitting an enemy who is immune to the Fish now causes the Fish to drop on the ground instead of fizzling.", "Fixed a bug where it stopped working if Fizz died.", "Using  Quicksilver Sash now drops the Fish on the ground instead of causing the shark to emerge immediately."]}]}, {"name": "Kassadin", "changes": [{"about": "Riftwalk", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 7 / 6 / 5 from 6 / 5 / 4."]}]}, {"name": "Lux", "changes": [{"about": "Prismatic Barrier", "lines": ["Shield strength increased to 80 / 105 / 130 / 155 / 180 from 60 / 85 / 110 / 135 / 160.", "Missile speed increased to 1400 from 1200."]}, {"about": "Lucent Singularity", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 9 seconds from 11."]}]}, {"name": "Miss Fortune", "changes": []}, {"name": "Mordekaiser", "changes": [{"about": "Iron Man", "lines": ["Shield conversion rate increased to 35% from 30%."]}, {"about": "Siphon of Destruction", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 from 65 / 105 / 145 / 185 / 225."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Aegis of Zeonia", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 55 from 70."]}, {"about": "Grand Skyfall", "lines": ["Mana cost reduced to 125 from 150."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated recommended items."]}, {"about": "Boomerang Blade", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 70 / 115 / 160 / 205 / 250 from 80 / 125 / 170 / 215 / 260.", "Now scales with ability power at