er champion hit increased to 7 / 10 / 13 from 5 / 8 / 11."]}]}, {"name": "Ahri", "changes": [{"about": "Essence Theft", "lines": ["Renamed from  Soul Eater."]}]}, {"name": "Viktor", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the End of Game screen was reporting massive damage done values for Viktor."]}, {"about": "Evolving Technology", "lines": ["Lowered Augment Costs to 1,000. (The displayed price will remain 1,200 until the patch in early 2012, but  The Hex Core will be upgradable for 1,000 as it was originally intended)"]}, {"about": "Augment Power", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it was not assigning the correct stats."]}, {"about": "Death Ray", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it was not doing the correct amount of damage reported."]}, {"about": "Chaos Storm", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it was reacting to  Twisted Fate's  Loaded Dice."]}]}]}
{"id": "V1.0.0.130", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.130", "date": "2011-11-29", "champions": [{"name": "Volibear", "changes": ["Rolling Thunder: Volibear drops to all fours and runs faster if chasing an enemy champion. The first enemy he attacks is knocked into the air and flung behind Volibear.", "Frenzy: Volibear's repeated attacks grant him additional attack speed. Once Volibear has repeatedly attacked three times, he can perform a vicious bite on his target.", "Majestic Roar: Volibear lets out a powerful roar that damages and slows enemies. Minions and monsters are feared as well.", "Thunder Claws: (Ultimate) Volibear channels the power of the storm causing his attacks to blast his targets with lightning that bounces to other nearby enemies.", "Chosen of the Storm (Innate): Volibear heals rapidly for a few seconds when his health drops to a critical level."]}, {"name": "Fizz", "changes": [{"about": "Urchin Strike", "lines": ["Targeting updated to hit targets slightly earlier.", "Damaging component can no longer be dodged."]}]}, {"name": "Jarvan IV", "changes": [{"about": "Martial Cadence:", "lines": ["Damage type changed to physical from magical.", "Damage changed to 6 / 8 / 10 (based on level)% of the target's current health from 8% at all levels.", "It no longer procs spell effects such as  Rylai's Crystal Scepter or Spell Vamp."]}, {"about": "Demacian Standard", "lines": ["Increased the hitbox size of it when targeted by  Dragon Strike."]}]}, {"name": "Karthus", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where  Leona's  Sunlight and the Dominion Storm Shield could cause an immediate double kill against Karthus."]}, {"about": "Wall of Pain", "lines": ["Wall duration reduced to 5 seconds from 7.", "Now only affects a target once instead of reapplying with every pass through."]}]}, {"name": "Kassadin", "changes": [{"about": "Force Pulse", "lines": ["Fixed a bug which caused it to cast backwards after performing  Riftwalk."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Shunpo", "lines": ["Now always moves Katarina behind the target regardless if  Killer Instincts is active."]}]}, {"name": "Kog'Maw", "changes": [{"about": "Icathian Surprise", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where if you killed an enemy that exploded using  Icathian Surprise, the enemy was awarded an extra kill.", "Fixed a bug where  Brand's  Pyroclasm would give him an extra kill if it was traveling toward  Kog'Maw when  Icathian Surprise triggered.", "Fixed a bug where if  Ignite killed  Kog'Maw, it would cause it to not trigger.", "Fixed a bug where  Vayne's  Silver Bolts sometimes caused it to not trigger."]}]}, {"name": "Riven", "changes": [{"about": "Blade of the Exile", "lines": ["Tooltip updated to display how much attack damage you will gain.", "It has been clarified to state that it scales off total attack damage, not bonus attack damage."]}]}, {"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "Shatter", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to 0.6 from 0.4."]}, {"about": "Radiance", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to 0.7 from 0.6."]}]}, {"name": "Vayne", "changes": [{"about": "Condemn", "lines": ["Fixed a couple small bugs introduced with last patch."]}]}, {"name": "Yorick", "changes": [{"about": "Omen of Death", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where  Ignite dealing the killing blow caused it to fail to reanimate its bearer.", "Fixed a bug where  Leona's  Sunlight and the Dominion Greater Relic could cause an immediate double kill against the  Omen of Death target.", "Fixed a bug where  Vayne's  Silver Bolts sometimes caused it to fail to reanimate its bearer."]}]}, {"name": "Nidalee", "changes": [{"about": "Bushwhack", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where traps were not dealing damage to targets.", "Fixed a bug where traps were not revealing targets, it now reveals both normal and stealthed units.", "Fixed a bug where traps were shredding things that weren't supposed to be shreddable."]}]}, {"name": "Tristana", "changes": [{"about"