{"id": "V1.0.0.126", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.126", "date": "2011-10-05", "champions": [{"name": "Xerath", "changes": ["Arcanopulse: Fires a long-range beam of energy, dealing magic damage to all targets hit.", "Locus of Power: Xerath anchors himself to a source of magical power, increasing the range of all spells and granting him bonus% Magic Penetration. Although he is immobilized while Locus of Power is active, his movement speed increases upon disabling the ability.", "Mage Chains: Deals magic damage to an enemy and marks them with Unstable Magic. The next spell Xerath strikes this enemy with stuns them.", "Arcane Barrage: Calls down a blast of arcane energy, dealing magic damage to all enemies in an area. May be cast up to three times before going on cooldown.", "Ascended Form (Innate): Xerath feeds on arcane power, making him increasingly resilient to physical harm. He converts a percentage of his Ability Power into Armor."]}, {"name": "Karthus", "changes": [{"about": "Requiem", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it would sometimes not finish channeling when cast during  Death Defied."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Ethereal Chains", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it would not root  Master Yi during  Highlander."]}]}, {"name": "Lee Sin", "changes": [{"about": "Sonic Wave", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 from 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6.", "Attack damage scaling reduced to 90% from 100%."]}, {"about": "Safeguard", "lines": ["Range reduced to 700 from 750."]}]}, {"name": "Malphite", "changes": [{"about": "Brutal Strikes", "lines": ["Modified the shape and range of its passive splash component.", "Added a visual indicator on targets hit by the passive splash damage."]}]}, {"name": "Malzahar", "changes": [{"about": "Call of the Void", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it would not finish casting if Malzahar died."]}, {"about": "Nether Grasp", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it couldn't break with distance.", "It will now