{"id": "V1.0.0.114", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.114", "date": "2011-03-29", "champions": [{"name": "Lee Sin", "changes": ["Flurry (Innate): After Lee Sin uses an ability, his next 2 basic attacks gain 50% Attack Speed and return 10 energy each.", {"about": "Sonic Wave: Lee Sin projects a discordant wave of sound to locate his enemies, dealing physical damage to the first enemy it encounters. If Sonic Wave hits, Lee Sin can cast Resonating Strike for the next 3 seconds.", "lines": [" Resonating Strike: Lee Sin dashes to the enemy hit by Sonic Wave, dealing physical damage plus 10% of their missing health."]}, {"about": "Safeguard: Lee Sin rushes towards a target ally, shielding them both from damage. If a shield is broken, half the energy cost is returned. After using Safeguard, Lee Sin can cast Iron Will for the next 3 seconds.", "lines": [" Iron Will: Lee Sin's intense training allows him to thrive in battle. For 5 seconds, Lee Sin gains lifesteal, spell vamp, and armor."]}, {"about": "Tempest: Lee Sin smashes the ground sending out a shockwave that deals magic damage and reveals enemy units hit. If Tempest hits an enemy, Lee Sin can cast Cripple for the next 3 seconds.", "lines": [" Cripple: Lee Sin cripples nearby enemies revealed by Tempest, reducing their Movement and Attack Speed for 4 seconds. Movement and Attack Speed recover gradually over the duration."]}, "Dragon's Rage (Ultimate): Lee Sin performs a powerful roundhouse kick launching his target back, dealing physical damage to the target and any enemies they collide with. Enemies the target collides with are knocked into the air for a short duration."]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Attack speed per level increased to 3% from 2.6%."]}, {"about": "Yordle Snap Trap", "lines": ["Max trap count increased to 3 from 2."]}]}, {"name": "Dr. Mundo", "changes": [{"about": "Infected Cleaver", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where targets were being slowed additively instead of multiplicatively."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Arcane Shift", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it could target unseen minions such as wards."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "Idol of Durand", "lines": ["Area of effect radius increased to 550 from 500."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Movement speed increased to 320 from 315."]}, {"about": "Courage", "lines": ["Damage reduction increased to 20 / 24 / 28 / 32 / 36% from 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30%."]}]}, {"name": "Jax", "changes": [{"about": "Leap Strike", "lines": ["Now prefers to target enemies over allies when your cursor overlaps both."]}]}, {"name": "Karma", "changes": [{"about": "Spirit Bond", "lines": ["Leash range has been increased by a small amount."]}, {"about": "Mantra", "lines": ["Charge reload time now scales with level. It has been changed to a 30 / 25 / 20 (based on level) cooldown from a 25 cooldown at all levels."]}, {"about": "Heavenly Wave", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it empowered by  Mantra was not granting assists for healing allies."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "Shunpo", "lines": ["Now prefers to target enemies over allies when your cursor overlaps both."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Distortion and  Mimic Distortion", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where they would break the target's spell shield and still deal damage."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": [{"about": "Vengeful Maelstrom", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it was reducing true damage."]}]}, {"name": "Nocturne", "changes": [{"about": "Shroud of Darkness", "lines": ["Shield is now brighter and easier to see."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "Aegis Protection", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it triggered after every 4 attacks, but every 5 spell casts instead of 4 as it was intended."]}]}, {"name": "Poppy", "changes": [{"about": "Paragon of Demacia", "lines": ["Updated shield texture."]}, {"about": "Heroic Charge", "lines": ["Fixed several unintended interactions with and spell shields. Notably, Poppy won't push herself past the target anymore."]}]}, {"name": "Shen", "changes": [{"about": "Ki Strike", "lines": ["It can now be cancelled mid-attack (and will not say 'Cannot Move While Casting').", "Fixed a bug where it could kill a target and not trigger  Vorpal Blade's heal effect."]}, {"about": "Feint", "lines": ["Updated tooltips to properly match the functionality and adjusted the playing tips referencing it."]}, {"about": "Shadow Dash", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it could move a shorter distance than intended if Shen was greatly slowed."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where some of her tooltips referred to 'Spiral Blade' instead of ' Boomerang Blade'."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "Infuse", "lines": ["Now prefers to target enemies over allies when your cursor overlaps both."]}]}, {"name": "Urgot", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base health reduced to 437 from 457."]}, {"about": "Acid Hunter", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 10 / 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 from 15 / 45 / 75 / 105 / 135."]}, {"about": "Terror Capacitor", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where its slow was stacking."]}, {"about": "Zaun-Touched Bolt Augmenter", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it was reducing true damage."]}]}, {"name": "Veigar", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed an issue on the  Leprechaun Veigar skin where the enemy  Event Horizon still had green pillars instead of red ones."]}]}, {"name": "Pantheon", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Walking animation has been updated."]}, {"about": "Grand Skyfall", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where AoE circle wasn't showing for some users."]}]}, {"name": "Nasus", "changes": [{"about": "Spirit Fire", "lines": ["Particle has been updated."]}]}]}
{"id": "V1.0.0.113", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.113", "date": "2011-03-15", "champions": [{"name": "Nocturne", "changes": [{"about": "Umbra Blades (Innate)", "lines": ["Every 10 seconds, Nocturne's next attack strikes surrounding enemies for physical damage and heals himself for each target hit. Nocturne's physical attacks reduce this cooldown by 1 second."]}, {"about": "Duskbringer (Q)", "lines": ["Nocturne throws a shadow blade which deals damage, leaves a Dusk Trail, and causes champions to leave a Dusk Trail. While on the trail, Nocturne ignores unit collision and has increased Movement Speed and Attack Damage."]}, {"about": "Shroud of Darkness (W)", "lines": ["Nocturne empowers his blades, passively gaining attack speed. Activating Shroud of Darkness allows Nocturne to fade into the shadows, creating a magical barrier which blocks a single enemy spell and doubles his passive attack speed if successful."]}, {"about": "Unspeakable Horror (E)", "lines": ["Nocturne plants a nightmare into his target's mind, dealing damage each second and fearing the target if they do not get out of range by the end of the duration."]}, {"about": "Paranoia (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Nocturne reduces the sight radius of all enemy champions and removes their ally vision in the process. He can then launch himself at a nearby enemy champion."]}]}, {"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Twin Disciplines", "lines": ["Adjusted to trigger at 9.5 bonus attack damage and 19.5 ability power to account for rounding."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated all animations."]}, {"about": "Glacial Storm", "lines": ["Initial mana cost reduced to 75 at all ranks from 75 / 125 / 175."]}, {"about": "Rebirth", "lines": ["Will now always activate after  Chronoshift and  Guardian Angel."]}]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "Headshot", "lines": ["Stacks required reduced to 8 / 7 / 6 (based on level) from 8 attacks at all levels."]}]