{"id": "V1.0.0.112", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.112", "date": "2011-03-01", "champions": [{"name": "Jarvan IV", "changes": ["Martial Cadence (Innate): Jarvan IV exploits his target's opening, dealing 10% of the target's current HP as magic damage. This effect cannot occur on the same target for 6 seconds.", "Dragon Strike: Jarvan IV charges through his opponent, dealing physical damage and lowering their armor by a percentage. This will pull Jarvan IV to a Standard if it encounters one, knocking up all enemies in his path.", "Golden Aegis: Jarvan IV calls upon the ancient kings of Demacia to shield him from harm and slow surrounding enemies.", "Demacian Standard: Passively grants Jarvan bonus attack speed and armor. Active: Throws a Demacian flag, dealing physical damage and granting passive benefits to nearby allies.", "Cataclysm (Ultimate): Jarvan IV heroically leaps at his target, dealing physical damage and creating a circle of terrain around them for a few seconds."]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Glacial Storm", "lines": ["Initial mana cost reduced to 75 / 125 / 175 from 100 / 150 / 200."]}]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "Ace in the Hole", "lines": ["Projectile speed increased to 3200 from 2200.", "Range increased to 1600 / 1900 / 2200 from 1400 / 1800 / 2200.", "Initial cast time leading up to the channeling time significantly decreased."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Trueshot Barrage", "lines": ["Now scales with the higher of a 1.0 bonus attack damage ratio OR the existing 0.9 AP ratio."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Decisive Strike", "lines": ["Attack damage scaling increased to 150% from 120%.", "Movement speed boost duration increased to 3 seconds from 2.", "Total duration available to proc the silence on hit reduced to 6 seconds from 7."]}, {"about": "Judgment", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 from 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "Janna", "changes": [{"about": "Monsoon", "lines": ["No longer has the effect of slowing enemies who re-entered the storm by 30%."]}]}, {"name": "Karma", "changes": [{"about": "Heavenly Wave", "lines": ["Base heal increased to 35 / 55 / 75 / 95 / 115 / 135 from 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 / 90 / 105."]}, {"about": "Spirit Bond", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 15 / 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 from 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 / 10."]}, {"about": "Soul Shield", "lines": ["Base shield strength and damage increased to 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 / 280 from 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 / 230 / 270."]}, {"about": "Mantra", "lines": ["Charge reload time reduced to 25 seconds from 30 seconds."]}]}, {"name": "LeBlanc", "changes": [{"about": "Ethereal Chains", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to 0.5 from 0.4 for both damage components."]}]}, {"name": "Maokai", "changes": [{"about": "Twisted Advance", "lines": ["Fixed its level up tooltip to correctly display the increase in mana cost.", "Fixed a bug where Maokai's death animation would not play."]}]}, {"name": "Mordekaiser", "changes": [{"about": "Mace of Spades", "lines": ["Ability power ratio increased to 0.4 from 0.2."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "Poison Trail", "lines": ["Fixed a bug that was producing a 1-second cooldown upon activation."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "Boomerang Blade", "lines": ["Fixed a bug that was causing certain items to not show their bonus attack damage in the tooltip."]}]}, {"name": "Urgot", "changes": [{"about": "Acid Hunter", "lines": ["Fixed a bug that was causing missile lock to shoot further than intended."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "Time Warp", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where the particle would not persist through the full duration of the movement speed modifier at later ranks."]}]}, {"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": [" Original Annie splash art has been updated."]}]}, {"name": "Evelynn", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": [" Original Evelynn splash art updated."]}]}, {"name": "Katarina", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": [" Original Katarina splash art has been updated."]}]}, {"name": "Twitch", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": [" Original Twitch splash art has been updated."]}]}]}
{"id": "V1.0.0.111", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.111", "date": "2011-02-16", "champions": [{"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}, {"about": "Mark of the Assassin", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where its sound could persist after her target died."]}]}, {"name": "Amumu", "changes": [{"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base attack damage increased to 47 from 45.", "Base armor increased to 18 from 15."]}, {"about": "Tantrum", "lines": ["Passive physical damage reduction increased to 2 / 4 / 6 / 8 / 10 from 1 / 2 / 3 / 4 / 5."]}, {"about": "Despair", "lines": ["Mana cost per second reduced to 8 from 10 at all ranks.", "Now has a new particle to match the area of effect."]}]}, {"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Rebirth", "lines": ["Armor and magic resistance modifier changed to -40 / -25 / -10 / 5 / 20 (based on level) from -40 / -20 / 10 / 40 (based on level).", "It now always shows the passive in the passive slot, and an additional buff in the buff bar with the current status (ready, active, or on cooldown)."]}, {"about": "Flash Frost", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it stunned for 0.75 seconds instead of 1 second as the tooltip stated.", "Fixed a bug where unlike other skillshots, it could not be cast from out of range."]}, {"about": "Glacial Storm", "lines": ["Initial mana cost increased to 100 / 150 / 200 from 25 / 35 / 45.", "Additional mana cost per second reduced to 40 / 50 / 60 from 50 / 70 / 90.", "Slow duration reduced to 1 second from 2.5."]}]}, {"name": "Ashe", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}]}, {"name": "Cassiopeia", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}]}, {"name": "Dr. Mundo", "changes": [{"about": "Infected Cleaver", "lines": ["Fixed an incorrect PvP.net descrip