r casting, causing him to move toward previous locations."]}]}, {"name": "Ryze", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Ryze's base mana regen did not get updated properly during the previous patch's revamp."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base magic resistance reduced to 30 from 35."]}, {"about": "Overload", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 30 / 55 / 80 / 105 / 130 from 50 / 90 / 130 / 170 / 210.", "Ability power ratio reduced to 0.2 from 0.45.", "Range increased to 675 from 600.", "Missile speed increased to 1400 from 1200.", "Cooldown reduced to 3.5 at all ranks from 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7.", "Mana cost changed to 70 at all ranks from 30 / 65 / 80 / 95 / 110."]}, {"about": "Rune Prison", "lines": ["No longer deals damage per tick and deals 60 / 95 / 130 / 165 / 200 damage up front (down from 80 / 120 / 160 / 200 / 240 over the duration).", "Ability power ratio changed to a flat 0.6 from 0.4 / 0.6 / 0.8 / 1 / 1.2 depending on snare duration.", "Now deals 5% of Ryze's maximum mana in bonus damage.", "Cast range increased to 625 from 600.", "Duration reduced to 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2 from 1.2 / 1.5 / 1.8 / 2.1 / 2.4."]}, {"about": "Spell Flux", "lines": ["Base damage reduced to 50 / 70 / 90 / 110 / 130 from 70 / 85 / 100 / 115 / 130.", "Ability power ratio per hit reduced to 0.35 from 0.38.", "Cast range increased to 675 from 625.", "Cooldown increased to 14 from 9.", "Mana cost reduced to 60 / 75 / 90 / 105 / 120 from 60 / 80 / 100 / 120 / 140."]}, {"about": "Desperate Power", "lines": ["No longer grants ability power but now grants 15% spell vamp.", "Area of effect damage percentage reduced to 50% from 65%.", "Cooldown increased to 70 / 60 / 50 from 50 at all ranks.", "Duration reduced to 5 / 6 / 7 from 8 at all ranks.", "Now grants a passive 75 / 150 / 225 mana."]}]}, {"name": "Singed", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}]}, {"name": "Sivir", "changes": [{"about": "Boomerang Blade", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 75 / 120 / 165 / 210 / 255 from 20 / 70 / 120 / 170 / 220.", "Now scales from 95% of bonus attack damage instead of 75% of total attack damage.", "Damage reduction to each subsequent target increased to 20% from 10%."]}]}, {"name": "Tryndamere", "changes": [{"about": "Undying Rage", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it could not be activated while suppressed."]}]}, {"name": "Vladimir", "changes": [{"about": "Crimson Pact", "lines": ["Bonus ability power gain reduced to 1 ability power per 40 bonus health from 1 per 25 health."]}, {"about": "Sanguine Pool", "lines": ["It no longer grants the hidden ~25% movement speed bonus on use.", "It fixed a bug where Turrets would sometimes idle while Vladimir was pooled.", "It fixed a bug where it would occasionally not properly draw aggro upon exiting his pool."]}]}, {"name": "Zilean", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Updated tooltips."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Base magic resistance reduced to 30 from 35."]}]}]}
