": ["Fixed a bug where could not deal damage to the same target within 1 second of the previous hit."]}]}, {"name": "Rammus", "changes": [{"about": "Powerball", "lines": ["Slow reduced to 20 / 25 / 30 / 35 / 40% from 28 / 36 / 44 / 52 / 60%.", "Slow duration reduced to 3 seconds from 4."]}, {"about": "Puncturing Taunt", "lines": ["Cooldown increased to 12 from 9."]}]}, {"name": "Renekton", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where Renekton was gaining bonus attack damage while wounded."]}, {"about": "Stats", "lines": ["Health per level increased to 87 from 82.", "Base armor increased to 15.2 from 14.", "Armor per level increased to 3.8 from 3.2."]}, {"about": "Cull the Meek", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 / 180 from 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160.", "Attack damage scaling increased to 80% from 60%.", "Basic heal reduced to 7.5% from 10%.", "Heal bonus when damaging Champions increased to 300% from 200%.", "Cooldown reduced to 8 seconds at all ranks from 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8."]}, {"about": "Ruthless Predator", "lines": ["Cooldown reduced to 13 / 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 from 14 / 13 / 12 / 11 / 10."]}, {"about": "Dice", "lines": ["Armor reduction when furious changed to 15 / 17.5 / 20 / 22.5 / 25% from a flat 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30."]}]}, {"name": "Shaco", "changes": [{"about": "Deceive", "lines": ["Fixed a bug where it could be dodged."]}]}, {"name": "Soraka", "changes": [{"about": "General", "lines": ["Removed  Innervating Locket from her tips."]}, {"about": "Astral Blessing", "lines": ["Base heal changed to 60 / 120 / 180 / 240 / 300 from 80 / 130 / 180 / 230 / 280.", "Ability power ratio reduced to 0.9 from 1.", "Armor buff increased to 20 / 35 / 50 / 65 / 80 from 15 / 20 / 25 / 30 / 35.", "Buff duration reduced to 4 seconds from 9."]}]}, {"name": "Teemo", "changes": [{"about": "Move Quick Reworked", "lines": ["Passive: Now grants 10 / 15 / 20 / 25 / 30% increased movement speed until struck by a champion or turret.", "Active: Tee