{"id": "V1.0.0.109", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.109", "date": "2011-01-18", "champions": [{"name": "Renekton", "changes": ["Renekton uses a new resource system called Fury. Renekton gains Fury by attacking or dealing damage with spells. When he has gathered enough Fury, the resource will be expended to empower his skills with bonus effects.", "Reign of Anger (Innate): Renekton gains 5 Fury per autoattack. Having sufficient fury empowers Renekton's abilities with bonus effects, but this drains Fury. Out of combat, Renekton loses 5 Fury per second.", {"about": "Cull the Meek: Renekton swings his blade, dealing damage to nearby enemies and healing for a portion of the damage dealt.", "lines": ["Fury Bonus: Heal amount raised dramatically."]}, {"about": "Ruthless Predator: Renekton's next attack swings twice, dealing damage, plus a large portion of his base damage, stunning his target briefly and applying on-hit effects each time.", "lines": ["Fury Bonus: Renekton's next attack swings three times, dealing a huge portion of his weapon damage, stunning his target greatly and applying on-hits each time."]}, {"about": "Slice: Renekton dashes forward, dealing physical damage to targets along the way. If he hits a target, he can use  Dice for a brief period of time for the same effect.", "lines": ["Fury Bonus: Renekton deals 50% increased damage and reduces the armor of units hit."]}, "Dominus (Ultimate): Renekton empowers himself with dark energy, gaining size and bonus health. He deals periodic damage to enemies around him and rapidly gains Fury."]}, {"name": "Caitlyn", "changes": [{"about": "Piltover Peacemaker", "lines": ["Base damage changed to 20 / 65 / 110 / 155 / 200 from 40 / 70 / 100 / 130 / 160.", "Attack damage scaling increased to 1.3 from 1.", "Damage loss per unit increased to 10% from 6%.", "Maximum damage loss increased to 50% from 30%."]}, {"about": "Ace in the Hole", "lines": ["Base damage increased to 250 / 475 / 700 from 250 / 