{"id": "V1.0.0.99", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V1.0.0.99", "date": "2010-08-24", "champions": [{"name": "Urgot", "changes": ["Zaun-Touched Bolt Augmenter (Innate): Enemies hit by Urgot have their damage output lowered.", "Acid Hunter: Urgot fires a straight line missile that deals damage to the first enemy it hits. If an enemy is hit by a Corrosive Charge then Acid Hunter can target lock onto them, guaranteeing a hit.", "Terror Capacitor: Urgot is shielded from damage and slows enemies with each hit.", "Noxian Corrosive Charge: Urgot fires a corrosive missile to a location that splashes to enemies on impact, dealing damage and lowering their armor. Allows target locking with Acid Hunter.", "Hyper-Kinetic Position Reverser (Ultimate): Urgot locks an enemy champion in place as he swaps positions with them, gaining armor and magic resist in the process."]}, {"name": "Akali", "changes": [{"about": "Twin Disciplines", "lines": ["Modified to gain 1% spell vamp for every 5 bonus attack damage instead of 1% for every 10 bonus attack damage."]}]}, {"name": "Annie", "changes": [{"about": "Molten Shield", "lines": ["Now reflects damage to all basic attacks instead of just melee attacks."]}]}, {"name": "Anivia", "changes": [{"about": "Flash Frost", "lines": ["Pass through damage will now break spell shields."]}]}, {"name": "Ezreal", "changes": [{"about": "Mystic Shot", "lines": ["Attack damage scaling reduced to 1.0 from 1.1."]}]}, {"name": "Galio", "changes": [{"about": "Resolute Smite", "lines": ["Particle now more properly represents the area of effect."]}, {"about": "Idol of Durand", "lines": ["Taunt radius reduced to 500 from 520.", "Damage radius increased to 520 from 500.", "Adjusted team colored range circle to more accurately represent taunt range."]}]}, {"name": "Garen", "changes": [{"about": "Judgment", "lines": ["Now reduces the duration of new slows by 50% rather than granting immunity to slowing effects. It will still completely clear any exis