{"id": "V0.9.25.34", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V0.9.25.34", "date": "2009-10-10", "champions": [{"name": "Shaco", "changes": [{"about": "Backstab (Innate)", "lines": ["Shaco deals 25% bonus damage when striking a unit from behind."]}, {"about": "Deceive (Q)", "lines": ["Shaco enters stealth and instantly teleports to target location. His next attack has a 100% chance to critical strike."]}, {"about": "Jack in the Box (W)", "lines": ["Shaco drops a Jack-in-the-Box at target location, which will wait, stealthed, to fear nearby units and attack them when someone comes nearby."]}, {"about": "Two-Shiv Poison (E)", "lines": ["Passive: Shaco's attacks poison targets on hit, reducing their chance to hit and slowing them.", "Active: Shaco throws his daggers to deal damage and poison the target."]}, {"about": "Hallucinate (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Shaco creates an illusion of himself that can attack nearby enemies. It explodes upon death dealing AoE damage."]}]}, {"name": "Heimerdinger", "changes": [{"about": "Techmaturgical Repair Bots (Innate)", "lines": ["Heimerdinger gives nearby allied turrets and champions 6 / 12 / 16 / 22 health regen per 5."]}, {"about": "H-28G Evolution Turret (Q)", "lines": ["Heimerdinger lays down a machine gun turret. This turret gains experience from attacking units, and can be upgraded."]}, {"about": "Hextech Micro-Rockets (W)", "lines": ["Heimerdinger fires a number of champion seeking missiles that randomly target champions within range."]}, {"about": "CH-1 Concussion Grenade (E)", "lines": ["Heimerdinger lobs a grenade at a location, dealing damage to enemy units and structures, as well as stunning anyone directly hit and blinding nearby units."]}, {"about": "UPGRADE!!! (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Passive: cooldown reduction.", "Active: Target an Evolution Turret to heal it, double its attack speed for 10 seconds, add 200 health, 10 damage, 10 armor, and upgrade it to:", "Level 2: Ur'Anium Rounds - Basic attacks reduce armor &