{"id": "V0.9.22.15", "url": "https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/V0.9.22.15", "date": "2009-08-19", "champions": [{"name": "Taric", "changes": [{"about": "Gemcraft (Innate)", "lines": ["Taric loves to socket magical gems into all of his weapons, resulting in his melee attacks replenishing his mana for 7.5% of damage dealt."]}, {"about": "Imbue (Q)", "lines": ["Taric channels earthen energy to heal his target. As the magic flows through him he is healed for the same amount. If Taric heals only himself, the total effect will be 1.25X the base heal amount."]}, {"about": "Shatter (W)", "lines": ["Taric increases the armor of his nearby allies. He may choose to activate this ability to deal damage and decrease the armor of his nearby enemies at the cost of this benefit."]}, {"about": "Dazzle (E)", "lines": ["Taric emits a brilliant ball of prismatic light from his gemmed shield, dazzling his enemies."]}, {"about": "Radiance (Ultimate)", "lines": ["Taric emits a brilliant light, healing his allies and increasing their physical damage."]}]}, {"name": "Gangplank", "changes": [{"about": "Grog-Soaked Blade (Innate)", "lines": ["Gangplank's attacks apply a poison that deals 5 (+1 per level) damage per second for 7 seconds and reduces incoming healing by 40%."]}, {"about": "Parrrley (Q)", "lines": ["Gangplank shoots a target unit dealing magical damage based on attack damage and can trigger on hit effects in addition to the ability's effects.. If he kills it, then he gains extra gold."]}, {"about": "Remove Scurvy (W)", "lines": ["Consumes a large quantity of citrus fruit which clears any crowd control effects on him and heals him."]}, {"about": "Raise Morale (E)", "lines": ["Passive: Gangplank's attack speed and movement speed are increased. Gangplank doesn't receive the benefit of the passive while the spell is recharging.", "Active: Gangplank kills an allied minion, inspiring nearby champions to receive Raise Morale's passive benefits for 10 seconds."]}, {"about": "Cannon